\id ACT
\h Řexdayem n rrusul
\toc1 Řexdayem n rrusul
\toc2 Řexdayem n rrusul
\toc3 Řex.
\mt1 Řexdayem n rrusul
\c 1
\s1 Tamezwarut
\m 
\v 1 Adlis amezwaru i uriɣ, \add a\add* Tiyufilis, \add uriɣ t\add* x marra min ibda Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad igg u ad isseřmed,
\v 2 ař ass i di immeksi \add ɣar ujenna\add*, awarni řami iweṣṣa i rrusul i tuɣa yixḍar Netta s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, \f ◼ \fr 1:2 \fk rrusul\ft - niɣ ‘imazanen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Mk. 16:19; Lk. 9:51; Yḥ. 20:21; 1 Tim. 3:16. \x*
\v 3 inni umi, awarni řami tuɣa iweddeb, isscen asen Ixef nnes s waṭṭas n řeɛřamat belli aqa iddar, am d asen dd-iḍhar arebɛin n wussan, issawař x Tgeldit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Mk. 16:14; Yḥ. 20:19; 21:1; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\b
\s1 Tameksit n Yasuɛ ɣar ujenna
\m 
\v 4 Řami akidsen icca aɣrum, iweṣṣa ten ḥima war dd-tteffɣen ca zi Urcalim, maca ad qqimen ad rajan lwaɛd n Baba i tuɣa kenniw, \add ammu i inna,\add* “tesřim zzayi, \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Lk. 24:48, 49; Yḥ. 14:26; 15:26; 16:7. \x*
\v 5 minzi Yuḥanna tuɣa isseɣḍaṣ deg waman, \add maca\add* kenniw ad ttwassɣeḍṣem di Arruḥ Iqeddsen awarni drus n wussan.” \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Ica. 44:3; Yuw. 3:1; Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:8; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:26; Řex. 2:4; 11:15, 16; 19:4. \x*
\m 
\v 6 Xenni sseqsan t inni tuɣa din imunen, nnan: “\add A\add* Siditneɣ, ma di řweqt-a ad dd-tarred Tageldit i Israil ɛawed?” \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Mt. 24:3. \x*
\v 7 Inna asen: “War d awem dd-yusi ad taregbem x zzman d zzmanat i igga Baba di ṣṣulṭa n Yixef nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Mt. 24:36. \x*
\v 8 Maca kenniw ad teksim jjehd xmi xawem dd ɣa ihwa Arruḥ Iqeddsen uca kenniw ad tiřim d řechud di Urcalim, di marra Yahudiyya, di Samarya, \add wah,\add* ař ineggura n ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ica. 2:3; Lk. 24:48; Yḥ. 15:27; Řex. 2:4, 32. \x*
\m 
\v 9 \add Awarni řami\add* inna aya, immeksi uca, am t ẓrin nitni, iksi t ijj n useynu, idweř inuffar x tiṭṭawin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Mk. 16:19; Lk. 24:51. \x*
\v 10 Am d as sseḍfaren s tiṭṭawin nsen am iruḥ ɣar ujenna, \add xzar\add*, aqa bedden ɣarsen tnayen n yeryazen arḍen arruḍ d acemřař, \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Mt. 28:3. \x*
\v 11 uca nnan asen: “\add A,\add* iryazen zi Ljalil, min kenniw ideɛwen tᵉttbeddam txezzarem ɣar ujenna? Aqa Yasuɛ wanita, wenni immeksin xawem ɣar ujenna, ad dd-iɛqeb am mammec t teẓrim igeɛɛed ɣar ujenna!” \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Dan. 7:13; Zak. 14:1-15; Mt. 24:30; Mk. 13:26; Lk. 21:27; 1 Ts. 1:10; 2 Ts. 1:10; Asa. 1:7. \x*
\b
\s1 Řixḍaret n Mattiya deg wemcan n Yahuda
\m 
\v 12 Xenni ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim zeg wedrar umi qqaren ‘Taddart n Zzitun’ i iǧan zzat i Urcalim, iggʷej xas ɛřaḥař sebɛa ‘istadiyyen’, \add ixs ad yini ɛřaḥař ijj n kilumitr u třata meyya mitr\add*.
\v 13 Awarni řami dd-udfen \add ɣar tendint\add*, geɛɛden ɣar tɣurfet sennej mani tuɣa ttɣiman nitni: Buṭrus, Yuḥanna, Yaɛqub, Andrawus, Filippus, Tuma, Matta, Bar-Tulumawus, Yaɛqub mmis n Ḥalfa, Cimɛun umi qqaren ‘Amɛessab’, d Yahuda, mmis n Yaɛqub.
\v 14 Ina marra idsen tuɣa ṣbaren s yijj n dmam x tẓaǧit, ak-d temɣarin u ak-d Maryam, yemmas n Yasuɛ, u ak-d aytmas. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Mt. 13:55. \x*
\m 
\v 15 Deg wussan nni ikkar Cimɛun Buṭrus jar asen, di řwesṭ n imeḥḍaren. Tuɣa din munen ɛřaḥař mya u-ɛicrin n iwdan, u netta inna: \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt 2 Im. 5:12\x*
\m 
\v 16 “\add A\add* iryazen tawmat, tuɣa ittxeṣṣa nican ad ittwakemmeř \add awař\add* n Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* i ittwannan qbeř s Arruḥ Iqeddsen s uqemmum n Dawud x Yahuda, wenni idewřen d amgewwed n yinni iḥebbsen Yasuɛ, \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Izhd. 41:10; Mt. 26:23, 47; Mk. 14:43; Yḥ. 13:18; 18:3. \x*
\v 17 minzi netta tuɣa ittwaḥseb zzayneɣ, \add zi tenɛac\add*, u tuɣa iṭṭef tasɣart di tsexxart-a. \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Mt. 10:4; Mk. 3:19; Lk. 6:16. \x*
\v 18 Aqa wa tuɣa ikesseb ijj n iyyar i yixef nnes s řmunet n ddenb \add nnes\add* uca umi iwḍa x uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt, aqa ifeǧeq ɣar tejɛinnatin nnes uca ffɣen-dd marra adan nnes ɣar barra. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt 2 Ṣm. 17:23; Mt. 27:3-5. \x*
\v 19 Aqa man aya idweř ittwassen ɣar marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim ařami semman iyyar nni deg iřes n temmurt nsen ‘Ḥaql-Dama’, min ixs ad yini ‘Iyyar n idammen’. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Mt. 27:8. \x*
\v 20 Minzi tura deg wedlis n Izehhiden \add n Dawud\add*:
\b
\m \qt ‘Ad tedweř taddart nnes d řxarbet,\qt*
\m \qt uřa d ijj war dayes izeddeɣ!’\qt*
\b
\m uca:
\b
\m \qt ‘Ad iksi wenneɣni tasexxart nnes.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Izhd. 69:26; 109:8. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 S uyenni ittřiq, aqa ijjen zeg yeryazen inni tuɣa d imɛacaren akidneɣ kuř řweqt i di tuɣa Siditneɣ Yasuɛ ittadef u itteffeɣ jar aneɣ - \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt Řex. 6:3. \x*
\v 22 zeg useɣḍeṣ n Yuḥanna ař ass i di immeksi xaneɣ - ad idweř d acehhad akidneɣ x tnukra nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 23 Areccḥen tnayen: Yusuf, umi qqaren Bar-Saba wenni umi ttkennan Yustus, d Mattiya. \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Řex. 6:6. \x*
\v 24 Am tuɣa ttẓaǧan, nnan: “\add A\add* SIDI, Cek tessned uřawen n marra, scen \add aneɣ\add* man wen zi tnayen-a i tixḍared, \x ◘ \xo 1:24 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:17; 1 Im. 28:9; 29:17; Izhd. 7:10; Irm. 11:20; 17:10; 20:12; Řex. 15:8; Asa. 2:23. \x*
\v 25 ḥima ad icarc di tsexxart-a u di řxedmet n rrusul i di ismeḥ Yahuda ḥima ad iraḥ ɣar wemcan nnes.”
\v 26 Xenni ggin akeccuḍ uca yusa-dd \add ukeccuḍ\add* x Mattiya uca arnin t ɣar ḥiṭac n rrusul.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Asfarreɣ n Arruḥ Iqeddsen
\m 
\v 1 Umi kemmřen wussan ař Řɛid n Xemsin n Wussan, tuɣa aten marra jmiɛ munen. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Lawi 23:15; Aɛwd. 16:9; Řex. 1:14. \x*
\v 2 X ict n řɣefřet yusa-dd ijj n zzhir zeg ujenna, igga axmi d asemmiḍ ijehden aṭṭas, iccur marra taddart mani tuɣa qqimen.
\v 3 Uca ḍharen asen-dd iřsawen am n tmessi nni ittemsebḍan, arsin x kuř ijjen zzaysen,
\v 4 u marra nitni dewřen ccuren s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, bdan ad ssiwřen \bd s ijj n yiřes nneɣni\bd* am mammec d asen iwca Arruḥ ad zzaysen neṭqen. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:8; 16:17; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 14:26; 15:26; 16:13; Řex. 10:46; 11:15; 19:6. \x*
\m 
\v 5 Tuɣa ttɣiman di Urcalim iryazen nni ittegʷeden AREBBI, Udayen zi marra řegnus sadu ujenna.
\v 6 Umi ikkar zzhir-a, imun marra řgens \add dinni\add* uca tbehten, minzi kuř ijj tuɣa ittesřa asen ssawařen s yiřsawen nsen \add ifarzen\add*.
\v 7 Dehcen, tbehten marra, nnan jar asen: “Ma war ǧin marra ina inni \add din\add* issawařen d Ijaliliyyen?
\v 8 Mammec d asen nesřa neccin, kuř ijj zzaysen, \add ssawařen\add* s yiřes i zi dd-netwaxřeq?
\v 9 Ipartiyyen d Imidiyyen d Iɛilamiyyen d imezdaɣ n Misuputamya, \add tenni d tammurt jar tnayen n iɣezran\add*, d Wudayen d inni zi Kappadukiya, inni dd-yusin zi jjwayeh n Punṭus d Asiya,
\v 10 zi jjwayeh n Frixiya, Pamfiliya d Miṣra u zi jjwayeh n Libiya ɣar Qayrawan, uřa d inni dd-yusin zi Ruma, am Udayen am yinni idewřen d imɛacaren n ddin n Wudayen,
\v 11 inni\add dd-yusin\add* zi Krita u \add zi\add* Ɛarabiyya, aqa neccin nesřa asen ssawařen s yiřes nneɣ x řeɛjayeb imeqqranen n AREBBI!”
\v 12 Marra tbehten uca nnan ijj i wenneɣni: “Min ixs ad yini man aya?”
\v 13 Maca inneɣni sthezzan zzaysen, nnan: “Nitni swin binu n jdid.”
\b
\s1 Abarreḥ n Buṭrus i řɣaci
\m 
\v 14 Awarni as ikkar Cimɛun Buṭrus, ak-d ḥiṭac n rrusul. Netta issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes, inna asen:
\b
\m “\add Kenniw\add*, \add a\add* iryazen d Udayen u marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ittxeṣṣa ad snem aya, sřem ɣar wawařen inu!
\v 15 \add Iwdan-a\add* war scaren ca am mammec d awem ittɣiř, minzi aqa-tt d tasaɛɛet d třata \add n wass\add*.
\v 16 Maca aya min ittwannan zeg unabi Yuwil:
\b
\m 
\v 17 \qt ‘Ad yiři deg wussan ineggura,\qt*
\m \qt iqqar AREBBI,\qt*
\m \qt aqa ad farrɣeɣ Arruḥ inu x marra ddat.\qt*
\m \qt Ad nebban iḥenjiren nwem d tḥenjirin nwem,\qt*
\m \qt ibřiɣen nwem ad twařan iweḥḥan,\qt*
\m \qt uca imeqqranen nwem ad arjan tirja.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Ica. 44:3; Ḥiz. 11:19; 36:27; Yuw. 3:1-5; Zak. 12:10; Lk. 2:36; Yḥ. 7:3; Řex. 10:45; 21:9. \x*
\m 
\v 18 \qt Uřa x imsexxaren inu u x tiyya inu\qt*
\m \qt ad farrɣeɣ Arruḥ inu deg wussan nni,\qt*
\m \qt uca ad nebban.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 19 \qt Ad wceɣ lmuɛjizat deg ujenna\qt*
\m \qt uřa d řeɛřamat x temmurt:\qt*
\m \qt idammen d tmessi d řefwar n ddexxan.\qt*
\m 
\v 20 \qt Ad tedweř tfuct ɣar taǧest,\qt*
\m \qt d tziri ɣar idammen,\qt*
\m \qt qbeř dd ɣa yas\qt*
\m \qt wass imɣaren iɛuǧen n SIDI.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt Mal. 3:23\x*
\m 
\v 21 \qt Uca ad yiři,\qt*
\m \qt aqa marra wi ɣa iřaɣan x Yisem n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt ad ittwassenjem!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt Yuw. 3:1-5; Rum. 10:13. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 \add A\add* iryazen, ayt n Israil, sřem awařen-a: Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri, aqa-t d Bnadem i d awem dd-ittwasscanen zi AREBBI s tmegga timeqqranin d řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat i yegga AREBBI s ufus nnes di řwesṭ nwem, am mammec tessnem kenniw,
\v 23 aqa Wanita, wenni ittwaḥuzen i man aya i Netta ɛlaḥsab tussna n AREBBI qbeř u ɛlaḥsab řxaḍar nnes, aqa kenniw tsellmem t deg ifassen n iɛeffanen u tṣellbem t u tenɣim t. \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt Řex. 4:28; 5:30. \x*
\v 24 Maca issnekkar i-t-i-dd AREBBI uca issarxu iseɣwan n řaxart, maɣar war izemmar ad ittwaṭṭef di řaxart. \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Řex. 10:40, 1 Ij. 3:16-28.\x*
\v 25 Minzi Dawud inna xas:
\b
\m \qt ‘Tuɣa ttwařiɣ Sidi zzati di kuř amur,\qt*
\m \qt aqa-t x yefus inu,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima war ttmeyyiřeɣ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Izhd. 16:8-11. \x*
\m 
\v 26 \qt S uya ifarreh uř inu\qt*
\m \qt uřa d asemɣar inu ifeyyeḍ s řefraḥet,\qt*
\m \qt uřa d arrimet inu ad yareyyeḥ\qt*
\m \qt x usitem \tl wanita\tl*,\qt*
\m 
\v 27 \qt minzi war tᵉttejjid řeɛmar inu di řaxart,\qt*
\m \qt uřa war tᵉttejjid Amsizdeg nnec ad ikiccu.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt Izhd. 16:10; Izhd. 49:10; Řex. 13:35 \x*
\m 
\v 28 \qt Cek tessecned ayi abrid n Tudart,\qt*
\m \qt Cek ad ayi teccured s řefraḥet\qt*
\m \qt di lḥaḍar nnec.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Izhd. 16:8-11. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 29 \add A\add* iryazen tawmat, aqa teɛdeř ayi ad awem ssiwřeɣ s bṭayṭay x arrays n řejdud \add nneɣ\add* Dawud, wenni aqa immut, ittwanḍeř, uca anḍeř nnes aqa-t ɣarneɣ ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 2:29 \xt 1 Ij. 2:10; Řex. 13:36. \x*
\v 30 Maɣar netta tuɣa d anabi, issen belli AREBBI ijjuǧ as s ict n tjaǧit:
\b
\m \qt ‘Ad ssɣimeɣ ijjen zi řɣiǧet n tɛeddist nnec\qt*
\m \qt x řkursi n řɛarc nnes.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:30 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Lk. 1:32; Řex. 13:23; Rum. 1:3; 2 Tim. 2:8. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 31 Ammu tuɣa netta izwar iẓra uca issiweř x tnukra n Lmasiḥ, belli war ittwajji ca di řaxart uca arrimet nnes war tᵉttaci akiccu. \x ◘ \xo 2:31 \xt Izhd. 16:10; Řex. 13:35. \x*
\v 32 Yasuɛ wanita aqa issnekkar i-t-i-dd AREBBI u neccin marra d řechud nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:32 \xt Yḥ. 15:27; Řex. 1:8. \x*
\v 33 Netta ittwassgeɛɛed ař \add a\add*fus afusi n AREBBI uca iṭṭef lwaɛd n Arruḥ Iqeddsen zi Babas. Aqa ifarreɣ tawhibt-a \add řexxu\add* am mammec tᵉttwařam u tᵉttesřam. \x ◘ \xo 2:33 \xt Řex. 1:4; 5:31; 10:45; Fil. 2:9. \x*
\v 34 Dawud maca war igeɛɛed ca ɣar ijenwan, maɣar inna:
\b
\m \qt ‘SIDI inna i Sidi inu:\qt*
\m \qt Qqim x yefus inu,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:34 \xt Izhd. 110:1; 1 Kur. 15:25; Afa. 1:20; Ɛbr. 1:13. \x*
\m 
\v 35 \qt ař d ɣa ggeɣ řɛedyan nnec\qt*
\m \qt d tanebdat sadu iḍaren nnec.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:35 \xt Izhd. 110:1. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 36 Ad tessen marra taddart n Israil nican, belli AREBBI igga Yasuɛ wanita, wenni tṣellbem kenniw, d SIDI d Lmasiḥ.”
\b
\m 
\v 37 Řami sřin man aya, tudef asen deg wuř nsen daxeř, nnan i Cimɛun u i rrusul nneɣni: “Min ɣa negg, a tawmat nneɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 2:37 \xt Zak. 12:10; Lk. 3:10; Řex. 9:6; 16:30. \x*
\v 38 Inna asen Cimɛun: “Tubem, ejj kuř ijjen zzaywem ad ittwasseɣḍeṣ s Yisem n SIDI Yasuɛ i weɣfar n ddnub, uca ad tqebřem tawhibt n Arruḥ Iqeddsen.
\v 39 Minzi lwaɛd i kenniw u i tarwa nwem u i marra inni iǧan ɣar řaggʷaj, inni x i d ɣa iřaɣa AREBBI nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 2:39 \xt Yuw. 3:1; Afa. 2;13. \x*
\v 40 Uca s wawařen nneɣni aṭṭas tuɣa isseqneɛ u iɛřem asen, inna: “Nejmem zi taṣiřet-a ifarɣen.”
\v 41 Tuɣa jar asen inni iwejden ad qebřen awař nnes uca ttwassɣeḍṣen nitni. Mmarnin-dd deg wass nni ɛřaḥař teřt-ařaf n řeɛmur.
\b
\s1 Tamesmunt n yenni yumnen di Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 42 Nitni qqimen ṣbaren di tɣuri n rrusul u carrcen di tẓaǧit u di tareẓẓit n weɣrum n nniɛmet.
\m 
\v 43 Kuř ijjen tudef i-t tiggʷudi uca msarent lmuɛjizat d řeɛřamat aṭṭas s ifassen n rrusul di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 2:43 \xt Mk. 16:17; Řex. 5:12. \x*
\v 44 Marra inni yumnen tuɣa aten munen jmiɛ, u marra min ɣarsen tuɣa icarc. \x ◘ \xo 2:44 \xt Aɛwd. 15:4; Řex. 4:32. \x*
\v 45 Inni ɣar iǧa wagřa tuɣa zznuzan man aya uca beṭṭan \add arbeḥ\add* ɛlaḥsab min iḥdaj kuř ijj. \x ◘ \xo 2:45 \xt Ica. 58:7; Řex. 4:35. \x*
\v 46 Tuɣa ttmunen kuř ass di Zzawect Tameqqrant s dmam d ijjen, ttareẓẓan aɣrum di tudrin, ksin macca nsen s řefraḥet u s wuř iṣfa, \x ◘ \xo 2:46 \xt Řex. 1:14; 20:7. \x*
\v 47 am ssemɣaran di AREBBI u tuɣa ttwassɛizzen ɣar marra iwdan. Kuř ass tuɣa Siditneɣ yarenni ɣar tmesmunt inni iwḍen ɣar Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 2:47 \xt Řex. 5:14; 11:21. \x*
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n uneɛḍab
\m 
\v 1 D man aya imsar umi geɛɛden Cimɛun Buṭrus d Yuḥanna jmiɛ ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant di tsaɛɛet n tẓaǧit tenni d wiss tesɛa, \add ixs ad yini d třata awarni ḍḍhur\add*.
\v 2 Xzar, tuɣa din ijj n weryaz d aneɛḍab zeg uɛeddis n yemmas, arbun t inni innumen ad t-i-dd-awyen, ssɣiman t ɣar tewwart n Zzawect Tameqqrant umi qqaren ‘Tawwart Taṣebḥant’, ḥima ad ittar ṣṣedqet zeg inni ittadfen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Yḥ. 9:8; Řex. 14:8. \x*
\v 3 Aqa wa, umi iẓra belli Cimɛun d Yuḥanna ttadfen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, ittar zzaysen ḥima ad as wcen ict n ṣṣedqet.
\v 4 Cimɛun ak-d Yuḥanna nḍaren dayes tiṭṭawin, nnan as: “Xzar dayneɣ!”
\v 5 Netta iqceɛ daysen, ittraja ad zzaysen iṭṭef ca.
\v 6 Inna as Cimɛun: “Nnuqart d wureɣ war ɣari ǧin, maca min ɣari d man aya i d ac ɣa wceɣ s Yisem n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ Nnaṣiri! Kkar, tuyured!” \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Řex. 4:10. \x*
\v 7 Iṭṭef i-t zeg ufus nnes afusi uca issnekkar i-t. Řexdenni menɛen iḍaren nnes d ticeɛbin nnes,
\v 8 uca ingez uca ibedd \add x iḍaren\add*, iggur uca yudef akidsen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, iggur, ineggez, issemɣara di AREBBI. \f ◼ \fr 3:8 \fk ineggez\ft - niɣ ‘ineṭṭu’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 Marra řgens iẓra i-t iggur, issemɣara di AREBBI.
\v 10 Ssnen \add iwdan\add* aqa netta d wenni tuɣa ittɣiman ittettar kuř ass ɣar Tewwart n Zzawect Tameqqrant umi qqaren ‘Taṣebḥant’ uca nitni dewřen ccuren s wedhac d utebhet x min d as imsaren.
\v 11 Am tuɣa \add aryaz aneɛḍab\add* ittcebbar di Cimɛun d Yuḥanna, dduqqzen xasen marra iwdan ɣar useqqif ak-d ukulwar d ipilaren, umi qqaren ‘aseqqif n Suliman’, tbehten.
\m 
\v 12 Umi iẓra Cimɛun aya, iṭṭef deg wawař, inna asen: “\add A\add* iryazen, iḥenjiren n Israil, min kenniw ideɛwen tᵉttbehtem s uya? Mayemmi dayneɣ tejɛarem axmi s jjehd n yixef nneɣ niɣ s ṣṣulṭa n yixef nneɣ narra i-t iggur?
\v 13 AREBBI n Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, AREBBI n řejdud nneɣ, aqa issɛuǧa Mmis Yasuɛ wenni tsellmem u tmenḍarem zzat n wudem n Pilaṭus wenni tuɣa xas iḥkem s ijj n řḥukm iseggden u tuɣa ixs ad as yarxu. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Uf. 3:6, 15; Mt. 27:20; Mk. 15:11; Lk. 23:18; Yḥ. 18:40. \x*
\v 14 Maca kenniw aqa temmenḍarem Amqeddas d Amseggad, tzawgem ad awem immewc aryaz aqettař. \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt Lk. 23:18. \x*
\v 15 Aqa tenɣim Azeǧif n Tudart, wenni dd-issnekkar AREBBI zi taddart n imettinen, aqa neccin marra d řechud x man aya. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Řex. 1:8; 2:32. \x*
\v 16 S l’iman deg Yisem nnes, aqa issejhed u issgenfa Netta wa, wenni tᵉttwařam, tessnem t. L’iman dayes aqa iwca as agenfi-ya zzatwem marra.
\m 
\v 17 Řexxu, \add a\add* aytma, ssneɣ, aqa teggim aya s tqubbanect, am mammec i ggin uřa d imeqqranen nwem.
\v 18 Ammu aqa ikemmeř AREBBI min tuɣa issizwar ixebbar xas s uqemmum n marra inabiyyen belli Lmasiḥ iggur ad iweddeb. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Ica. 50:6; 53:5; Lk. 24:27. \x*
\v 19 S uyenni tubem, tdewřem \add ɣar webrid\add* ḥima ad awem ttwamesḥen ddnub nwem uca xenni ad dd-asen zzmanat n arraḥet zzat i wudem n SIDI, \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Řex. 2:38. \x*
\v 20 uca Netta ad awem dd-issekk wenni iwejden i kenniw \add i man aya\add*: Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ,
\v 21 wenni ittxeṣṣa ujenna ad t iqbeř ař ukemmeř n zzmanat, n marra min xef tuɣa issawař AREBBI s uqemmum n marra inabiyyen nnes iqeddsen zi zzman.
\v 22 Maɣar Musa inna:
\b
\m \qt ‘SIDI ad awem dd-issgeɛɛed ijj n Unabi\qt*
\m \qt am necc zeg wawmatwem.\qt*
\m \qt I Netta umi ɣa tesřem\qt*
\m \qt di marra mixef d awem i ɣa issiweř.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Aɛwd. 18:15-16, 18; Yḥ. 1:46; Řex. 7:37. \x*
\m 
\v 23 \qt Ad yiři belli kuř řeɛmar\qt*
\m \qt i war isřin ɣar Unabi nni,\qt*
\m \qt ad ittwasshellek zeg řgens.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 24 Marra inabiyyen zi Camwil d \add marra inabiyyen\add* nni i-t-i-dd-ixeřfen, aqa izwaren xebbaren x wussan-a.
\v 25 Kenniw d ayt n inabiyyen u n Řɛahd i igga AREBBI ak-d řejdud nwem řami tuɣa iqqar i Ibrahim:
\b
\m \qt ‘S zzariɛet nnec ad ttwabarkent\qt*
\m \qt marra tiqebbař n temmurt!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:25 \xt Amz. 22:18; Gal. 3:8. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 26 Zic igga Netta \add Řɛahd nnes\add* akidwem uca issekk-dd AREBBI řexxu Mmis maḥend ad awem ibarek, mařa ad tdewřem, ad tᵉtubem zi řɣar nwem.”
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Buṭrus d Yuḥanna zzat i Jmaɛet Tameqqrant n Wudayen
\m 
\v 1 Am tuɣa ssawařen awařen-a ak-d řgens, xeccen-dd xasen ikehhanen ak-d Iṣaduqiyyen d imeqqranen x Zzawect Tameqqrant,
\v 2 minzi tuɣa xeyyqen xasen aṭṭas, maɣar nitni tuɣa sseřmaden řgens u ttbarrḥen tanukra zi taddart n imettinen s Lmasiḥ.
\v 3 Ssarsen xasen ifassen uca ḥebbsen ten ař tiwecca nnes, minzi tuɣa tewḍa-dd tmeddit.
\v 4 Aṭṭas zeg inni isřin awař-a umnen u řqedd n yeryazen yiweḍ-dd ɛřaḥař xemsa-ařaf.
\m 
\v 5 Tiwecca nnes munen imeqqranen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imseřmaden n idlisen di Urcalim,
\v 6 uřa d Ḥannan, arrays n ikehhanen, d Qayafa d Yuḥanna d Aliksandir d \add marra\add* inni tuɣa dd-iqqarṣen zi řaǧ n imeqqranen n ikehhanen.
\v 7 Umi ten ssbedden di řwesṭ, sseqsan ten: “S man jjehd niɣ s man isem i teggim aya?” \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Uf. 2:14; Mt. 21:23; Řex. 7:27. \x*
\v 8 Řexdenni inna asen Cimɛun Buṭrus iccuren s Arruḥ Iqeddsen: “Sřem, \add a\add* imeqqranen n řgens d imɣaren n taddart n Israil!
\v 9 Mařa ass-a nettwaḥkem zzaywem x řxar i ittwaggen i umehřuc, s min zi idweř weryaz-a iggenfa,
\v 10 ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem kenniw d marra řgens n Israil belli aryaz wanita ibedd zzatwem iṣeḥḥ s Yisem n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ Nnaṣiri, wenni tṣellbem, \add maca\add* wenni dd-issnekkar AREBBI zi taddart n imettinen, \add wah,\add* aqa zzayes ibedd \add aryaz-a\add* zzatwem iṣeḥḥ.
\v 11 D wa d Aẓru nni temmenḍarem \add kenniw\add*, \add a\add* ibennayen, \add maca\add* Netta aqa idweř d \add aẓru\add* Azeǧif n teɣmart. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Izhd. 118:22; Ica. 28:16; Mt. 21:42; Mk. 12:10; Lk. 20:17; Rum. 9:33; 1 Bṭ. 2:7. \x*
\v 12 Asenjem war iǧi s ijjen bnadem nneɣni, minzi war din Isem nneɣni sadu ujenna i zi ɣa nettwassenjem.” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Mt. 1:21; Řex. 10:43; 1 Tim. 2:5. \x*
\m 
\v 13 Řami sřin awařen i ssiwřen Cimɛun d Yuḥanna s bṭayṭay, uca ufin belli nitni war ǧin d imusnawen n Wedlis niɣ d iwdan inni iřemden aṭṭas, aqa tbehten uca ɛeqřen belli nitni tuɣa aten ak-d Yasuɛ.
\v 14 Nitni ẓrin bnadem i tuɣa d aneɛḍab uca idweř iggenfa, ibedd akidsen, uca war ufin min ɣa inin x man aya.
\v 15 U awarni řami umuren maḥend ad ten ssuffɣen barra i Jmaɛet nsen \add Tameqqrant\add*, mcawaren ak-d wayawya, \add nnan\add*: \f ◼ \fr 4:15 \fq ’Jmaɛet \bdit Tameqqrant\bdit*\ft - niɣ: ‘Jmaɛet n řḥukkam imeqqranen n Wudayen’.\f*
\v 16 “Min ɣa negg s iryazen-a? Minzi aqa iban-dd mliḥ i marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim belli řeɛřamet temsar s ufus nsen, war nzemmar ad tt nenkar. \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt Yḥ. 11:47. \x*
\v 17 Maca ḥima war ittwabarreḥ řexbar-a ktar jar weydud, ejj aneɣ ad ten nessiggʷed ḥima war ssiwiřen ɛemmarṣ ɛawed deg Yisem-a, uřa ak-d ijj n bnadem.”
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* řaɣan-dd xasen, umuren ten maḥend war ssiwiřen war sseřmiden ɛemmarṣ ɛad deg Yisem n Yasuɛ.
\m 
\v 19 Maca Cimɛun Buṭrus d Yuḥanna arrin-dd xasen, nnan asen: “Ḥekmem kenniw, ma iḥiqq zzat i AREBBI maḥend ad nseř ktar i kenniw x AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Řex. 5:29. \x*
\v 20 minzi war nzemmar ad neqqim war nessiwiř x min neẓra u x min nesřa.”
\v 21 Maca nitni ssiggʷeden ten \add ɛad ktar\add*, xenni jjin ten ad raḥen, ařami war ufin min zi ten i ɣa ɛaqben zi ssibbet n iwdan, minzi marra \add iwdan\add* tuɣa ssemɣaran di AREBBI x min imsaren, \x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt Řex. 3:7, 8; 5:26. \x*
\v 22 minzi aryaz i dayes ittwagg řeɛřamet-a n ugenfi, tuɣa ɣares ktar zi arebɛin n iseggʷusa.
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit n řmuminin
\m 
\v 23 Awarni řami d asen arxun, ruḥen nitni ɣar aytmatsen uca xebbaren ten s marra min d asen nnan imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:23 \xt Řex. 12:12. \x*
\v 24 Umi sřin aya, ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen ɣar AREBBI s dmam d ijjen, nnan: “\add A\add* SIDI, Cek d AREBBI wenni iggin ajenna d temmurt d řebḥur d marra min dayes, \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt Uf. 20:11\x*
\v 25 Cek d Wenni innan s Arruḥ Iqeddsen s uqemmum n umsexxar nnec Dawud:
\b
\m \qt ‘Mayemmi ɣewwɣen řegnus\qt*
\m \qt u \tl mayemmi\tl* xarrṣen řegnus di min ixwan?\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:25 \xt Izhd. 2:1. \x*
\m 
\v 26 \qt Aqa kkaren ijeǧiden n ddunect,\qt*
\m \qt uca inni ɣarsen teǧa ṣṣulṭa mcawaren\qt*
\m \qt ḍidd n SIDI u ḍidd n Lmasiḥ nnes.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:26 \xt Izhd. 2:1, 2. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 27 Minzi s tidett aqa Hirudus d Punṭiyus Pilaṭus d řegnus d ibarruten n Israil munen x Mmic nnec amqeddas Yasuɛ, wenni umi tmesḥed, \x ◘ \xo 4:27 \xt Mt. 26:3; Mk. 14:1; Lk. 22:2; Yḥ. 11:47. \x*
\v 28 ḥima ad ggen marra min tuɣa izwar ineyyec ufus nnec d ccwar nnec ad yiři.
\v 29 Ɛad řexxu, a SIDI, xzar ɣar usiggʷed nsen uca ewc i imsexxaren nnec ḥima ad ssiwřen s wawař nnec s taryast,
\v 30 am tesswiẓẓḍed afus nnec i usgenfi u ḥima ad \add din\add* iřint timegga jehdent d řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb deg Yisem n Mmic nnec amqeddas: Yasuɛ.” \x ◘ \xo 4:30 \xt Mk. 16:17. \x*
\v 31 Awarni řami kemmřen taẓaǧit d tkessit s řmeɛruf, inhezz wemcan i di tuɣa munen, u marra dewřen ccuren s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, ssawařen s Wawař n AREBBI s teryast. \x ◘ \xo 4:31 \xt Řex. 16:26. \x*
\b
\s1 Beddu n Tmesmunt n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 32 Uca řɣaci n yinni yumnen tuɣa s řeɛmar d uxarreṣ d ijjen uca uřa d ijj war iqqar belli min tuɣa ɣares aqa i netta weḥḥdes, maca nitni carcen di kuřci jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 4:32 \xt Řex. 2:44; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*
\v 33 Tuɣa rrusul nni cehhden s yijj n jjehd imɣar x tnukra n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ uca yiweḍ-dd arḍa imɣar x marra nitni.
\v 34 War tuɣi jar asen uřa d ijj dayes řexṣeṣ, minzi marra inni ɣar iǧa iyyaren niɣ tudrin zznuzan ten, uca ttawyen-dd ttaman n min zznuzan,
\v 35 ssrusan t ɣar iḍaren n rrusul. Nitni bḍan \add zzayes\add* i kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab min tuɣa iḥwaj. \x ◘ \xo 4:35 \xt Ica. 58:7. \x*
\m 
\v 36 Yusuf wenni umi řaɣan rrusul Bar-Naba\add s\add*, min ixs ad yini ‘mmis n ufewwej’, netta \add zi teqbič\add* n Lawi, yusa-dd zi tegzirt n Qubrus,
\v 37 tuɣa ɣares ijj n iyyar, izzenz i-t uca yiwi-dd tmenyat, issars i-tent ɣar iḍaren n rrusul.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Řḥukm x Ananiyas d Saffira
\m 
\v 1 Ijj n weryaz qqaren as Ananiyas, ak-d temɣart nnes, qqaren as Saffira, izzenz iyyar nnes.
\v 2 Netta iksi ijj n wezyen n tmenyat n ttaman \add n yeyyar\add*, am tessen temɣart nnes \add man aya\add*, uca issnufar i-t. \add Xas uca\add* yiwi-dd ca n tmenyat n nnuqart zzayes, issars i-tt ɣar iḍaren n rrusul.
\v 3 Inna as Cimɛun: “\add A\add* Ananiyas, mayemmi iccur cciṭan uř nnec ḥima ad tessxarqed x Arruḥ Iqeddsen u ḥima ad tnuffared ca n tmenyat deg iyyar?
\v 4 Ma war iǧi \add yiyyar\add* nnec qbeř ittwammenz? U řami ittwammenz, tuɣa ṣṣulṭa x ttaman nnes \add ɛad\add* deg ufus nnec! Min cek ideɛwen tᵉttegged man aya deg wuř nnec? Aqa cek war tessxarqed ca x iwdan maca x AREBBI.”
\v 5 Umi isřa Ananiyas awařen-a, iwḍa ɣar temmurt, immut, uca tedweř tiggʷudi temɣar x marra inni isřin aya.
\v 6 Kkaren ibřiɣen, cefnen t, arbun \add t\add* ɣar barra, neḍřen t.
\m 
\v 7 Awarni řami ɛdunt ɛřaḥař třata n tsaɛɛetin, tudef-dd temɣart nnes, war tessin min imsaren.
\v 8 Inna as Cimɛun: “Ini ayi, ma aqa tezzenzem iyyar s wanect uya?” Tenna as: “Wah, s wanect uya!”
\v 9 Inna as Cimɛun: “Min kenniw ideɛwen tᵉttafqem jar awem maḥend ad tjarrbem Arruḥ n SIDI? Xzar, iḍaren n yinni ineḍřen aryaz nnem, aqa aten ɣar tewwart, ad cem ksin barra ɛawed.”
\v 10 Řexdenni tewḍa ɣar iḍaren nnes uca temmut. Udfen-dd ibřiɣen nni, ufin tt temmut, ksin tt, arbun tt ɣar barra uca neḍřen tt zzat i weryaz nnes,
\v 11 uca tedweř tiggʷudi temɣar ɣar marra tamesmunt u ɣar marra inni isřin man aya.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Msarent waṭṭas n řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb jar iwdan s ifassen n rrusul uca marra nitni tuɣa munen s wuř d ijjen deg useqqif ak-d ukulwar d ipilaren n Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Mk. 16:17; Řex. 2:43. \x*
\v 13 Maca zeg iwdan inneɣni war izɛim ḥed ad kisen igg azeǧif, maca řgens iweqqar ten aṭṭas.
\v 14 Mmarenyen-dd ktar ɛad ɣar yinni yumnen di SIDI, ibarruten n yeryazen d temɣarin,
\v 15 ařami tuɣa kessin imehřac barra ɣar zznaqi, ssrusan ten x tassut ḥima, xmi dd ɣa yas Cimɛun, balak ad tekk mɣir tiři nnes xasen.
\v 16 Usin-dd uřa d aṭṭas zi tneddam nneɣni i d as dd-innḍen i Urcalim, iwyen-dd imehřac nsen d yinni daysen řaryaḥ imengas, uca marra ggenfan. \x ◘ \xo 5:16 \xt Mk. 16:17; Řex. 8:7; 16:18; 19:12. \x*
\b
\s1 Buṭrus d Yuḥanna barrḥen di Temzida Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 17 Arrays n ikehhanen d marra inni iǧan akides, inni iǧan zi tebridt n Iṣaduqiyyen, dewřen ccuren s řeḥsed.
\v 18 Nitni ssarsen ifassen x rrusul, ṭṭfen ten uca arrin ten di řeqyud di řeḥbes.
\v 19 Maca lmalak n SIDI yarzem tiwwura n řeḥbes s ǧiřet, issuffeɣ i-ten ɣar barra, inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Řex. 12:7; 16:26. \x*
\v 20 “Ruḥem, xenni tbeddem di Zzawect Tameqqrant, siwřem i řgens s marra awařen-a n Tudart!”
\m 
\v 21 Ffɣen-dd nitni ɣar wenqar n tfuct, udfen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, bdan sseřmaden. Maca ikkar-dd arrays n ikehhanen d yinni akides iǧan, uca řaɣan x yinni ibedden akidsen u x imɣaren n ayt n Israil, uca ssekken \add imsexxaren nsen\add* ɣar řeḥbes ḥima ad ten dd-awyen.
\v 22 Umi dd-ffɣen inni \add zzaysen\add* dd-ittwassekken \add dinni\add*, war ten ufin ca di řeḥbes, uca ɛeqben, nnan:
\v 23 “Aqa nufa řeḥbes ibelleɛ mliḥ u iɛessasen bedden barra ɣar tewwura, \add maca\add* umi narzem tawwart, war din nufi ḥed daxeř.”
\m 
\v 24 Řami sřin imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imeqqranen n Zzawect Tameqqrant awařen-a, tbehten aṭṭas, iweddar asen min ɣa ggen.
\v 25 Uca yusa-dd ijj n weryaz ixebbar i-ten, \add iqqar\add*: “Xzar, iryazen nni teggim di řeḥbes, aqa bedden di Zzawect Tameqqrant, sseřmaden iwdan!”
\b
\m 
\v 26 Řexdenni ruḥen \add din\add* řquyad ak-d iɛessasen, iwyen ten-dd, war t ggin s uɣiř minzi tuɣa ggʷeden aqa řgens ad ten iḥejjar. \x ◘ \xo 5:26 \xt Mt. 21:26; Řex. 4:21. \x*
\v 27 Umi ten dd-iwyen, ssbedden ten zzat i marra Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*. Isseqsa ten arrays n ikehhanen, iqqar:
\v 28 “Ma war kenniw numur s jjehd maḥend war tessɣaram uřa d ijjen s Yisem-a? U xzar, aqa kenniw teccurem Urcalim s tɣuri nwem, kenniw texsem ad xaneɣ tarrem Idammen n Bnadem-a!” \x ◘ \xo 5:28 \xt Mt. 27:25; Řex. 4:18. \x*
\m 
\v 29 Cimɛun d rrusul arrin-dd, nnan: “Ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad nᵉttaɛ AREBBI ktar zeg iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 5:29 \xt Řex. 4:19. \x*
\v 30 AREBBI n řejdud nneɣ issnekkar-dd Yasuɛ wenni tenɣim kenniw, tuyřem t x tefřawt. \x ◘ \xo 5:30 \xt Aɛwd. 21:23; Řex. 3:15; 10:39; 13:29; 1 Bṭ. 2:24. \x*
\v 31 AREBBI igga i-t d Azeǧif d wenni itticen Tudart, uca issgeɛɛed i-t ɣar ufus nnes ufusi maḥend ad iwc ttubet d weɣfar n ddnub i Israil. \x ◘ \xo 5:31 \xt Řex. 2:33; 3:15; Fil. 2:9. \x*
\v 32 Neccin d řechud x man aya uca uřa d Arruḥ Iqeddsen, i yewca AREBBI i yinni dayes yumnen.” \x ◘ \xo 5:32 \xt Yḥ. 15:27; Řex. 2:4. \x*
\v 33 Řami sřin aya, hajen aṭṭas uca ttemcawaren ḥima ad ten nɣen.
\m 
\v 34 Maca ikkar ijjen zeg Ifarisiyyen, qqaren as Gamaliyal. Netta d amseřmad n Ccariɛa u marra řgens ittweqqar i-t. Yumur netta ḥima ad nedhen rrusul ɣar barra i cwayt n řweqt.
\v 35 Inna asen: “\add A\add* iryazen, ayt n Israil, ḥḍam ixef nwem, xzarem mliḥ aqa \add marra\add* min ɣa teggem s iwdan-a ad yiři s řḥeqq.
\v 36 Minzi qbeř řweqt-a tuɣa ikkar Tuddas, inna aqa netta d ca, řeṣqen dayes ɛřaḥař ca n arebɛa-mya n yeryazen. Aqa nɣin t u marra inni tuɣa t iḍeffaren, dewřen ttwazuzzaren, ikemmeř array nsen. \x ◘ \xo 5:36 \xt Řex. 21:38. \x*
\v 37 Awarni man aya ikkar Yahuda Ajalili deg wussan n uzemmem i uxeǧeṣ n ḍḍariba i kuř uzeǧif \add i Zzawect Tameqqrant\add*, uca isseɣwa aṭṭas \add n iwdan\add* di řgens awarni as. Uca netta immut uca marra inni i-t-i-dd-iḍfaren, dewřen ttwazeǧɛen.
\v 38 Řexxu ad awem iniɣ: “Sbeɛɛdem ixef nwem x iwdan-a, jjem ten ad raḥen, minzi mařa axarreṣ-a niɣ řxedmet-a zeg iwdan i yeǧa, xenni ad iqḍa. \x ◘ \xo 5:38 \xt Awřn. 21:30; Ica. 8:10; Mt. 15:13. \x*
\v 39 Maca mařa tuɣa-t zi AREBBI, war tzemmarem ad t tbeṭṭřem, ḥima ad taɣ kenniw war tᵉttwifim d inni ittmenɣan ak-d AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 5:39 \xt Řex. 9:5; 23:9. \x*
\v 40 Ggin ad ttwassqenɛen zzayes uca awarni řami d řaɣan x rrusul, jjin ad ten hettken s urekkuḍ, ɛeřmen asen ḥima war ssiwiřen ɛad s Yisem n Yasuɛ, xenni arxun asen.
\m 
\v 41 Nitni ruḥen zzaysen, farḥen řami \add ufin belli nitni\add* ttwaḥesben ad sdaheǧen abehdeř di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:41 \xt Mt. 5:12. \x*
\v 42 War ssbedden ca zeg useřmad di mkuř ass di Zzawect Tameqqrant u di tudrin u zeg ubarreḥ s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Řixḍaret n sebɛa imsexxaren n řmuminin
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni, řami tuɣa ktaren imeḥḍaren aṭṭas, aqa imeḥḍaren inni ɣarsen iřes n Iyunaniyyen ɛeksen inni ɣarsen iřes n Tɛibranit minzi tijjař nsen farrḍen daysent di tsexxart \add n zzad\add* n kuř ass.
\v 2 \add S uya\add* řaɣan tenɛac n rrusul x marra agraw n imeḥḍaren maḥend ad munen, nnan asen: “War iɛeddeř ad nsexxar ṭṭwabeř \add i macca\add* am nᵉttejja deg Wawař n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Uf. 18:17. \x*
\v 3 Arzum xenni, \add a\add* aytma, u xḍarem sebɛa n yeryazen zzaywem inni ɣar teǧa cchadet \add tecna\add*, ccuren s Arruḥ n SIDI d tiɣit, uca neccin ad ten nkellef \add xenni\add* s tmesřact-a. \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Aɛwd. 1:13; Řex. 1:21; 16:2; 1 Tim. 3:7. \x*
\v 4 Maca neccin ad neṣbar di tẓaǧit u di tsexxart n Wawař.”
\v 5 Iɛjeb wawař-a i marra řɣaci uca nitni ixḍaren Stifanus, ijj n weryaz iccuren s l’iman d Arruḥ Iqeddsen, \add xenni\add* Filippus d Pruxurus d Nikanur d Timun d Parminas d Nikulas, ijj n umɛacar n ddin n Wudayen zi Antiyuxiya. \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Řex. 11:24; 21:8. \x*
\v 6 Ssbedden ten qibač i rrusul uca, awarni řami ẓẓuǧen, ssarsen xasen ifassen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Řex. 1:23; 8:17; 13:3; 1 Tim. 4:14; 5:22; 2 Tim. 1:6. \x*
\m 
\v 7 Tuɣa Awař n AREBBI iggam u řqedd n imeḥḍaren di Urcalim tuɣa imeqqar aṭṭas. Ijj n ubarru d ameqqran n Wudayen iṭaɛ i l’iman. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Řex. 19:20. \x*
\b
\s1 Uḍuf n Stifanus
\m 
\v 8 Stifanus, iccur s arḍa d jjehd, tuɣa ittegg řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb mɣarent jar řgens.
\v 9 Kkaren yeryazen zi temzida umi qqaren ‘Alibertinu’, \add iryazen zi\add* Qayrawan d Iskandariyya, uřa zi Kilikiya d Asiya, uca nitni tuɣa ttqacaḥen Stifanus. \f ◼ \fr 6:9 \fk Alibertinu\ft - iwdan qqaren belli Ilibirtiniyyen d ca n Israiliyyen i tuɣa ḥebbsen-ten Irumaniyyen iwyen ten ɣar tendint n Ruma. Menbaɛd ḍeȓqen-asen-dd, ssufɣen-ten zi Ruma, uca ɛeqben-dd ɣar Israil d imucan nneɣni. (Řex. 6:9).\f*
\v 10 \add Maca\add* war zemmaren ad ɛeksen tiɣit d Arruḥ i zzayes tuɣa issawař. \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt Uf. 4:12; Ica. 54:17; Lk. 21:15. \x*
\v 11 Řexdenni ssekken iryazen, ɛarrnen ten maḥend ad inin: “Aqa nesřa asen ssawařen s wawařen iceqqfen di Musa u di AREBBI!” \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Mt. 26:59. \x*
\v 12 Aqa ssɣewwɣen řgens d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imseřmaden n idlisen uca umi xas dd-dduqqzen, ṭṭfen t, nedhen t ɣar Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*.
\v 13 Ggin řechud issxarriqen, inni innan: “Bnadem-a war issbeddi ad iceqqef di Ccariɛa u deg wemcan-a iqeddsen,
\v 14 minzi nesřa as iqqar belli Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri wanita ad yareddeǧ amcan-a, ad ibeddeř ṭṭbayeɛ i d aneɣ iwca Musa.”
\m 
\v 15 Marra inni tuɣa ɣar iǧa řkursi di Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*, ḥekkaren dayes u ẓrin aɣembub nnes am uɣembub n ijj n lmalak.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Awař n Stifanus zzat i Jmaɛet Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Arrays n ikehhanen inna: “Ma man aya d tidett?”
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna \add Stifanus\add*:
\b
\m “A kenniw, \add a\add* iryazen, aytmatneɣ d ibabaten nneɣ, sřem! AREBBI n uɛuǧi iḍhar i jedditneɣ Ibrahim am tuɣa ɛad di Misuputamya, \add tenni d tammurt jar tnayen n iɣezran\add*, qbeř ma ad izdeɣ di Ḥaran.
\v 3 Netta inna as: ‘Ffeɣ zi temmurt nnec u zi řaǧ nnec, ruḥ ɣar temmurt tenni i d ac ɣa ssecneɣ.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Amz. 12:1. \x*
\v 4 Řexdenni iffeɣ Ibrahim zi temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen uca izdeɣ di Haran. Awarni řami immut babas, issmuṭṭiy i-t-i-dd AREBBI ɣar temmurt-a i di tzeddɣem ass-a.
\v 5 Netta war d as iwci ca dayes řwart uřa d ijj n uṣurif n uḍar, \add maca\add* iwaɛd ad as tt iwc d řwart, i netta u i zzariɛet nnes awarni as, am war tuɣi ɣares ɛad mmis. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15. \x*
\v 6 Issiweř AREBBI akides, inna as: ‘Ad tiři zzariɛet nnec d amɛezzeb deg ict n temmurt teɣribt, uca nitni ad ten arren d isemɣan, ad daysen ɣezzan arebɛa-mya n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Amz. 15:13-14, 16; Uf. 12:40; Gal. 3:17. \x*
\v 7 Uca řgens i d as ɣa ɛebden am yisemɣan, ad t ḥasbeɣ.’ Uca yarni AREBBI deg wawař nnes, inna: ‘Awarni man aya ad ffɣen, ad ayi ɛebden deg wemcan-a’. \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Amz. 15:16; Uf. 3:12. \x*
\v 8 Netta iwca as řɛahd n wextan. Xas uca ijja-dd Isḥaq uca ixten i-t deg wass wiss tmenya uca Isḥaq ijja-dd Yaɛqub, Yaɛqub ijja-dd tenɛac n řejdud \add imezwura\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt Amz. 21:2; 25:24; 29:32; 30:5; 35:23. \x*
\m 
\v 9 Řejdud \add imezwura\add* ɣarren zi Yusuf uca zzenzen t ɣar Miṣra. \add Maca\add* AREBBI tuɣa-t akides, \x ◘ \xo 7:9 \xt Amz. 37:3, 28; Izhd. 105:17. \x*
\v 10 issenjem i-t zi marra řemḥayem nnes. Netta iwca as arḍa d tiɣit qibač i firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, uca wanita igga i-t d azeǧif x Miṣra u x marra taddart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Amz. 41:40. \x*
\v 11 \add Maca\add* yusa-dd řaẓ d ict n řmeḥnet temɣar di marra tammurt n Miṣra u di temmurt n Kenɛan, war tuɣi i řejdud nneɣ ḥima ad jiwnen. \x ◘ \xo 7:11 \xt Amz. 41:54; Izhd. 105:16. \x*
\v 12 Maca umi isřa Yaɛqub belli aqa din \add ɛad\add* min iqqimen \add n řḥebb\add* di Miṣra, issekk řejdud nneɣ \add dinni\add* i umur amezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt Amz. 42:1. \x*
\v 13 Řami din ruḥen i umur wiss tnayen isseḍhar Yusuf ixef nnes i yaytmas uca yargeb firɛun x řaǧ n Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt Amz. 45:4. \x*
\v 14 Issekk Yusuf, yumur maḥend ad dd-yas babas Yaɛqub d marra řaǧ nnes: xemsa u-sebɛin n řeɛmur.
\v 15 Ihwa-dd Yaɛqub ɣar Miṣra, immut netta d řejdud nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt Amz. 46:5; 49:33. \x*
\v 16 Iwyen t ɣar Cakim, ssarsen t deg wenḍeř nni isɣa Ibrahim s yijj n ttaman n nnuqart zeg ayt n Ḥamur, babas n Cakim. \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Amz. 23:16; 50:13; Uf. 13:19; Yac. 24:32. \x*
\m 
\v 17 Maca ařami dd-tiweḍ řweqt i tuɣa iwaɛd zzayes AREBBI i Ibrahim s ict n tjaǧit, tuɣa igam řgens, idweř ijhed di Miṣra, \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Uf. 1:7; Izhd. 105:24. \x*
\v 18 ařami dd-ikkar ijj n ujeǧid nneɣni x Miṣra i tuɣa war issinen Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt Uf. 1:8\x*
\v 19 Wanita tuɣa ittegg s řeɣdar ak-d jjadira nneɣ uca iɣezza x řejdud nneɣ. Yumur i-ten maḥend ad nḍaren iseyman nsen ḥima war ttɣimin ad ddaren.
\m 
\v 20 Di řweqt nni ixřeq-dd Musa, yusa as-dd x řxaḍar i AREBBI. Sseymen t di taddart n babas třata n iyuren. \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Uf. 2:2; 6:19; Řxř. 26:59; 1 Im. 23:13; Ɛbr. 11:23. \x*
\v 21 Řami ittwammenḍar zeg yemmas \add deg iɣzar\add*, tufa i-t yeǧis n firɛun, tesseyem i-t am mammec \add iǧa\add* d mmis n yixef nnes.
\v 22 Ittwassɣar Musa di marra tiɣit n Imiṣriyyen uca tuɣa ittqedda x wawař u x min tuɣa ittegg.
\m 
\v 23 Ařami ɣares arebɛin n iseggʷusa, iḍar-dd xas deg wuř nnes maḥend ad yarzef aytmas, ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt Uf. 2:11-15. \x*
\v 24 Umi iẓra aqa ḍeǧen ijjen zeg aytmas zi teqbič nnes, ixřef zzayes di ṭṭweɛ nnes, igga ixef nnes d řqaḍi di ssibbet nnes uca inɣa Amiṣri nni t iḍeǧen.
\v 25 Tuɣa ittraja belli tawmat nnes, ayt n Israil, ad fehmen aqa AREBBI ad asen issiwiḍ asenjem s ufus nnes, maca nitni war fhimen.
\m 
\v 26 Deg wass awarni as iḍhar asen-dd ɛawed, řami tuɣa ttmenɣan. Iɛřem asen maḥend ad messeṣřaḥen, iqqar: ‘\add A\add* iryazen, kenniw d awmaten, mayemmi tɛeddam ijjen x wenneɣni?’
\v 27 Wenni tuɣa ittɛeddan x umeddukkeř nnes, iɛarren i-t, iqqar: ‘Wi cek iggin xaneɣ d azeǧif d řqaḍi? \x ◘ \xo 7:27 \xt Mt. 21:23; Řex. 7:35; 4:7. \x*
\v 28 Ma ad taɣ ad texsed ad ayi tenɣed am mammec tenɣid iḍennaḍ Amiṣri?’ \x ◘ \xo 7:28 \xt Uf. 2:14. \x*
\v 29 Řexdenni yarweř Musa di ssibbet n wawař-a uca idweř d amɛezzeb di temmurt n Midyan mani dd-yejja tnayen iḥenjiren.
\m 
\v 30 Awarni řami ɛdun i netta arebɛin n iseggʷusa, iban as-dd lmalak n SIDI di řexřa n wedrar n Sina di tmessi itteḥduduqen di cbarq ak-d isennanen. \x ◘ \xo 7:30 \xt Uf. 3:2 \x*
\v 31 Umi iẓra Musa man aya, itebhet s řewḥiy i iẓra, uca umi dd-iqarreb ḥima ad iẓar, inna as SIDI s ict n tmijja:
\v 32 ‘Aqa d NECC, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, AREBBI n Ibrahim, n Isḥaq u n Yaɛqub!’ Ibda Musa ittarjiji aṭṭas, war izɛim ad ixzar ɣar řewḥiy. \x ◘ \xo 7:32 \xt Uf. 3:6; Mt. 22:32; Ɛbr. 11:16. \x*
\v 33 Inna as SIDI: ‘Kkes sandaliyat nnec zeg iḍaren nnec, minzi tammurt mixef tbedded tqeddes \add i teǧa\add*.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:33 \xt Uf. 3:5, 7, 8, 10; Yac. 5:15. \x*
\v 34 Aqa ẓriɣ řmeḥnet n řgens inu di Miṣra uca sřiɣ i uzehhar nsen, hwiɣ-dd ḥima ad ten ssnejmeɣ. Uca řexxu, as-dd da, ad dd cek ssekkeɣ ɣar Miṣra.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:34 \xt Uf. 3:2-10. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Musa wanita, wenni inḍaren nitni umi nnan: ‘Wi cek iggin xaneɣ d azeǧif d řqaḍi?’, wanita issekk i-t i-dd AREBBI ɣarsen d azeǧif d umsenjem s ufus n lmalak nni d as dd-iḍharen di cbarq ak-d isennanen.
\v 36 Wanita issuffeɣ i-ten \add zi Miṣra\add* am igga řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb d tmegga timeqqranin di temmurt n Miṣra, ɣar Řebḥar n Uɣanim u di řexřa řmijař n arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 7:36 \xt Uf. 7; 8; 9; 10; 11; 13; 14; 16:1; Aɛwd. 1:3. \x*
\v 37 Wa d Musa wenni innan i ayt n Israil: ‘SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad awem dd-issgeɛɛed ijj n Unabi am necc zi tawmat nwem. I Netta umi ittxeṣṣa ad tesřam!’ \x ◘ \xo 7:37 \xt Aɛwd. 18:15, 18; Yḥ. 1:46; Řex. 3:22; Mt. 17:5. \x*
\v 38 Wanita tuɣa-t di tmesmunt n řgens di řexřa ak-d lmalak wenni tuɣa akides issawařen x wedrar n Sina uřa ak-d řejdud nneɣ. Aqa netta tuɣa itteṭṭef awařen n Tudart ḥima ad aneɣ ten yewc. \x ◘ \xo 7:38 \xt Uf. 19:3; Gal. 3:19. \x*
\v 39 \add Maca\add* řejdud nneɣ war xsen ad as mmarsen ixef nsen, maca sstewwjen t xasen uca ɛeqben ɣar Miṣra deg wuřawen nsen.
\v 40 Maɣar nnan i Harun: ‘Egg aneɣ irebbiten inni d aneɣ i ɣa izwaren, minzi Musa wanita wenni d aneɣ igewwden zi temmurt n Miṣra, war nessin min d as imsaren.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:40 \xt Uf. 32:1, 23. \x*
\v 41 Ggin ijj n ufunas n ṣṣanam i yixef nsen deg wussan nni, ssgeɛɛden tiɣarṣa i l’aṣnam uca farḥen s min ggin ifassen nsen.
\v 42 AREBBI iwca \add asen\add* s weɛrur uca yarra i-ten ad ɛebden řɛeskarat n ujenna am mammec tuɣa tura deg wedlis n inabiyyen:
\b
\m \qt ‘Mayemmi tiwyem ayi-dd\qt*
\m \qt zeɛma immudaren d tiɣarṣa\qt*
\m \qt arebɛin n iseggʷusa di řexřa,\qt*
\m \qt \tl a\tl* ayt n Israil?\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:42 \xt Ɛam. 5:25. \x*
\m 
\v 43 \qt Aqa tiwyem-dd tazeddiɣt n Malkum,\qt*
\m \qt d itri n arebbi Rimfan,\qt*
\m \qt řexyařat i teggim ḥima ad tent tɛebdem.\qt*
\m \qt Necc ad kenniw ssbeɛɛdeɣ\qt*
\m \qt aɣirin qaɛ i Babil.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:43 \xt Ɛam. 5:26, 27. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 44 Tazeddiɣt n Cchadet n řejdud nneɣ tuɣa-tt di řexřa am mammec tuɣa yumur Netta wenni tuɣa issawař ak-d Musa maḥend ad tt igg x umedya i d as isscen. \x ◘ \xo 7:44 \xt Uf. 25:40; Ɛbr. 8:5. \x*
\v 45 Řejdud nneɣ ak-d Yacuwa ssidfen Tazeddiɣt-a ɣar temmurt nni d asen iwca AREBBI d řwart zi řegnus, \add řegnus\add* nni issuffeɣ i-ten AREBBI qibač i uɣembub nsen, u nitni arbun tt ař wussan n Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 7:45 \xt Yac. 3:14. \x*
\v 46 Wanita yufa arḍa ɣar AREBBI uca ittar \add as\add* ad yaf ict n Tzeddiɣt i AREBBI n Yaɛqub. \x ◘ \xo 7:46 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:1; 2 Ṣm. 7:2; 1 Im. 17:1; Izhd. 89:21; 132:5; Řex. 13:22. \x*
\v 47 Maca Suliman ibna as Taddart. \x ◘ \xo 7:47 \xt 1 Ij. 6:1; 1 Im. 17:12. \x*
\v 48 Maca Amɛuǧi x kuřci war izeddeɣ deg \add ict n tzeddiɣt\add* i ittwaggen s ifassen \add n iwdan\add* am mammec iqqar unabi: \x ◘ \xo 7:48 \xt 1 Ij. 8:27; Řex. 17:24. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 49 \qt ‘Ajenna d řɛarc inu\qt*
\m \qt u temmurt d tanebdat sadu iḍaren inu.\qt*
\m \qt Mani taddart i d ayi ɣa tebnam,\qt*
\m \qt iqqar SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt niɣ mani amcan n arraḥet inu?\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:49 \xt 2 Im. 6:33; Ica. 66:1, 2; Mt. 5:34; 23:22. \x*
\m 
\v 50 \qt Ma war iggi ufus inu man aya marra?’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:50 \xt Ica. 66:1-2; Amz. 1:4. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 51 \add A kenniw\add* inni ittɣennan d yinni war ittwaxetnen n wuř d utesři, řebda tᵉttemɛařam x Arruḥ Iqeddsen. Am mammec ggin řejdud nwem, ammu i tᵉtteggem uřa d kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 7:51 \xt Naḥ. 9:16, 17; Irm. 6:1. \x*
\v 52 Man wen zeg inabiyyen war ten marrten u war ten nɣin řejdud nwem, aqa inni izwaren barrḥen x twasit n Umseggad, wenni tsellmem, tenɣim t kenniw, \x ◘ \xo 7:52 \xt Řex. 22:14; Rum. 3:26; 1 Bṭ. 3:18; 1 Yḥ. 2:1\x*
\v 53 kenniw inni iksin Ccariɛa s řumur n lmalakat maca war dayes tᵉṭṭifem.” \x ◘ \xo 7:53 \xt Uf. 19:3; 24:3; Yḥ. 7:19; Gal. 3:19; Ɛbr. 2:2. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 54 Umi sřin aya, dduqqzen nitni s uxeyyeq, ɣeẓẓen tiɣmas nsen ɣares.
\v 55 Maca am tuɣa iccur s l’iman d Arruḥ Iqeddsen, ikessi netta tiṭṭawin nnes deg ujenna, iẓra aɛuǧi n AREBBI, d Yasuɛ ibedd ɣar yefus n AREBBI,
\v 56 inna: “Xzar, ttwařiɣ ijenwan arzmen u Mmis n bnadem ibedd ɣar yefus n AREBBI.”
\v 57 Maca nitni, am sɣuyyun s ict n tmijja d tameqqrant, qqnen imejjan nsen uca hejmen xas marra.
\v 58 Tṭfen t, ssuffɣen t barra i tendint, bdan ttḥejjaren t u řechud ssarsen arruḍ nsen ɣar iḍaren n ijj n ubřiɣ qqaren as Cawul. \x ◘ \xo 7:58 \xt 1 Ij. 21:13; Lk. 4:29. \x*
\v 59 Tuɣa ttḥejjaren Stifanus am ittřaɣa, iqqar: “A Siditneɣ Yasuɛ, ṭṭef arruḥ inu.” \x ◘ \xo 7:59 \xt Izhd. 31:6; Lk. 23:46. \x*
\v 60 Xenni iwḍa \add x ifadden nnes\add*, isɣuy s ict n tmijja tejhed, inna: “A Siditneɣ, war d asen ttḥasab ddnub-a!” Awarni řami inna aya, iṭṭeṣ \add s yiḍes n řmewt\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:60 \xt Mt. 5:44; Lk. 23:34; 1 Kur. 4:12. \x*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Adarrec x Tmesmunt n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 1 Cawul yarḍa x řmewt nnes uca icarc deg uneqqi nnes. Deg wussan nni imsar ijj n umarret imɣar x tmesmunt di Urcalim u marra ttwazuzzaren ɣar dcurat n Yahudiyya d Samarya, mɣir rrusul lla. \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt Řex. 11:19; 22:20. \x*
\v 2 Ca n yeryazen yumnen ksin t, arbun Stifanus ɣar wenḍeř uca ggin xas ijj n wecḍan ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Amz. 23:2; 50:10; 2 Ṣm. 3:31\x*
\v 3 Maca Cawul tuɣa ittdarrec tamesmunt xmi ittadef ɣar tudrin, ittjarra iryazen d temɣarin, ineddeh i-ten ɣar řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Řex. 9:1; 22:4; 26:9; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\b
\s1 Abarreḥ n L’Injil s Filippus di tendint n Samariya
\m 
\v 4 Inni ittwazuzzaren tuɣa gguren, ttennḍen, ttbarrḥen s Wawař n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt Mt. 10:23; Řex. 11:19. \x*
\v 5 Amu ihwa-dd Filippus \add ɛawed\add* ɣar ict n tendint n Isamariyyen, ibarreḥ i-ten s Lmasiḥ.
\v 6 Umi sřin i wawař nnes, ttwassqenɛen iwdan i tuɣa ittesřan s marra min ittwannan zi Filippus, maɣar ẓrin řeɛřamat i igga.
\v 7 Minzi aṭṭas n yinni ittwaṭṭfen zi řaryaḥ imengas, sɣuyyun s tmijja ijehden uca ffɣen zzaysen. Inneɣni i tuɣa d ineɛḍaben d iqejdaḥen ttwassgenfan. \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt Mk. 16:17; Řex. 5:16; 16:18; 19:11. \x*
\v 8 Tuɣa din ict n řefraḥet temɣar di tendint nni.
\m 
\v 9 Tuɣa din ijj n weryaz, qqaren as Cimun, tuɣa izeddeɣ di tendint nni aṭṭas zeg wami. Netta tuɣa issɣekkwa řgens n Isamariyyen s tseḥḥart nnes, ittbarren x yixef nnes, inna: “Necc, \add aqa\add* necc d wenni imɣaren!” \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt Řex. 13:6. \x*
\v 10 Marra sřin ɣares, am umeẓyan, am umeqqran, nnan: “Wanita d jjehd imɣaren n AREBBI.”
\v 11 Isseqneɛ i-ten marra s minzi tuɣa issarjef i-ten s ssḥur nnes aṭṭas zeg wami.
\v 12 Maca umi yumnen di Filippus wenni tuɣa ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Tgeldit n AREBBI u s Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ttwassɣeḍṣen nitni, am yeryazen am temɣarin.
\v 13 Cimun s yixef nnes ɛawed yumen, ittwasseɣḍeṣ uca iqqim iḍeffar Filippus. Řami iẓra lmuɛjizat d řeɛřamat imɣaren i imsaren s ufus nnes, itebhet, yarjef.
\m 
\v 14 Umi sřin rrusul inni iǧan di Urcalim belli řgens n Samarya iqbeř Awař n AREBBI, ssekken ɣarsen Cimɛun Buṭrus d Yuḥanna.
\v 15 Nitni hwan-dd ɣarsen, ẓẓuǧen asen ḥima ad ṭṭfen Arruḥ Iqeddsen,
\v 16 minzi Wanita tuɣa ɛad war dd-yusi x uřa d ijj zzaysen, tuɣa ttwassɣeḍṣen waha s Yisem n Sidi Yasuɛ.
\v 17 Xenni ssarsen xasen ifassen uca nitni ṭṭfen Arruḥ Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Řex. 6:6; 13:3; 19:6; 1 Tim. 4:14; 5:22; 2 Tim. 1:6. \x*
\m 
\v 18 Umi iẓra Cimun belli s usarsi n ifassen n rrusul immewc asen Arruḥ Iqeddsen, xenni ixs ad asen iwc \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart,
\v 19 inna: “Ewc ayi ɛawed ṣṣulṭa-ya, ḥima man wen i x ɣa ssarseɣ afus inu, ad iqbeř Arruḥ Iqeddsen.”
\v 20 \add Maca\add* inna as Cimɛun Buṭrus: “Ad tᵉtteḥḥa nnuqart nnec akidek, minzi ittɣiř ac ad tkesbed tawhibt n AREBBI s wagřa n ddunect! \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Mt. 10:8. \x*
\v 21 War ɣarek bu tesɣart uřa d ca di l’iman wanita, minzi uř nnec war iǧi isegged zzat i AREBBI.
\v 22 Tub zi tuɛeffna nnec uca ttar zi AREBBI maḥend ad xak tᵉttwaɣfar teḥraymect-a n wuř nnec,
\v 23 minzi ttwařiɣ aqa cek tewḍid-dd deg ijj n uḥrir d amerzag u deg ijj n uceddi n tuɛeffna.”
\v 24 Yarra-dd Cimun, inna: “Ttarem i AREBBI xafi ḥima war dd-ittis xafi ca zi min tennam.”
\m 
\v 25 Awarni řami cehden Cimɛun d Yuḥanna u ssřemden Awař n AREBBI, ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim, barrḥen s Řexbar Aṣebḥan deg waṭṭas n ředcur n Isamariyyen.
\b
\s1 Aseɣḍaṣ n řewzir zi temmurt n Kuc
\m 
\v 26 Uca lmalak n SIDI issiweř ak-d Filippus, inna: “Kkar, truḥed ɣar ljanub deg webrid n řexřa i dd-ihwan zi Urcalim ɣar Ɣazza.”
\v 27 Ikkar iruḥ, uca immeřqa ak-d ijj n řewzir zi \add temmurt n\add* Kuc, ijj n řewzir n Kandaki, tajeǧidt n ayt n Kuc. Tuɣa-t ɣares ṣṣulṭa x marra řeknuz nnes, yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim ḥima ad \add din\add* iɛbed. \f ◼ \fr 8:27 \fk tammurt n Kuc\ft - deg wussan nni tuɣa tammurt n Kuc tesswiẓẓeḍ ixef nnes zi temmurt n Itiyupiya d Ssudan ař tammurt n Miṣra.\f*
\v 28 Umi dd-iɛqeb, iqqim x ijj n ukarru, iqqar \add deg wedlis\add* n unabi Icaɛya.
\m 
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* inna Arruḥ i Filippus: “Zid, tmuned ak-d ukarru-ya.”
\v 30 Iqarreb-dd \add ɣares\add* Filippus, isřa as min iqqar \add zeg wedlis\add* n unabi Icaɛya, inna as: “Ma tfehmed min teqqared?”
\v 31 Inna as: “Mammec zemmareɣ ad fehmeɣ mařa war din ḥed i d ayi ɣa issefhemen?” Uca ittar zi Filippus maḥend ad yenya uca ad kis iqqim.
\v 32 Udem i tuɣa iqqar zeg Wedlis d wa:
\b
\m \qt “Amecnaw izmar ittwandeh\qt*
\m \qt ɣar řgurnet i tɣarṣt,\qt*
\m \qt amecnaw texsi tegnu\qt*
\m \qt qibač i wenni tt iǧasen,\qt*
\m \qt war yarzim Netta aqemmum nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 8:32 \xt Ica. 53:7-8\x*
\m 
\v 33 \qt Deg useḥqar nnes ittwakkes\qt*
\m \qt zi tmeḥbast u zi řḥukm.\qt*
\m \qt Wi ɣa iɛawden x dduriyet nnes?\qt*
\m \qt Minzi tudart nnes tᵉttwassgeɛɛed\qt*
\m \qt zi temmurt.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 34 Yarra-dd řewzir x Filippus, inna: “Ad cek sseqsiɣ, x wi xef issawař unabi man aya, ma x yixef nnes niɣ x ijjen nneɣni?”
\v 35 Yarzem Filippus aqemmum nnes, uca ibda ittbarreḥ as s Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ s wawař-a zi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 8:35 \xt Lk. 24:45. \x*
\m 
\v 36 Am tuɣa gguren nitni deg webrid, iwḍen ɣar ijj n wemcan mani tuɣa ǧan waman. Inna řewzir: “Xzar, aqa din aman. Min dayi iṭṭfen war ttwasseɣḍaṣeɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 8:36 \xt Řex. 10:47. \x*
\v 37 Inna Filippus: “Mařa tumned s wuř nnec marra, tḥeǧeř!” Uca netta yarra-dd, inna: “Umneɣ aqa Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ d Mmis n AREBBI.”
\v 38 Yumur ad ibedd ukarru, hwan tnayen idsen deg waman uca Filippus isseɣḍeṣ řewziř.
\v 39 Ařami dd-geɛɛden zeg waman, ixḍef Arruḥ n SIDI Filippus. Uca řewzir war t iẓri ɛad, maca iruḥ deg webrid nnes s řefraḥet.
\v 40 Maca Filippus ittwaf di Acdud u ssenni ittcuqa \add di temmurt\add*, ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan di marra tineddam ařami dd-yiweḍ ɣar Qayṣariya.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Cawul deg webrid ɣar Dimacq
\m 
\v 1 Maca Cawul tuɣa \add ɛad\add* ittsuḍ s uɛeddi d řmewt ḍidd n imeḥḍaren n Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Řex. 8:3; 22:4; 26:9; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 2 Ittar zeg arrays n ikehhanen tibratin i temzidawin n Dimacq, maḥend, mařa yufa ca n yinni iḍeffaren ‘Abrid-a’, iryazen niɣ timɣarin, izemmar ad ten icedd u ad ten dd-indeh ɣar Urcalim.
\m 
\v 3 Řami \add din\add* iruḥ, imsar, am tuɣa ittqarrab ɣar Dimacq, tařɣa-dd xas deɣya ict n tfawt zeg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Řex. 22:6; 26:31; 1 Kur. 15:8; 2 Kur. 12:2. \x*
\v 4 Iwḍa ɣar temmurt, xenni isřa i yict n tmijja teqqar as: “Cawul, Cawul mayemmi xafi tdarraced? Tzeyyared x yixef nnec umi teccated di sřek n buykucḍan.”
\v 5 Yarra-dd, inna: “Min teɛnid Cek, a Sidi?” Inna as Siditneɣ: “Aqa d NECC, Yasuɛ wenni x tdarrced. \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Řex. 5:39. \x*
\v 6 Kkar, tudfed ɣar tendint, ad ac ittwanna dinni min ittxeṣṣa ad tegged!” \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Lk. 3:10; Řex. 2:37; 16:30. \x*
\v 7 Uca iryazen inni kis isafaren, bedden ttbehten, minzi nitni sřin tmijja, maca war ẓrin ḥed. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Dan. 10:7. \x*
\m 
\v 8 Ikkar-dd Cawul zi temmurt, waxxa arzment tiṭṭawin nnes war izemmar ad ittwařa, u nitni gewwden t zeg ufus, nedhen t ɣar Dimacq.
\v 9 Třata n wussan tuɣa war ittwiři, war icci, war iswi.
\m 
\v 10 Tuɣa \add din\add* di Dimacq ijj n umeḥḍar qqaren as Ananiyas. SIDI inna as deg ijj n řewḥiy: “\add A\add* Ananiyas!” Inna as: “Aqa ayi da, \add a\add* Sidi inu!”
\v 11 Inna as Siditneɣ: “Kkar, truḥed ɣar webrid umi qqaren ‘Abrid isseggden’, xenni ɣar taddart n Yahuda, seqsa x ijj n weryaz zi Tarsus, qqaren as Cawul, xzar, aqa ittẓaǧa \add din\add*, \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Řex. 21:39; 22:3. \x*
\v 12 uca yusa-dd ɣares deg ijj n řewḥiy, aqa ijj n weryaz qqaren as Ananiyas yudef-dd, issars xas afus nnes ḥima ad ttwarzment tiṭṭawin nnes.”
\v 13 Yarra-dd Ananiyas: “A Sidi, aqa sřiɣ aṭṭas \add n tmesřayin\add* x weryaz-a, mecḥař d řɣar i igga deg imqeddasen nnec di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Řex. 9:1; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 14 Aqa da, ɛawed danita ɣares ttesriḥ zeg \add uɣezdis\add* n imeqqranen n ikehhanen, maḥend ad iḥebbes marra inni ittřaɣan x Yisem nnec.”
\v 15 \add Maca\add* SIDI inna as: “Ruḥ minzi wa aqa-t ɣari d řqecɛet ifarzen ḥima ad yarbu Isem inu ɣar řegnus u ɣar ijeǧiden u jar ayt n Israil, \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Řex. 13:2; 22:21; Rum. 1:1; Gal. 1:15; 2:8; Afa. 3:8; 1 Tim. 2:7; 2 Tim. 1:1. \x*
\v 16 minzi ad as ssecneɣ mecḥař ittxeṣṣa as ad iweddeb di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu.” \x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt Řex. 21:11; 2 Kur. 11:23. \x*
\m 
\v 17 Iruḥ Ananiyas, yudef ɣar taddart, issars xas afus nnes, inna: “\add A\add* uma Cawul, aqa Siditneɣ Yasuɛ, wenni d ac dd-iḍharen deg webrid i zi dd-tusid, issekk ayi-dd, ḥima ad tᵉttwařid ɛawed u ad tᵉttwaccured s Arruḥ Iqeddsen.” \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Řex. 22:12. \x*
\v 18 Řexdenni tewḍa-dd ca am teqcurt zi tiṭṭawin nnes, ttwarzment tiṭṭawin nnes. Ikkar uca ittwasseɣḍeṣ.
\b
\s1 Cawul ibda ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan di Dimacq
\m 
\v 19 Umi icca, imḥeḍ uca iqqim ca n wussan ak-d imeḥḍaren di Dimacq.
\v 20 Řexdenni ibda ittbarreḥ di temzida n Wudayen x Yasuɛ, belli Netta d Mmis n AREBBI.
\v 21 Marra inni tuɣa ittesřan, ttbehten, qqaren: “Ma war iǧi d wanita i tuɣa imarrten marra inni tuɣa ittřaɣan s Yisem-a di Urcalim, u \add ma war iǧi d wanita\add* i dd-ittwassekken ɛad danita zi ssibbet d ict, maḥend ad ten icarf u ad ten igewwed ɣar imeqqranen n ikehhanen?”
\v 22 Cawul tuɣa yarenni di jjehd, issedhec Udayen inni izeddɣen di Dimacq am d asen isscen belli \add Yeccu\add* wanita d Lmasiḥ.
\m 
\v 23 Umi ɛdun wussan, ggin Wudayen ijj n wenway s teḥraymect ḥima ad t nɣen.
\v 24 Maca taḥiřet nsen i zi tuɣa arezzun ad t nɣen, tᵉttwassargeb i Cawul. \add Maca\add* nitni tuɣa ḥeṭṭan tiwwura \add n tendint\add* s uziř d ǧiřet, maḥend ad awḍen ad t nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt 2 Kur. 11:32. \x*
\v 25 Maca imeḥḍaren nnes ggin t deg ict n tsuǧet uca ssehwan t zi řḥiḍ s ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt Yac. 2:15; 1 Ṣm. 19:12. \x*
\b
\s1 Cawul di Urcalim
\m 
\v 26 Yuyur netta ɣar Urcalim, yarzu ad imun ak-d imeḥḍaren, maca nitni marra ggʷeden zzayes, war ttiqqen ca belli netta \add idweř\add* d ameḥḍar. \x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt Řex. 22:17. \x*
\v 27 Maca Bar-Naba iksi t ɣares uca indeh i-t ɣar rrusul uca \add Cawul\add* ixebbar i-ten mammec iẓra SIDI deg webrid u mammec kis issiweř u mammec tuɣa ittbarreḥ s teryast s Yisem n Yasuɛ di Dimacq. \x ◘ \xo 9:27 \xt Řex. 11:25. \x*
\v 28 Tuɣa iqqim akidsen ittadef itteffeɣ zi Urcalim,
\v 29 uca ittbarreḥ s teryast s Yisem n Yasuɛ, ittqacaḥ ak-d Wudayen inni issnen \add iřes n\add* Tyunanit, maca nitni arzun ad t nɣen.
\v 30 Umi ssnen tawmat man aya, nedhen t ɣar Qayṣariya di ǧiřet uca sekken t ssenni ɣar Tarsus.
\m 
\v 31 Tamesmunt di marra Yahudiyya d Ljalil d Samarya tuɣa dayes řehna, tᵉttwabna \add di l’iman\add*, teggur di tiggʷudi n AREBBI uca truḥ di tyumi s ufewwej n Arruḥ Iqeddsen.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n Aniyas
\m 
\v 32 Řami tuɣa Cimɛun iggur di tneddam, ihwa-dd ɣar imqeddasen inni izeddɣen di tendint n Lidda.
\v 33 Yufa din ijj n bnadem, qqaren as Aniyas, izzeř s tassut u teɛdu xas tmenya n iseggʷusa d aneɛḍab.
\v 34 Inna as Cimɛun: “\add A\add* Aniyas, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad cek issgenfa. Kkar, tessud i ixef nnec!” Řexdenni ikkar deɣya.
\v 35 Uca ẓrin t marra imezdaɣ n Lidda d Sarun, uca dewřen-dd ɣar AREBBI.
\b
\s1 Asnekkar n Tabita
\m 
\v 36 Tuɣa di tendint n Yaffa ict n tmeḥḍart, qqaren as Tabita, \add maca s yiřes n Tyunanit qqaren as ‘Durka’, ixs ad yini ‘Ɣazala’\add*. Ta tuɣa teccur s řexdayem tiṣebḥanin i tuɣa tᵉttegg u s ṣṣdaqi \add i tuɣa tessuffuɣ\add*.
\v 37 Deg wussan nni tehřec uca temmut. Sirden tt uca ssarsen tt di tɣurfet.
\v 38 Maca imeḥḍaren sřin belli Cimɛun aqa-t di tendint n Lidda, tenni zzat n Yaffa. \add Xenni\add* ssekken nitni tnayen n yeryazen ḥima ad zzayes ḥeccmen, ḥima war ittɛeṭṭař maḥend ad kidsen yuyur!
\v 39 Ikkar Cimɛun, yuyur akidsen. Řami dd-yiweḍ, nedhen t ɣar tɣurfet sennej. Beddent-i-dd ɣares marra tijjař, runt, sscanent as tcamirat d ijeǧaben i d asent tewca Tabita ařami tuɣa-tt ɛad teddar. \f ◼ \fr 9:39 \fk Durka\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ɣazala’.\f*
\m 
\v 40 Maca Cimɛun issuffeɣ i-tent marra ɣar barra, isjed, iẓẓuǧ uca inneqřeb-dd ɣar řxecbet inna: “Tabita, kkar!” Nettat tarzem tiṭṭawin nnes uca řami teẓra Cimɛun, teqqim.
\v 41 Isswiẓẓeḍ ɣares afus nnes, issnekkar i-tt-i-d, xenni iřaɣa-dd x imqeddasen d tijjař, isscen asen tt, belli aqa teddar.
\m 
\v 42 Iffeɣ-dd řexbar-a ɣar tendint marra uca aṭṭas umnen di Siditneɣ.
\v 43 Uca iqqim di Yaffa, war iǧi drus n wussan, ɣar ijj n weryaz nni tuɣa iɛeddeř iřmawen, qqaren as Cimɛun.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Buṭrus d řqebṭan arumani Kurniliyus
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa di Qayṣariya ijj n weryaz, isem nnes Kurniliyus, aqa-t d řqebṭan \add x mya\add*, inni zi řkumpaniyyet umi qqaren ‘Aṭalyan’.
\v 2 Netta tuɣa ittweqqar u itteggʷed AREBBI ak-d aytbab n taddart nnes marra, ittic aṭṭas n ṣṣdaqi i iwdan uca ikessi s řmeɛruf i AREBBI řebda.
\v 3 Wa iẓra deg ijj n řewḥiy iṣfa aqa ijj n lmalak n AREBBI yudef-dd ɣares ɣar tsaɛɛet wiss tesɛa n wass, \add ixs ad yini ɣar tsaɛɛet wiss třata n uziř\add*, inna as: “\add A\add* Kurniliyus!”
\v 4 Umi dayes inḍar tiṭṭawin nnes, iggʷed aṭṭas, inna: “Min din, a Sidi?” Inna as lmalak: “Tiẓaǧitin nnec d ṣṣdaqi nnec iwḍent ɣar řidaret zzat i \add wudem n\add* AREBBI.
\v 5 Ssekk řexxu iryazen ɣar Yaffa, tɛarḍed x Cimɛun, wenni umi qqaren ɛawed Buṭrus.
\v 6 Xzar, netta yarzef ɣar Cimɛun, wenni iɛeddřen iřmawen, wenni ɣar iǧa taddart ɣar tma n řebḥar.”
\v 7 Umi iruḥ lmalak wenni tuɣa akides issawařen, iřaɣa netta x tnayen n imsexxaren zi taddart nnes u x ijj n uɛeskari itteggʷeden AREBBI, wenni tuɣa iṭaɛ as.
\v 8 Ihaja asen marra min iẓra uca issekk i-ten ɣar Yaffa.
\m 
\v 9 Tiwecca nnes, am tuɣa aten deg webrid ttqarraben ɣar tendint, igeɛɛed Cimɛun x tzeqqa ɣar tsaɛɛet wiss setta, \add aqa-tt d ḍḍhur\add*, ḥima ad iẓẓaǧ. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt 2 Ij. 4:33; Mt. 6:6. \x*
\v 10 Iǧuẓ aṭṭas uca tuɣa immeẓri ad icc, uca, am tuɣa d as ssewjaden, iwyi t řewḥiy.
\v 11 Iẓra ajenna yarzem uca ict n řqecɛet am yict n tcuqqet tameqqrant zi řeqṭen \add azdad\add* ittwaṭṭfen zi arebɛa n tɣemmura nnes, tehwa-dd zeg ujenna ɣar temmurt.
\v 12 Tuɣa dayes marra imuddaren n temmurt s arebɛa n iḍaren uřa d imuddaren nni ittbuɛen x temmurt d ijḍaḍ n ujenna. \f ◼ \fr 10:12 \fk imuddaren\ft - ixs ad yini ‘iwdan’ d ‘lḥayawanat’ d marra min iddaren nni izemmar ad yuyur.\f*
\v 13 Tusa-dd ɣares ict n tmijja, teqqar as-dd: “\add A\add* Cimɛun, kkar, ɣarṣ, tecced!”
\v 14 Maca Cimɛun inna: “Lla, \add a\add* Sidi, war cciɣ ɛemmarṣ min iǧan d řeḥram uřa min war izdigen.” \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt Lawi 11:4; Aɛwd. 14:7. \x*
\v 15 Tmijja \add tessiweř\add* ɣares ɛawed i twařa wiss tnayen, \add teqqar\add*: “Min issizdeg AREBBI, war dd t tᵉttarrid ca cek d řeḥram.” \x ◘ \xo 10:15 \xt Mt. 15:11; Rum. 14:17, 20; 1 Tim. 4:4; Tit. 1:15. \x*
\v 16 Man aya imsar třata n imuřen, uca deɣya tᵉttwassgeɛɛed tajartiřt \add ɛawed\add* ɣar ujenna.
\m 
\v 17 Am tuɣa Cimɛun \add ɛad\add* ittxarraṣ deg ixef nnes min ixs ad yini řewḥiy i iẓra, xzar, usin-dd tnayen n yeryazen inni dd-ittwassekken zi Kurniliyus, sseqsan x taddart mani tuɣa iqqim Cimɛun. Nitni bedden-dd ɣar tewwart n řemraḥ.
\v 18 Řaɣan, sseqsan: “Ma Cimɛun, umi ttkennan Buṭrus, aqa-t danita?”
\m 
\v 19 Umi tuɣa Cimɛun \add ɛad\add* ittxarraṣ di řewḥiy i iẓra, inna as Arruḥ: “Xzar, aqa da třata n yeryazen arezzun xak!
\v 20 Kkar, tehwid-dd, ruḥ akidsen břa ma ad tcekked di ca, minzi d Necc i-ten-dd-issekken.”
\v 21 \add Řexdenni\add* ihwa Cimɛun ɣar yeryazen nni, inna asen: “Xzar, aqa d necc wenni xef tarezzum. Min ɣar dd-tusim da?”
\v 22 Nnan as: “Kurniliyus, ijj n řqebṭan x mya d ijj n weryaz isegged itteggʷed AREBBI, wenni xef icehhed mliḥ marra řgens n Wudayen, aqa ijj n lmalak iqeddsen tuɣa iɛřem as deg ijj n řewḥiy, maḥend ad dd-issekk ɣarek, ḥima ad cek dd-aywyen ɣar taddart nnes, \add maḥend\add* ad zzayek iseř ict n tebrat.”
\v 23 Cimɛun issidef i-ten ɣar daxeř, igga ten d inewjiwen mani iqqim. Tiwecca nnes ikkar, iruḥ akidsen u ca n wawmaten inni iǧan zi Yaffa ruḥen akides.
\m 
\v 24 Tiwecca nnes awarni as iwḍen ɣar Qayṣariya. Kurniliyus tuɣa ittraja ten am ssmunan ɣares marra aytbab n řaǧ nnes uřa d imeddukkař i-t-i-dd-yudsen aṭṭas.
\v 25 Umi yudef Cimɛun, iřqa t-i-dd Kurniliyus, iwḍa as ɣar iḍaren uca isjed as.
\v 26 \add Maca\add* issnekkar i-t-i-dd Cimɛun, inna as: “Kkar, aqa uřa d necc d bnadem \add am cek\add*!” \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt Řex. 14:14; Asa. 19:10; 22:9. \x*
\v 27 Am kides issawař, yudef uca yufa din aṭṭas inni dd-yusin \add ttmunan\add* dinni.
\v 28 Inna asen: “Kenniw tessnem aqa war iḥeǧer x weryaz d Uday ad imun ak-d ijj n ubarrani i war dd-iqqarṣen zi teqbič n řgens nnes. Maca AREBBI isscen ayi belli war icuwwar ad řaɣiɣ uřa x ijj n bnadem ixmej niɣ d řeḥram. \x ◘ \xo 10:28 \xt Uf. 23:32; 34:15; Aɛwd. 7:2; Yḥ. 4:9; 18:28; Řex. 11:3; 15:8; Afa. 3:6. \x*
\v 29 S uyenni usiɣ-dd ɛawed \add da\add* břa ma ad cekkeɣ di ca umi xafi tɛarḍed. Maca xseɣ ad kenniw sseqsiɣ, mayemmi d ayi tejjim ad dd-aseɣ?”
\v 30 Inna as Kurniliyus: “Arebɛa n wussan zeg wami tuɣa ttẓummeɣ, uca xzar, ɣar tsaɛɛet wiss tesɛa umi tuɣa ttẓaǧiɣ di taddart inu, aqa din ijj n weryaz ibedd-dd qibač inu s warruḍ d acemřař!
\v 31 Inna ayi: ‘\add A\add* Kurniliyus, taẓaǧit nnec tᵉttwaseř u ṣṣdaqi nnec iwḍent ɣar řidaret n AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 10:31 \xt Mt. 28:3; Mk. 16:5; Lk. 24:4. \x*
\v 32 Sekk \add ijjen\add* ɣar Yaffa, tɛarḍed x Cimɛun wenni umi ttkennan Buṭrus. Xzar, aqa netta d anewjiw di taddart n Cimɛun, wenni iɛeddřen iřmawen, tenni ɣar tma n řebḥar. Netta ad dd-yas uca ad kidek issiweř.
\v 33 S uyenni ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarek řexdenni u cek aqa teggid mliḥ umi dd-tusid da. Neccin marra i da neǧa qibač i cek, nᵉttexs ad nseř marra min zi cek yumur AREBBI.”
\b
\s1 Abarraḥ n L’injil i řegnus d usfarreɣ n Arruḥ Iqeddsen
\m 
\v 34 Yarzem Cimɛun aqemmum nnes, inna: “S tidett, ufiɣ belli AREBBI war ittegg ca s wudmawen. \x ◘ \xo 10:34 \xt Aɛwd. 10:17; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 34:19; Rum. 2:11; Gal. 2:6; Afa. 6:9; Kul. 3:25; 1 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*
\v 35 Maca wenni t itteggʷeden d wenni itteggen tasegda zi kuř řgens, yusa-dd as x řxaḍar nnes.
\v 36 Maɣar wa d Awař i issekk ɣar ayt n Israil d wenni zi i d asen ibarreḥ: řehna d řhudnet s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni d SIDI n marra. \x ◘ \xo 10:36 \xt Ica. 9:5; 52:7; Yḥ. 16:33; Rum. 5:1; Kul. 1:20. \x*
\v 37 Kenniw tessnem aqa Awař yiweḍ-dd ɣar marra Yahudiyya, \add awarni řami\add* ibda zi Ljalil awarni i useɣḍaṣ i zi tuɣa ittbarreḥ Yuḥanna, \x ◘ \xo 10:37 \xt Ica. 8:23; 9:1; Mt. 4:12; Mk. 1:14,38, 39; Lk. 4:14. \x*
\v 38 \add řexbar\add* zi jjihet n Yasuɛ zi Nnaṣira, mammec t idhen AREBBI s Arruḥ Iqeddsen u s jjehd. Netta issara \add tammurt\add*, igga řxar, issgenfa inni ittwaɣezzan zeg umɛeffan minzi AREBBI tuɣa-t akides. \x ◘ \xo 10:38 \xt Izhd. 45:8; Ica. 61:1; Lk. 4:18. \x*
\v 39 Neccin d řechud xas u x marra min igga di temmurt n Yahudiyya u di Urcalim. Aqa uyřen t Wudayen x teḥnact, nɣin t.
\v 40 Wa issnekkar i-t-i-dd AREBBI deg wass wiss třata uca isseḍhar i-t s bṭayṭay, \x ◘ \xo 10:40 \xt Mk. 16:14; Lk. 24:34; Yḥ. 20:19; Řex. 2:24; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\v 41 maca war iǧi i marra řgens, maca i řechud inni izwar ixḍar i-ten AREBBI, i neccin inni akides iccin iswin awarni tanukra nnes zi taddart n imettinen.
\v 42 Yumur aneɣ ad nbarreḥ u ad neched i řgens, aqa d Netta d Wenni igga AREBBI d Řqaḍi x yinni iddaren u x yinni immuten. \x ◘ \xo 10:42 \xt Mt. 28:19; Mk. 16:15; Yḥ. 15:16; Řex. 17:31. \x*
\v 43 Cehhden xas marra inabiyyen, belli kuř ijjen wenni i ɣa yamnen deg Yisem nnes, ad as ttwaɣfaren ddnub nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 10:43 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:24; Dan. 9:24; Mixa 7:20; Řex. 15:9. \x*
\m 
\v 44 Am tuɣa Cimɛun issawař \add ɛad\add*, ihwa-dd Arruḥ Iqeddsen x marra inni tuɣa ittesřan i wawař. \x ◘ \xo 10:44 \xt Řex. 8:17. \x*
\v 45 Tawmat nni ittwaxetnen, inni dd-yusin akides, tbehten, umi tamewci n Arruḥ Iqeddsen ittwafarreɣ ɛawed x \add yenni iǧan zi\add* řegnus.
\v 46 Minzi tuɣa ten ttesřan ssawařen \bd s ijj n yiřes nneɣni\bd*, ssmeɣɣaran di AREBBI. Řexdenni iqqar Cimɛun: \x ◘ \xo 10:46 \xt Mk. 16:17; Řex. 2:4. \x*
\v 47 “Ma izemmar ḥed ad iqḍeɛ aman maḥend war ttwasseɣḍiṣen ina? Maɣar, xzar, aqa qebřen Arruḥ Iqeddsen am neccin!” \x ◘ \xo 10:47 \xt Řex. 8:36; 11:17. \x*
\v 48 Xenni yumur ad ten ssɣeḍṣen s Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, uca nitni ttaren zzayes ad iqqim akidsen \add ɛad\add* ca n wussan.
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Buṭrus isseɛdu řexbar x weɣḍaṣ n Kurniliyus
\m 
\v 1 Rrusul d tawmat inni iǧan di Yahudiyya sřin belli uřa d řegnus qebřen Wawař n AREBBI.
\v 2 Řami igeɛɛed Cimɛun ɣar Urcalim, mcubbcen akides inni iǧan zeg wextan.
\v 3 Nnan, belli netta yudef-dd ɣar iwdan i war ittwaxetnen, icca akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 11:3 \xt Uf. 23:32; 34:15; Aɛwd. 7:2; Yḥ. 18:28. \x*
\m 
\v 4 Maca Cimɛun iqḍeɛ \add daysen řhard\add*, uca ibda ad asen iɛawed awař iḍfar umas:
\v 5 “Řami tuɣa ayi di \add tendint n\add* Yaffa ttẓaǧiɣ, ẓriɣ deg ijj n řewḥiy aqa ict n řqecɛet am tcuqqet tameqqrant n řeqṭen \add azdad\add* ittwaṭṭfen zi arebɛa n tɣemmura nnes tehwa-dd zeg ujenna, tiweḍ-dd ɣari. \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Řex. 10:9. \x*
\v 6 Xzareɣ mliḥ u ẓriɣ aqa dayes \add imuddaren\add* n temmurt s arebɛa n iḍaren d \add imuddaren\add* inni ittbuɛen x temmurt uřa d ijḍaḍ n ujenna.
\v 7 Sřiɣ awarni ayi ict n tmijja, tenna ayi: ‘\add A\add* Cimɛun, kkar, ɣarṣ, tecced!’
\v 8 Maca necc nniɣ: ‘Lla, \add a\add* Sidi, ɛemmarṣ war yudif ɛad ɣar uqemmum inu min war izdigen niɣ min iǧan d řeḥram.’ \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Lawi 11:4; Aɛwd. 14:7. \x*
\v 9 Tenna xafi tmijja zeg ujenna ɛawed: ‘Min issizdeg AREBBI, war dd t tᵉttarrid ca cek d řeḥram!’
\v 10 Man aya imsar třata n imuren uca \add xenni\add* ittwassjbed marra ɛawed ɣar ujenna.
\v 11 U xzar, řexdenni aqa din třata n yeryazen inni ɣari dd-ittwassekken zi Kurniliyus zi Qayṣariya, bedden ɣar tewwart n řemraḥ mani d ayi tuɣa.
\v 12 Inna ayi Arruḥ aqa ittxeṣṣa ad kisen raḥeɣ břa ma ad cekkeɣ. Tuɣa akidi uřa d setta n wawmaten u nudef ɣar taddart n weryaz \add nni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt Řex. 10:19; 15:7. \x*
\v 13 Netta issargeb aneɣ mammec iẓra ijj n lmalak i ibedden di taddart nnes, wenni d as innan: ‘Sekk \add ijj n weryaz\add* ɣar Yaffa, tɛarḍed x Cimɛun wenni umi ttkennan Buṭrus.
\v 14 Netta ad ac issiweř awařen i zi ɣa tᵉṭṭfed Tudart, cek d marra taddart nnec.’
\v 15 Umi qqimeɣ ssiwřeɣ, ihwa-dd Arruḥ Iqeddsen xasen am mammec xaneɣ dd-ihwa ɛawed ɣar umezwaru.
\v 16 Ttwassɛeqřeɣ x wawař n Siditneɣ, mammec inna: ‘Yuḥanna tuɣa isseɣḍaṣ s waman maca kenniw ad ttwassɣeḍṣem s Arruḥ Iqeddsen.’ \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt Ica. 44:3; Yuw. 3:1; Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:8; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:26; Řex. 1:5; 2:4; 19:4. \x*
\v 17 Mařa AREBBI iwca tamewci-ya i řegnus nni yumnen di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ am mammec d aneɣ tt iwca, xenni min ɛniɣ necc maḥend ad ssbeddeɣ AREBBI?” \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Řex. 15:9. \x*
\m 
\v 18 Umi sřin awařen-a, heddnen, ssemɣaren AREBBI, nnan: “Ad taɣ iwca AREBBI uřa i řegnus maḥend ad dd-dewřen ad tuben i Tudart.”
\b
\s1 Tamesmunt n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ di Antiyuxiya
\m 
\v 19 Inni ittwazuzzaren zi ssibbet n řmeḥnet i imsaren s ssibbet n Stifanus, ẓwan ɣar Finiqiya u ɣar jjwayeh n Qubrus u ɣar Antiyuxiya, am war ssiwiřen ak-d ḥed s wawař mɣir ak-d Wudayen waha. \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Řex. 8:1, 4. \x*
\v 20 Tuɣa din jar asen ca n yeryazen zi Qubrus u zi Qayrawan inni, ařami dd-usin ɣar Antiyuxiya, tuɣa issawařen ak-d Iyunaniyyen, barrḥen asen s Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ.
\v 21 Tuɣa afus n SIDI akidsen uca aṭṭas umnen, dewřen-dd ɣar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 11:21 \xt Řex. 2:47; 5:14. \x*
\m 
\v 22 Ikka-dd řexbar xasen x imezzuɣen n ayt n tmesmunt di Urcalim. Nitni ssekken Bar-Naba ɣar Antiyuxiya.
\v 23 Ařami dd-yiweḍ \add din\add*, iẓra arḍa n AREBBI, uca ifarḥ, iɛřem asen ḥima ad qqimen ttcebbaren di Siditneɣ s marra uř nsen. \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt Řex. 13:43; 14:22. \x*
\v 24 Minzi tuɣa-t d aryaz isegged, iccur s Arruḥ Iqeddsen d l’iman, uca ijj n ubarru d ameqqran \add n iwdan\add* immarni-dd ɣar Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt Řex. 4:36; 6:5. \x*
\v 25 Xenni iruḥ ɣar Tarsus ḥima ad yarzu x Cawul, \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Řex. 9:27. \x*
\v 26 uca ařami t yufa, yiwi i-t akides ɣar Antiyuxiya. Uca imsar aqa nitni munen di tmesmunt aseggʷas ikmeř uca ssřemden ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran. Zi  řweqt nni ttwasemman imeḥḍaren d ‘imasiḥiyyen’ i umur amezwaru. \f ◼ \fr 11:26 \fk tamesmunt\ft - niɣ: ‘jmaɛet n řmuminin’.\f*
\m 
\v 27 Deg wussan nni hwan-dd ca n inabiyyen zi Urcalim ɣar din.
\v 28 Uca ikkar ijj n zzaysen qqaren as Aɣabus, iɛřem asen s Arruḥ belli ijj n řaẓ imɣar ad yekk x marra tammurt. Uca yusa-dd řaẓ-a deg wussan n qayṣar Kludiyus. \x ◘ \xo 11:28 \xt Řex. 21:10. \x*
\v 29 Xenni ggin imeḥḍaren aqa kuř ijj zzaysen ad igg ca n twiza ɣar uɣezdis ɛlaḥsab tizemmar nnes i wawmaten i izeddɣen di Yahudiyya.
\v 30 Uca amenni i ggin nitni, uca ssekken t din ɣar imɣaren \add n řgens\add* i din iǧan s ufus n Bar-Naba d Cawul. \x ◘ \xo 11:30 \xt Řex. 12:25. \x*
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Řmewt n Yaɛqub d ufekki n Buṭrus
\m 
\v 1 Di řweqt nni ɛřaḥař isswiẓẓeḍ Hirudus afus nnes ḥima ad ikarfes x ca n yinni iǧan zi tmesmunt.
\v 2 Inɣa Yaɛqub umas n Yuḥanna s ssif. \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Mt. 4:21. \x*
\v 3 Umi iẓra aqa man aya iɛjeb asen i Wudayen, ikemmeř deg webrid nni maḥend ad iṭṭef uřa d Cimɛun Buṭrus. Tuɣa d ussan n \add Weɣrum\add* břa Antun.
\v 4 \add Řami\add* t iṭṭef, igga i-t di řeḥbes, uca igga as deg ifassen n setta-ɛecra n iɛessasen, ḥima ad xas ɛessen. Tuɣa ixs ad t iqeddem zzat i Wudayen awarni i \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Yḥ. 21:18. \x*
\v 5 Umi tuɣa ɛessen x Cimɛun di řeḥbes, tuɣa teẓẓaǧa tmesmunt i AREBBI břa qeṭṭu di ṭṭweɛ nnes.
\m 
\v 6 Di ǧiřet, ɣar tuffut i di tuɣa izɛem \add Hirudus\add* ad t iqeddem, umi iṭṭeṣ Cimɛun am t cedden s tnayen n ssnaseř jar tnayen n iɛessasen n řɛeskar u inneɣni ḥeṭṭan ɣar tewwart n řeḥbes,
\v 7 ibedd-dd lmalak n SIDI sennej nnes u ṭṭya n tfawt tᵉttceɛciɛ di marra axxam uca netta iɛarn i-t deg uɣezdis nnes, issfaq i-t, inna: “Kkar deɣya!” Deɣya wḍant ssnaseř zeg ifassen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Řex. 5:19; 16:26. \x*
\v 8 Inna as lmalak: “Byes, teqqned tisiřa nnec!” Igga ammu. Inna as xenni: “Arḍ ajeǧab nnec, ḍfar ayi-dd!”
\v 9 Xenni iffeɣ, iḍfar i-t, war issin min d as igga lmalak, aqa man aya d tidett, maɣar ittɣiř as iẓra ijj n řewḥiy.
\v 10 Ařami kkin x uɛessas amezwaru d x wenni wiss tnayen, iwḍen ɣar tewwart n wuzzař tenni ittawyen ɣar tendint, tennurzem asen weḥḥdes. Awarni řami zzayes ffɣen, qeḍɛen ict n zzenqet, řexdenni ijja i-t lmalak.
\m 
\v 11 Xenni idweř-dd Cimɛun ɣar řbař nnes, inna: “Řexxu ssneɣ s tidett belli SIDI issekk-dd lmalak nnes, issenjem ayi zeg ifassen n Hirudus u zi marra min zeɛmen ad ayi ggen Wudayen.”
\v 12 Umi tuɣa ittxarreṣ di man aya, yusa-dd ɣar taddart n Maryam, yemmas n Yuḥanna, wenni ittkennan Markus, mani tuɣa ttmunan aṭṭas, ttẓaǧan \add din\add*.
\m 
\v 13 Ařami issqarqeb di tewwart n barra n řemraḥ, tusa-dd ict n tḥenjirt, qqaren as Ruda ḥima ad tseř \add wi dinni\add*.
\v 14 Teɛqeř tmijja n Cimɛun, uca zi ssibbet n řefraḥet war tarzim ca tewwart, \add maca\add* teɛqeb deɣya uca txebbar i-ten, inna asen: “Xzar, Cimɛun, aqa ibedd ɣar tewwart n řemraḥ!”
\v 15 Nnan as: “Aqa cem txeřfed!” Maca nettat teqqim teqqar aqa man aya nican. Nnan as: “Ma ad taɣ d lmalak nnes!”
\m 
\v 16 Maca Cimɛun, iqqim issqarqub uca ffɣen, ẓrin t uca tbehten.
\v 17 Iceyyar asen s ufus nnes ḥima ad sqaren uca iɛawed asen mammec t-i-dd-issuffeɣ SIDI zi řeḥbes, inna: “Xebbarem Yaɛqub d tawmat x uya!” Xenni iffeɣ ɣar ijj n wemcan nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt Řex. 13:16; 19:33; 21:40. \x*
\m 
\v 18 Řami dd-yiweḍ uziř, imsar ijj n uxarweḍ i war iǧin drust jar řɛeskar x min imsaren i Cimɛun.
\v 19 Awarni řami tuɣa xas yarezzu Hirudus, maca war t yufi, iḥkem x iɛessasen s řmewt, iffeɣ zi Yahudiyya, iqqim izeddeɣ di Qayṣariya.
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Hirudus Aɣripas
\m 
\v 20 Umi tuɣa řeɛdawet di Hirudus ḍidd i ayt n Ṣur d Ṣaydun, munen nitni, iwḍen ad ssqenɛen Blastus amsexxar icennɛen n ujeǧid uca ttaren as maḥend ad asen iwc ijj n weṣřaḥ, minzi macca n temmurt nsen tekka-dd zi tgeldit n Hirudus.
\v 21 Deg ijj n wass \add n řfarḥ\add* ittwassnen yarḍ Hirudus ajeǧab n ujeǧid am iqqim x řkursi n ccreɛ, uca issiweř i řɣaci.
\v 22 Uca marra řgens isɣuy ɣares: “Aqa d awařen n AREBBI, war iǧi n bnadem.”
\v 23 Řexdenni iwta i-t lmalak n SIDI, minzi netta war iwci aɛuǧi i AREBBI. Uca dřen t ikeccawen, iffeɣ zzayes buḥbeř.
\b
\m 
\v 24 Awař n AREBBI ittwabarreḥ \add zzayes\add*, imeqqar. \x ◘ \xo 12:24 \xt Ica. 55:11; Řex. 6:7. \x*
\v 25 Bar-Naba d Cawul ɛeqben-dd zi Urcalim ɣar Antiyukiya awarni řami kemmřen tasexxart nsen uca iwyen akidsen Yuḥanna, wenni umi ttkennan Markus.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Řixḍaret n Barnaba d Bulus i tsexxart nsen
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa din di Antiyuxiya di tmesmunt inabiyyen d imseřmaden: Bar-Naba, d Cimɛun wenni ittkennan Nijer, d Lukiyus zi tendint n Qayrawan, d Manaɛin wenni d mmis n wenni yarebban Hirudus, řḥakem x ijj n arbaɛ n temmurt, d Cawul. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Řex. 14:26. \x*
\v 2 Am tuɣa ttẓumman, ttzawgen AREBBI, inna asen Arruḥ Iqeddsen: “Farzem ayi-dd Bar-Naba d Cawul i řxedmet tenni umi d asen dd-řaɣiɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Mt. 9:38; Řex. 9:15; 22:21; Rum. 1:1; 10:15; Gal. 1:15; 2:8; Afa. 3:8; 1 Tim. 2:7; 2 Tim. 1:11; Ɛbr. 5:4. \x*
\v 3 Awarni řami ẓummen, ẓẓuǧen, ssarsen xasen ifassen, sekken ten. \x ◘ \xo 13:3 \xt Řex. 6:6; 8:15; 19:6. \x*
\b
\s1 Asafar amezwaru n Bulus ɣar Qubrus
\m 
\v 4 Řami tuɣa dd-ttwassekken zi Arruḥ Iqeddsen, hwan-dd ɣar Salukiya uca ssenni ruḥen di řebḥar ɣar Qubrus.
\v 5 Umi iwḍen ɣar Salamis, barrḥen s wawař n Siditneɣ di temzidawin n Wudayen. Tuɣa Yuḥanna ittsexxar i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Řex. 12:25. \x*
\m 
\v 6 Awarni řami ẓwan marra tagzirt, iwḍen-dd ɣar Pafus. Nitni ufin din ijj n weryaz d Uday, tuɣa wanita d aseḥḥar, d anabi issxarriqen, qqaren as Bar-Cuma. \f ◼ \fr 13:6 \fk Bar-Cuma\ft - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini: ‘mmis n yisem’. S řxeṭṭ agřinzi qqaren as ‘Bar-Yasuɛ’, ixs ad yini ‘mmis n Yasuɛ’. Maca ḥima war din ittiři usekkwi jar Lmasiḥ d bnadem wanita, negg as ‘Bar-Cuma’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Řex. 8:9; 19:13. \x*
\v 7 Netta ɣares ict n tesɣunt imten ak-d ijj n bnadem d amiɣis, lɛamil umi qqaren Sarjiyus Bulus. Iřaɣa-dd lɛamil i Bar-Naba d Cawul, tuɣa immeẓri ad iseř awař n AREBBI.
\v 8 Maca aseḥḥar Bar-Cuma, isem wanita ittwatarjem s ‘Ilimas’, tuɣa ittɛekkas i-ten, yarzu ad issbeɛɛed lwali x l’iman. \x ◘ \xo 13:8 \xt Uf. 7:11; 2 Tim. 3:8\x*
\v 9 Maca Cawul umi qqaren ɛawed Bulus, ittwaccur s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, ijɛar dayes mliḥ, inna:
\v 10 “A \add cek\add*, aqa teccured s kuř řɣecc d kuř teḥraymect, \add a cek\add* mmis n ibřis d řeɛdu n marra tasegda. Ma aqa cek war tbedded \add ɛemmarṣ\add* ad tessxarwḍed ibriden iseggden n SIDI?
\v 11 Řexxu, xzar, aqa da afus n SIDI ḍidd nnec, ad tdewřed d adarɣař, war tᵉttwiřid tafuct \add ɛad\add* i yijj n řmijař.” Řexdenni tewḍa-dd xas tayyut d taǧest uca ibda iddura ittfafa, yarezzu wi t ɣa igewwden zeg ufus.
\v 12 Řami iẓra lɛamil min imsaren, itebhet uca yumen di tɣuri n SIDI.
\b
\s1 Bulus d Barnaba ɣar Antiyuxiya di Pisidiya
\m 
\v 13 Bulus d Bar-Naba kkin x řebḥar zi tendint n Pafus uca iwḍen ɣar tendint n Pirxa di Pamfiliya. Ssenni yuyur xasen Yuḥanna, iɛqeb ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Řex. 15:38. \x*
\m 
\v 14 Maca nitni ruḥen zi Pirxa, \add kkin x temmurt,\add* uca iwḍen ɣar Antiyuxiya, ict n tendint di \add jjwayeh n\add* Pisidiya. Udfen nitni ɣar temzida deg wass n ssebt uca qqimen dinni.
\v 15 Awarni tiɣri n Ccariɛa d Inabiyyen, ssekken ɣarsen imɣaren n temzida, nnan: “\add A\add* iryazen tawmat, mařa tuɣa ɣarwem ijj n wawař n ucejjeɛ i iwdan, barrḥem zzayes i řgens!”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Bulus iceyyar s ufus nnes, inna:
\b
\m “A kenniw, iryazen n Israil u kenniw inni itteggʷeden AREBBI, sřem! \x ◘ \xo 13:16 \xt Řex. 12:17; 19:33; 21:40. \x*
\v 17 AREBBI n řgens-a tuɣa ifarz řejdud nneɣ uca issgeɛɛed i-ten u immarni daysen aṭṭas řami ten tuɣa d imeɛzab di temmurt n Miṣra uca issuffeɣ i-ten s ufus nnes yuɛřan, \x ◘ \xo 13:17 \xt Uf. 1:1. \x*
\v 18 issecca i-ten řmijař n arebɛin n iseggʷusa di řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt Uf. 16:35; Řxř. 14:34; Izhd. 95:10. \x*
\v 19 Iteḥḥa sebɛa n řegnus di temmurt n Kenɛan, uca iwca asen temmurt nsen d řwart i nitni. \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Aɛwd. 7:1; Yac. 14:2. \x*
\v 20 Netta iwca asen řquḍat i yijj n řmijař n arebɛa-mya u-xemsin n iseggʷusa, ař řweqt n unabi Camwil. \x ◘ \xo 13:20 \xt Řqḍ. 2:16; 3:9. \x*
\m 
\v 21 Xenni ttaren ijj n ujeǧid i yixef nsen uca AREBBI iwca asen Cawul, mmis n Kis, ijj n weryaz zi teqbič n Binyamin, řmijař n arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Ṣm. 8:5; 9:15; 10:15; Ḥuc. 13:11. \x*
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* ikkes i-t, issgeɛɛed asen Dawud d ajeǧid, wenni umi x iched \add AREBBI\add* ɛawed \add ammu\add*: ‘Ufiɣ Dawud mmis n Yassa, aqa-t d ijj n weryaz yusa-dd x řxaḍar inu, wenni i ɣa iggin marra min xseɣ Necc.’ \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Ṣm. 13:14; 16:12; Izhd. 89:21; Řex. 7:45. \x*
\m 
\v 23 Zi zzariɛet nnes igga AREBBI i Israil Yasuɛ Amsenjem am mammec tuɣa zzayes iwaɛd.
\v 24 Issekk Yuḥanna ḥima ad ibarreḥ s uṣeɣḍaṣ n ttubet qbeř twasit nnes i marra řgens n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt Mt. 3:1; Mk. 1:2; Lk. 3:2; Yḥ. 3:23. \x*
\v 25 Umi dd-yiweḍ Yuḥanna ikemmeř tasexxart nnes, inna: ‘Min d awem ittɣiř aqa d necc? War ǧiɣ d \add Lmasiḥ\add*, maca, xzar, Netta ad dd-yas awarni ayi, Wenni umi necc war sdiheǧeɣ ad as fesyeɣ ifiřan n sandaliyat nnes!’ \x ◘ \xo 13:25 \xt Mt. 3:11; Yḥ. 1:20. \x*
\m 
\v 26 \add A\add* iryazen tawmat, tarwa n jjiř n Ibrahim d yinni akidwem itteggʷeden AREBBI: I kenniw umi dd-ittwassekk Netta, Wenni d Awař Iddaren. \x ◘ \xo 13:26 \xt Mt. 10:6; Řex. 3:26; 13:46. \x*
\v 27 Minzi imezdaɣ n Urcalim d imeqqranen nsen war d as fhimen uřa d idlisen n inabiyyen i iqqaren kuř ssebt, maca nitni ḥekmen xas u \add ammu\add* kemmřen nitni min yuran. \x ◘ \xo 13:27 \xt Yḥ. 16:3; Řex. 3:17; 1 Kur. 2:8; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 28 Waxxa war ufin uřa d ijj n řesbab ḥima ad xas ḥekmen s řmewt, ttaren zi Pilaṭus \add ttesřiḥ\add* ḥima ad t nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 13:28 \xt Mt. 27:20; Mk. 15:11; Lk. 23:18; Yḥ. 19:6. \x*
\v 29 Umi kemmřen marra min xas yuran, ssehwan t-i-dd zi teḥnact uca ssarsen t deg wenḍeř.
\v 30 Maca AREBBI issnekkar i-t-i-dd zi taddart n imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 13:30 \xt Mt. 28:6; Mk. 16:6; Lk. 24:6. \x*
\v 31 Iḍhar asen-dd aṭṭas n wussan i yinni akis igeɛɛden zi Ljalil ɣar Urcalim uca řexxu aqa aten d řechud nnes zzat i řgens. \x ◘ \xo 13:31 \xt Mk. 16:14; Yḥ. 20:19; 21:1; Řex. 1:3; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\v 32 Xzar, uřa d neccin nettbarreḥ i kenniw s wawař n lwaɛd i ittwannan i řejdud nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 13:32 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:24; Dan. 9:24, 25. \x*
\v 33 Xzar, AREBBI ikemmeř \add lwaɛd\add* i neccin, inni iǧan d tarwa nsen, umi dd-issnekkar Yasuɛ \add zi řmewt\add*. Am mammec tura deg uzehhid wiss tnayen:
\b
\m \qt ‘Cek d Mmi, ass-a jjiɣ-dd Cek!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:33 \xt Izhd. 2:7. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 34 S uya issnekkar i-t-i-dd AREBBI zi taddart n imettinen ařami war dd-iddikkwiř ɛemmarṣ ařami ɣa ikiccu, am t inna:
\b
\m \qt ‘Necc ad awem wceɣ\qt*
\m \qt \tl timegga n\tl* arḍa n Dawud\qt*
\m \qt i daysent řaman.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:34 \xt Ica. 55:3. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 35 S uyenni iqqar ɛawed deg ijj n wemcan nneɣni:
\b
\m \qt ‘Cek war tᵉttejjid Amsizdeg nnec\qt*
\m \qt ad ikiccu.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:35 \xt Izhd. 16:10; Izhd. 49:10; Řex. 2:27. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 36 Minzi Dawud isexxar jar jjiř nnes ɛlaḥsab min ixs AREBBI, uca immut, ittwassmun ɣar řejdud nnes, xenni ikiccu. \x ◘ \xo 13:36 \xt 1 Ij. 2:10; Řex. 2:29. \x*
\v 37 Maca Wanita, wenni dd-issnekkar AREBBI, war ittkicci.
\m 
\v 38 S uya, \add a\add* tawmat, snem aqa s Wa ittwabarreḥ s weɣfar n ddnub i kenniw, \x ◘ \xo 13:38 \xt Lk. 24:47; 1 Yḥ. 2:12\x*
\v 39 u \add snem\add* aqa zi marra min zi war tzemmarem ad tᵉttwaseggdem s Ccariɛa n Musa, aqa ad ttwaseggden marra inni yumnen zzayes Netta. \x ◘ \xo 13:39 \xt Rum. 3:28; 8:3; 10:4; Gal. 2:16; Ɛbr. 7:19. \x*
\v 40 Ḥḍam xenni ḥima war xawem dd-iweṭṭi ca n min yuran deg \add idlisen n\add* inabiyyen:
\b
\m 
\v 41 \qt ‘Xzarem, \tl a\tl* kenniw inni ittbuṣaren,\qt*
\m \qt tɛejbem u tweddarem,\qt*
\m \qt minzi Necc ad ggeɣ ict n řxedmet\qt*
\m \qt deg wussan nwem\qt*
\m \qt i war tᵉttiqqim\qt*
\m \qt waxxa iɛawed awem tt ca n ijjen.’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:41 \xt Ica. 28:14; Ḥab. 1:5. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 42 Řami zzaysen dd-ffɣen, ttaren zzaysen ḥima ad kisen ssiwřen s wawařen d ijjen deg ijj n ssebt nneɣni.
\v 43 Řami immsebḍa \add umuni n\add* temzida, aṭṭas n Wudayen d waṭṭas n imɛacaren n Wudayen inni itteggʷeden AREBBI ḍfaren Bulus d Bar-Naba. Nitni tuɣa kisen ssawařen, ɛeřmen asen ḥima ad qqimen ttᵉṭṭfen deg arḍa n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 13:43 \xt Řex. 11:23; 14:22. \x*
\m 
\v 44 Di ssebt i dd-yusin tusa-dd tendint marra ḥima ad tseř i Wawař n AREBBI.
\v 45 Ařami ẓrin Wudayen řɣaci d ameqqran, dewřen ɛemmaren s řeḥsed, ɛeksen min xef issiweř Bulus, qacḥen u ceqqfen \add dayes\add*.
\v 46 Maca Bulus d Bar-Naba nnan s teryast: “Tuɣa ittřiq ad awem nessiweř d amezwaru Awař n AREBBI, maca umi t tugim, u tekksem awař ḍidd i yixef nwem belli war tesdiheǧem Tudart ittduman, xzar, aqa \add řexxu\add* neccin ad nwejjeh řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 13:46 \xt Uf. 32:10; Ica. 55:5; Mt. 8:12; 10:6; 21:43; Řex. 3:26; 13:26; Rum. 10:19. \x*
\v 47 Minzi ammu d aneɣ iweṣṣa Siditneɣ, iqqar:
\b
\m \qt ‘Necc arriɣ Cek d tafawt i řegnus,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad tiřid i Tudart ař ṭṭrufa n ddunect.’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:47 \xt Ica. 42:6; 49:6; Lk. 2:32. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 48 Umi sřin řegnus man aya, farḥen ssemɣaren awař n Sidi uca umnen marra inni tuɣa ittwafarzen i Tudart ittduman.
\v 49 Uca iffeɣ Awař n SIDI ɣar jjihet nni marra.
\m 
\v 50 Maca Udayen ssḥarrcen imcennɛen n tendint d temɣarin tinni ɣarsent ccan u ɛebbdent i AREBBI akidsen. Ammu ssekkaren nitni ict n umarret x Bulus d Bar-Naba uca ssuffɣen ten barra i temmurt nsen. \x ◘ \xo 13:50 \xt 2 Tim. 3:11. \x*
\v 51 Maca nitni zzerzen taɛejjajt zeg iḍaren nsen xasen uca iwḍen ɣar tendint n Ikuniya.\x ◘ \xo 13:51 \xt Mt. 10:14; Mk. 6:11; Lk. 9:5; 10:11\x*
\v 52 Imeḥḍaren dewřen ccuren s řefraḥet n Arruḥ Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 13:52 \xt Řex. 13:52; Gal. 5:22; 1 Th. 1:6\x*
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Bulus d Barnaba ruḥen ɣar Ikuniya di Likaɛunya
\m 
\v 1 Deg Ikuniya udfen nitni jmiɛ ɣar temzida n Wudayen uca ssiwřen ařami umnen aṭṭas n řɣaci, am Wudayen am Iyunaniyyen.
\v 2 Maca Udayen inni war yuminen, ssekkaren \add iryazen n tendint i yeǧan zi\add* řegnus, maḥend ad ssɛiǧten tawmat.
\v 3 \add Waxxa amenni\add* kkin dinni aṭṭas n řweqt, ttbarrḥen s bṭayṭay s SIDI. U Netta tuɣa ittic cchadet i Wawař n arḍa nnes s řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb i igga s ifassen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Mk. 16:20; Řex. 19:11; Ɛbr. 2:4. \x*
\v 4 Marra řɣaci \add n imezdaɣ\add* n tendint immsebḍa. Ca \add zzaysen\add* ruḥen ak-d Wudayen u ca nneɣni ak-d rrusul.
\v 5 Tuɣa din ict n tmeɛmuč xasen zeg yinni zi řegnus u zeg Wudayen ak-d imeqqranen nsen, ḥima ad xasen karfsen u ḥima ad ten arejmen.
\v 6 Řami ssnen man aya, ffɣen-dd uca arewřen ɣar tneddam n Likaɛunya, aqa aten d Listra d Dirbi, u ɣar dcurat i d as dd-innḍen, \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Mt. 10:23; Řex. 8:1. \x*
\v 7 uca ttbarrḥen dinni s Řexbar Aṣebḥan.
\b
\s1 Abarreḥ d uḥejjar n Bulus di Listra
\m 
\v 8 Tuɣa izeddeɣ ijj n weryaz di Listra wenni d aneɛḍab deg iḍaren nnes, aqa-t d aqejdaḥ zeg uɛeddis n yemmas, war yuyur ɛemmarṣ. \x ◘ \xo 14:8 \xt Řex. 3:2. \x*
\v 9 Tuɣa ittesřa i Bulus am issawař netta. Řami t iẓra Bulus, yuca aqa dayes l’iman ḥima ad ittwassgenfa.
\v 10 Inna as s ict n tmijja tejhed: “Ad ac iniɣ deg Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, kkar, tbedded nican x iḍaren nnec!” Ingez, ikkar, uca iggur.
\m 
\v 11 Řami iẓra řɣaci min igga Bulus, ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen, nnan s řhard n temmurt nni: “Aqa irebbiten dewřen arewsen deg iwdan, hwan-dd ɣarneɣ!” \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Řex. 28:6. \x*
\v 12 Nitni semman Bar-Naba s yisem ‘Sidi n irebbiten’, u Bulus s yisem ‘Hirmis’, minzi netta izwar ɣar wawař.
\v 13 Akehhan n ‘Sidi n irebbiten’ tuɣa barra i tendint, yiwi iyenduzen d tseddiyin n nnuwwac ɣar tiwwura n řemraḥ mani qqimen, tuɣa ixs ad ten iqeddem d tɣarṣt i nitni.
\m 
\v 14 Řami sřin Bar-Naba d Bulus x man aya, carrgen arruḍ nsen, negzen, ffɣen ɣar barra jar řɣaci, sɣuyyun, nnan:
\v 15 “\add A\add* iryazen, min i tᵉtteggem? Uřa d neccin d lbacar d ijjen am kenniw, nettbarreḥ kenniw ḥima ad tbeɛɛdem x tmesřayin-a ibeṭṭřen, ḥima ad tubem ɣar AREBBI iddaren i dd-ixeřqen ajenna d temmurt d řebḥar d marra min daysen. \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt Amz. 1:1; Izhd. 33:6; 124:8; 146:6; Řex. 10:26; Asa. 14:7; 19:10; 22:9. \x*
\v 16 Di řweqt n řejyuř iɛdun ijja Netta marra řegnus ad uyuren deg ibriden nsen, \x ◘ \xo 14:16 \xt Izhd. 81:13. \x*
\v 17 waxxa war ijji Ixef nnes břa cchadet am d asen iwca tcuni zeg ujenna, issehwa-dd anẓar u iwca aṭṭas n řɣiǧet di řweqt nsen \add ittwaggen\add* uca issjiwen uřawen nneɣ s macca d řefraḥet.” \x ◘ \xo 14:17 \xt Rum. 1:19. \x*
\v 18 Waxxa ssawařen amenni, tuɣa ɛad iqseḥ xasen ad ssbedden řɣaci, maḥend uřa d ijj war ittqeddim tiɣarṣin i nitni.
\m 
\v 19 Maca usin-dd Wudayen zi Ikuniya d Antiyuxiya, ssḥarrcen xasen řɣaci uca arejmen Bulus, jarren t barra i tendint, minzi ittɣiř asen aqa immut. \x ◘ \xo 14:19 \xt 2 Kur. 11:25. \x*
\v 20 Maca am d as dd-nnḍen imeḥḍaren, ikkar uca yudef ɣar tendint. Xenni tiwecca nnes iffeɣ ak-d Bar-Naba, iwḍen nitni ɣar tendint n Dirbi.
\b
\s1 Aɛqab ɣar Antiyuxiya di Surya
\m 
\v 21 Umi barrḥen s Řexbar Aṣebḥan i imezdaɣ n tendint nni, ggin aṭṭas n imeḥḍaren. Xenni ɛeqben ɣar Listra d Ikuniya d Antiyuxiya,
\v 22 ggin uř di řeɛmur n imeḥḍaren, ɛeřmen asen ad cebbaren di l’iman, nnan asen belli ittxeṣṣa ad nadef ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI s waṭṭas n řemḥayem. \x ◘ \xo 14:22 \xt Mt. 10:38; 16:24; Lk. 24:26; Řex. 11:23; 13:43; 2 Tim. 3:12. \x*
\v 23 Areccḥen imɣaren di kuř tamesmunt am ttẓuman u ttẓaǧan akidsen, uca xenni sellmen ten i Siditneɣ i di umnen nitni.
\v 24 Xas uca ẓwan Pisidiya, usin-dd ɣar Pamfiliya.
\v 25 Awarni řami ssiwřen s Wawař n SIDI di Pirxa, hwan-dd ɣar Attalya.
\v 26 Ssenni ruḥen di řebḥar ɣar Antiyuxiya minzi ssenni tuɣa ttwassqebbḍen i arḍa n SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n řxedmet tenni aqa kemmřen. \x ◘ \xo 14:26 \xt Řex. 13:1. \x*
\v 27 Řami din iwḍen, řaɣan x tmesmunt, xebbaren s marra řexdayem timeqqranin i yegga AREBBI s ifassen nsen u mammec yarzem tawwart n l’iman i řegnus.
\v 28 Uca qqimen din ict řweqt d azirar ak-d imeḥḍaren. *
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Agraw n rrusul di Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 Hwan-dd yeryazen zi Yahudiyya \add ɣar Antiyuxiya\add* uca bdan sseřmaden i tawmat, nnan: “Mařa war tᵉttwaxetnem ɛlaḥsab tnamit n Ccariɛa \add n Musa\add*, war tzemmarem ad tᵉttwassnejmem.” \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Amz. 17:10; Lawi 12:3; Gal. 5:2. \x*
\v 2 Ikkar ijj n uxarweḍ d unaqec akidsen zi ṭṭarf n Bulus d Bar-Naba. Imsar aqa Bulus d Bar-Naba, u akidsen ɛad inneɣni, ruḥen ɣar rrusul d imɣaren di Urcalim zi ssibbet n unaqec-a. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Gal. 2:1. \x*
\m 
\v 3 Tessqebbeḍ u tessekk i-ten tmesmunt. Nitni cuqen di marra Finiqiya d temmurt n Samarya uca xebbaren mammec tuben inni iǧan zi řegnus, ssfarḥen marra tawmat aṭṭas.
\v 4 Řami iwḍen ɣar Urcalim, tareḥḥeb zzaysen tmesmunt d rrusul d imɣaren u nitni xebbaren \add i-ten\add* s marra min zzaysen igga AREBBI.
\m 
\v 5 Maca ca zi tebridt n Ifarisiyyen inni idewřen umnen, kkaren, nnan: “Ittxeṣṣa ad ten txetnem u ad ten umuren ad cebbaren di Ccariɛa n Musa.”
\m 
\v 6 Munen rrusul d imɣaren ḥima ad mcawaren x tmesřact-a.
\v 7 Awarni řami tuɣa ttqacaḥen aṭṭas, ibedd Cimɛun, inna asen: “A iryazen tawmat, kenniw tessnem belli aṭṭas zeg wami AREBBI ixḍar aqa řegnus ad sřen i wawař n Řexbar Aṣebḥan s uqemmum inu uca ad \add zzayes\add* amnen. \x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Řex. 10:20; 11:12. \x*
\v 8 AREBBI, wenni issnen min iǧan deg wuřawen, iched xasen am d asen iwca Arruḥ Iqeddsen am i neccin. \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt 1 Im. 28:9; 29:17; Izhd. 7:10; Irm. 11:20; 17:10; 20:12. \x*
\v 9 Netta war ittegg bu řfarz jar neccin d nitni, am issizdeg uřawen nsen s l’iman. \x ◘ \xo 15:9 \xt Řex. 10:43, 44. \x*
\v 10 Iwa řexxu, mayemmi tᵉttjarrabem ɛad AREBBI u tᵉtteggem ijj n uzayřu x irawen n imeḥḍaren i war zemmaren řejdud nneɣ uřa d neccin ad t narbu? \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Mt. 23:4. \x*
\v 11 Maca s arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ numen aqa ad neṭṭef Tudart am nitni.” \x ◘ \xo 15:11 \xt Afa. 2:8; Tit. 3:4. \x*
\m 
\v 12 Isqar řɣaci, nitni sřan i Bar-Naba d Bulus ttɛawaden x řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb timeqqranin i zzaysen igga AREBBI jar řegnus.
\v 13 Umi qqimen sqaren, ikkar Yaɛqub, inna: “\add A\add* iryazen tawmat, sřem-dd ɣari.
\v 14 Cimɛun ixebbar mammec tuɣa igga AREBBI deg umezwar ḥima ad ixdar ijj n řgens zi řegnus i Yisem nnes.
\v 15 Man aya ittas-dd ak-d wawařen n inabiyyen am mammec tura:
\b
\m 
\v 16 \qt “‘Awarni man aya ad dd-ɛeqbeɣ\qt*
\m \qt uca ad ssbeddeɣ \tl ɛawed\tl*\qt*
\m \qt Tazeddiɣt iwḍan n Dawud,\qt*
\m \qt u min zzayes yareddǧen\qt*
\m \qt ad tt ssgeɛɛdeɣ\qt*
\m \qt uca ad tt areqqɛeɣ ɛawed,\qt*
\m 
\v 17 \qt ḥima min iqqimen n iwdan\qt*
\m \qt ad arzun x SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt uřa d marra řegnus\qt*
\m \qt i xef ittwařaɣa s Yisem inu!’,\qt*
\m \qt \tl ammu\tl* i iqqar SIDI\qt*
\m \qt wenni iggin marra aya.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:17 \xt Ɛam. 9:11, 12. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 Řexdayem n AREBBI aqa ttwassnent zi řebda.
\v 19 S uyenni ttwařiɣ icuwwar war nesseḍqiř ca x yinni dd-iddakkwařen ɣar AREBBI zi řegnus,
\v 20 maca ad asen nari ḥima ad beɛɛden x texmuji zi tɣarṣa \add i l’aṣnam\add* u x farq-ccɣeř u x jjiyfat u x idammen. \x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt Amz. 9:4; Uf. 20:3; 1 Kur. 8:1; 10:20;1 Ts. 4:3. \x*
\v 21 Minzi Musa tuɣa ɣares di kuř tandint imxeṭṭaben di temzidawin di řejyuř iɛdun, inni zzayes qqaren di marra ussan n ssebt.”
\b
\s1 Tabrat ɣar tmesmunt di Antiyuxiya
\m 
\v 22 Xenni ixḍaren rrusul d imɣaren, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra tamesmunt, iryazen zi řwesṭ nsen uca ssekken Yahuda, umi qqaren ɛawed Bar-Saba, d Sila ak-d Bulus d Bar-Naba ɣar Antiyuxiya. Iryazen-a tuɣa aten d imeqqranen jar tawmat.
\v 23 Urin s ufus nsen ammu:
\b
\m “Rrusul d imɣaren d tawmat.
\m I tawmat i yeǧan di Antiyuxiya d Suriya d Kilikiya, i tawmat i yeǧan zi řegnus. Sřam xawem!
\m 
\v 24 Nesřa belli ca n yinni dd-yusin zi řwesṭ nneɣ, ṣedɛen kenniw s wawařen nsen, ssenhezzen tanefsect nwem, qqaren: ‘Ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwaxetnem u ad tᵉṭṭfem di Ccariɛa!’, umi neccin war d asen numur s man aya. \x ◘ \xo 15:24 \xt Gal. 2:4. \x*
\v 25 S uya nemcawar awarni řami nmun marra, uca nfarz ca n yeryazen ḥima ad ten nessekk ɣarwem ak-d imɛizzen nneɣ Bar-Naba d Bulus.
\v 26 Nitni d iryazen inni iṭṭewwɛen tudart nsen i Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 15:26 \xt Řex. 13:50; 14:19. \x*
\v 27 Nessekk-dd akidsen Yahuda d Sila, inni kenniw i ɣa ixebbaren man aya ɛawed s uqemmum nsen.
\v 28 Minzi aqa-t di řxaḍar n Arruḥ Iqeddsen u di řxaḍar nneɣ, ḥima war xawem nesseḍqiř ca sennej i timesřayin tinni labudda zzaysent,
\v 29 aqa ad taggʷejem x min wehhben d taɣarṣt i l’aṣnam řa x idammen řa x jjiyfat uřa x farq-ccɣeř! Mařa teḥḍam ixef nwem zi man aya, ad teggem mliḥ. Iřim d imtiqqan di Siditneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt Amz. 9:4; Uf. 20:3; Lawi 17:14; 1 Kur. 8:1; 1 Ts. 4:3. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 30 Inni dd-ittwassekken iwḍen ɣar Antiyuxiya uca ssmunen marra iwdan, wcin asen tabrat.
\v 31 Řami tt ɣrin, farḥen nitni, ttwassfewwjen.
\v 32 S wawařen aṭṭas ssjehden nitn tawmat uca ssmetnen inni iǧan ak-d Yahuda d Sila, maɣar uřa d nitni tuɣa aten d inabiyyen.
\v 33 Awarni řami qqimen dinni ca n řweqt, ssqebbḍen ten wawmaten s řehna ḥima ad dd-dewřen ɣar rrusul.
\v 34 Maca Sila tuɣa ixs ad iqqim dinni.
\m 
\v 35 Bulus d Bar-Naba qqimen di Antiyuxiya, ssɣaran, ttbarrḥen s Wawař n AREBBI ak-d waṭṭas inneɣni.
\b
\s1 Amsebḍi n Bulus d Barnaba
\m 
\v 36 Awarni ca n wussan inna Bulus i Bar-Naba: “Ejj aneɣ ad neɛqeb ɣar tawmat di kuř tandint mani tuɣa nettbarreḥ s Wawař n AREBBI, ad nargeb mammec ɣa iffeɣ umeddur nsen.”
\v 37 Bar-Naba tuɣa ixs ad kisen indeh Yuḥanna, wenni ittkennan Markus, \x ◘ \xo 15:37 \xt Uf. 20:3. \x*
\v 38 maca Bulus tuɣa war ixs ad t yiwi, minzi \add Markus\add* ismeḥ daysen umi tuɣa aten di Pamfiliya, u minzi war kisen iruḥ.
\v 39 Ikkar ijj n umcubbec d ameqqran jar asen ařami mmsebḍan ijjen x wenneɣni. Bar-Naba yiwi Markus akides uca ibeḥḥar ɣar tegzirt n Qubrus.
\v 40 Maca Bulus ixḍar Sila uca iffeɣ, awarni řami sellmen t wawmaten ɣar arḍa n AREBBI.
\v 41 Icuq di Suriya d Kilikiya, ittcejjaɛ timesmunin.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Timutiyu iruḥ ak-d Bulus d Silas
\m 
\v 1 \add Řami\add* dd-yusa ɣar tneddam n Dirbi d Listra, tuɣa din ijj n umeḥḍar qqaren as Timutiyu. Tuɣa netta d mmis n ict n temɣart d tudact d řmumina, maca babas d Aramiyu. \f ◼ \fr 16:1 \fk Aramiyu\ft - di řmaxtuṭṭat s yiřes n Tyunanit ad naf: ‘Ayunani’.\f*
\v 2 Marra tawmat n Listra d Ikuniya cehden xas s řxar.
\v 3 Bulus tuɣa ixs wa ad isafar akides. \add Xenni\add* iksi t uca ixten as, minzi Udayen di tendint nni ssnen belli babas d Aramiyu. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt 1 Kur. 9:20; Gal. 2:3. \x*
\b
\s1 Asafar wiss tnayen n Bulus: Masiduniya, Atina d Kurintus
\m 
\v 4 Umi kkin x tneddam, ttbarrḥen, sseřmaden ten ɛawed maḥend ad ṭṭfen di tiweṣṣa i yuran rrusul d imɣaren di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt Řex. 15:20. \x*
\m 
\v 5 Ammu dewřent tmesmunin beddent mliḥ di l’iman uca tuɣa řqedd nsent imeqqar kuř ass.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Umi cuqen nitni di jjwayeh n Frixiya d Galaṭiya, imneɛ i-ten Arruḥ Iqeddsen maḥend ad beccaren s Wawař n AREBBI di Asiya.
\v 7 Řami dd-usin ɣar jjihet n Misya, arzun ad raḥen ɣar Bitiniya, maca Arruḥ n Yasuɛ war ten ijji. \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt Fil. 1:19 \x*
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ffɣen-dd zi Misya, hwan ɣar temmurt n Truwas. \x ◘ \xo 16:8 \xt 2 Kur. 2:12. \x*
\v 9 Deg ijj n řewḥiy s ǧiřet iban-dd ijj n weryaz zi Makiduniya ɣar Bulus, ibedd \add dinni\add*, ittar zzayes, inna: ‘Hwa-dd ɣar Makiduniya ḥima ad ayi tewced afus!’
\v 10 Awarni řami iẓra Bulus řewḥiy-a, nekkar řexdenni maḥend ad nraḥ ɣar Makiduniya, minzi nefhem belli Siditneɣ iřaɣa aneɣ-dd ḥima ad asen nbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan.
\b
\s1 Bulus di tendint n Filippi - L’iman n Lidiya
\m 
\v 11 Aqa nuyur di řebḥar zi Truwas uca nruḥ nican ɣar Samutraki, u tiwecca nnes \add nruḥ\add* ssenni ɣar Niyapulis.
\v 12 Ssenni \add nruḥ\add* ɣar Filippi, tenni d lɛaṣima n Makiduniya, tuɣa ṭṭfen tt Irumaniyyen d tzeddiɣt i nitni. Neqqim ijj n řmijař n ca n wussan di tendint nni.
\v 13 Deg wass n ssebt neffeɣ zi tewwart n tendint ɣar tma n iɣzar minzi neẓra din ict n taddart n tẓaǧit. Awarni řami neqqim din, nessiweř ak-d temɣarin tinni tuɣa imunen \add dinni\add*.
\v 14 Ict n temɣart nni izzenzen řeḥrar, qqarent as Ludiya zi tendint n Tiyatira, tuɣa tᵉtteggʷed AREBBI. Siditneɣ yarzem as uř nnes ḥima ad tseř mliḥ mixef issawař Bulus.
\v 15 Ttwasseɣḍeṣ nettat d aytbab n taddart nnes, uca xenni tᵉttar zzayneɣ, tenna: “Mařa s tidett tᵉttwařam belli necc umneɣ di Siditneɣ, iwa araḥem-dd, qqimem di taddart inu!” Tuɣa tzawg aneɣ aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Amz. 19:3; 33:11; Řqḍ. 19:21; Lk. 24:29; Ɛbr. 13:2. \x*
\b
\s1 Bulus d Silas di řeḥbes
\m 
\v 16 Am neggur ɣar taddart n tẓaǧit, temmseřqa akidneɣ ict n tayya, dayes řaryaḥ n tgezzant, tiwi-dd ijj n řefḍeř imɣar i aytbab nnes s tgezzant nni. \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt 1 Ṣm. 28:7; Řex. 19:24. \x*
\v 17 Nettat tḍeffar Bulus d neccin, tesɣuyyu, teqqar: “Iwdan-a d imsexxaren n AREBBI, Amɛuǧi x kuřci, nitni ttbarrḥen i kenniw s webrid n Tudart!”
\v 18 Ammu i teqqim aṭṭas n wussan. Maca Bulus, umi tuɣa ittxeyyaq x man aya, inneqřeb, inna i řaryaḥ: “Ttumureɣ cek s Yisem n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ffeɣ zzayes.” Uca iffeɣ-dd \add řaryaḥ\add* di tsaɛɛet nni. \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Mk. 16:17. \x*
\m 
\v 19 Umi ẓrin aytbab nnes belli asitem n řefḍeř nsen iffeɣ zzayes, ṭṭfen Bulus d Sila, jarren ten, iwyen ten ɣar ssuq. \x ◘ \xo 16:19 \xt 2 Kur. 6:5. \x*
\v 20 Nitni iwyen ten zzat i imxazniyyen u zzat i imḍebbaren n tendint, nnan: “Iwdan-a ttxarwaḍen tandint nneɣ, minzi nitni d Udayen. \x ◘ \xo 16:20 \xt 1 Ij. 18:17; Řex. 17:6. \x*
\v 21 Nitni ttbarḥen aneɣ s ttaqalid nni war iḥeǧeř ad tent neqbeř niɣ ad tent neḍfar, minzi neccin d Irumaniyyen!”
\v 22 Issmun xasen ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran. Xenni carrgen imxazniyyen arruḍ nsen, umuren ad ten hettken s urekkuḍ. \x ◘ \xo 16:22 \xt 2 Kur. 11:25; 1 Ts. 2:2. \x*
\v 23 Awarni řami ten hettken aṭṭas s urekkuḍ, nḍaren ten di řeḥbes, umuren i uɛessas n řeḥbes ḥima ad xasen iɛess mliḥ.
\v 24 U netta, umi iksi tawṣeyyet-a, issidef i-ten ɣar daxeř qaɛ n řeḥbes, iqqen i-ten zeg iḍaren nsen deg ijj n řqařeb n ǧuḥ.
\m 
\v 25 Deg wezyen n ǧiřet tuɣa Bulus d Sila ttẓaǧan u ttsebbaḥen AREBBI am d asen sřin imeḥbas. \x ◘ \xo 16:25 \xt Ayub 35:10; Izhd. 42:9; Řex. 4:31. \x*
\v 26 Řexdenni imsar ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt d ameqqran ařami ittwanhezz dsas n řeḥbes, uca deɣya nnurzment marra tiwwura uca dewřen iceddiyyen n marra \add imeḥbas\add* fesyen. \x ◘ \xo 16:26 \xt Řex. 5:19; 12:7. \x*
\m 
\v 27 Řami d ifaq uɛessas n řeḥbes, iẓra tiwwura arzment, ijbed ssif nnes, tuɣa iggur ad ineɣ ixef nnes, ittɣiř as belli imeḥbas arewřen.
\v 28 Maca Bulus iřaɣa s jjehd: “War ttḍarra ixef nnec, aqa aneɣ da marra!”
\v 29 Xenni issareɣ ijj n řefnar, ingez ɣar daxeř, ittarjiji, inḍar ixef nnes ɣar iḍaren n Bulus d Sila.
\m 
\v 30 Issuffeɣ i-ten-dd ɣar barra, inna: “\add A\add* řejwad, min ittxeṣṣa ad ggeɣ ḥima ad ṭṭfeɣ Tudart?” \x ◘ \xo 16:30 \xt Lk. 3:10; Řex. 2:37; 9:6. \x*
\v 31 Nitni nnan as: “Amen di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ad tᵉṭṭfed Tudart, cek d \add aytbab n\add* taddart nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 16:31 \xt Yḥ. 3:16,36; 6:47; 1 Yḥ. 5:10. \x*
\v 32 Ssiwřen Awař n SIDI akides u ak-d marra aytbab n taddart nnes.
\m 
\v 33 Di tsaɛɛet nni n ǧiřet iwyi ten-dd \add ɣares\add*, issird asen iyezzimen nsen uca deɣya ittwasseɣḍeṣ netta ak-d marra aytbab n taddart nnes.
\v 34 Xenni iwyi ten ɣar taddart nnes, issewjed asen ṭṭabřa, ifarḥ netta d aytbab n taddart nnes, minzi ṭṭfen l’iman zi AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 16:34 \xt Lk. 5:29; 19:6. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Umi dd-yiweḍ uziř, ssekken imxazniyyen iweqqafen x řaman, ḥima ad inin i uzeǧif n řeḥbes: “Ḍeřq asen-dd i iwdan nni.”
\v 36 Umi isřa aya uzeǧif n řeḥbes, yudef-dd ɣar daxeř uca issiweḍ awařen-a ɣar Bulus, inna: “Imxazniyyen sekken-dd ḥima ad awem ḍeřqen. Xenni řexxu, ffɣem, řuḥem di řehna!”
\v 37 Maca Bulus inna as: “Waxxa neccin d Irumaniyyen, jjin ad aneɣ hettken s urekkuḍ s bṭayṭay am war dayneɣ iǧi řɛib, nḍaren aneɣ di řeḥbes, uca řexxu, ma xsen nitni ad aneɣ ḍeřqen s tnuffra? Lla, ejj i-ten ad dd-asen s yixef nsen, ḥima ad aneɣ ḍeřqen.”
\v 38 Iweqqafen x řaman ruḥen, ssiwḍen awařen-a nni d asen ittwannan ɛawed ɣar izeǧifen n tendint. Uca nitni ggʷeden umi sřin aqa-ten d Irumaniyyen.
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd ɣarsen, ttaren zzaysen ad ruḥen, ad ffɣen zi tendint. \x ◘ \xo 16:39 \xt Mt. 8:34. \x*
\v 40 Awarni řami ffɣen-dd zi řeḥbes, ɛeqben ɣar Ludiya, mani ẓrin tawmat. Sscejjɛen ten uca uyuren.
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Bulus d Silas di Tissaluniki
\m 
\v 1 Ẓwan x Amfipulis d Apulluniya, iwḍen ɣar Tissalunika mani tuɣa ict n temzida n Wudayen.
\v 2 Bulus yudef-dd din ɣarsen, am tuɣa d lqaɛida nnes. Di třata \add n wussan\add* n ssebt issiweř akidsen zi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*.
\v 3 Iffessar u issbeyyen \add asen ammu\add*: “Tuɣa ittxeṣṣa i Lmasiḥ ad ittwaweddeb u ad dd-ikkar zi taddart n imettinen. Aqa Netta d Yasuɛ, Lmasiḥ min xef d awem barrḥeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Izhd. 22:7; Mt. 16:21; Lk. 24:46. \x*
\v 4 Ca zzaysen umnen, munen ak-d Bulus d Sila, uřa d aṭṭas n Iyunaniyyen inni itteggʷeden AREBBI, uřa d timɣarin icennɛen, war iǧi drust zzaysent, \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Řex. 28:24. \x*
\m 
\v 5 Maca Udayen dewřen ttasmen, nedhen ca n yeryazen iɛeffanen zeg ibriden n tendint, ssgeɛɛden ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran ɣarsen, sshajan tandint uca ssekkaran ten ḍidd n taddart n Yasun, arzun ad ten sellmen i řɣaci.
\v 6 Umi war ten ufin din, jarren Yasun d wawmaten i din iǧan ɣar izeǧifen n tendint, sɣuyyun: “Xzar, ina, inni issɣewwɣen tammurt marra, aqa usin-dd ɛawed da! \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Řex. 16:20. \x*
\v 7 Yasun issidef i-ten ɣares d inewjiwen, \add waxxa\add* nitni marra ttɛekksen tiwṣeyyat n qayṣar, qqaren aqa da ajeǧid nneɣni, aqa-t d Yasuɛ.” \x ◘ \xo 17:7 \xt Lk. 23:2; Yḥ. 19:12. \x*
\v 8 Ssarejfen izeǧifen n tendint d řgens umi sřin aya.
\v 9 Maca awarni řami ṭṭfen řɛarbunat zi Yasun d yinneɣni, arxun asen.
\b
\s1 Bulus d Silas di Biriya
\m 
\v 10 Řexdenni ssekken tawmat Bulus d Sila ɣar Biriya s ǧiřet. Umi din iwḍen, ruḥen ɣar temzida n Wudayen, \x ◘ \xo 17:10 \xt Řex. 9:25. \x*
\v 11 minzi Udayen dinni tuɣa aten xar zeg inni i yeǧan di Tissalunika, minzi tuɣa xsen ad sřen i Wawař kuř ass, arezzun ad ssnen zi Tira Iqeddsen, ma timesřayin-a aqa tent amenni. \x ◘ \xo 17:11 \xt Ica. 34:16; Lk. 16:29; Yḥ. 5:39. \x*
\v 12 Aṭṭas zzaysen umnen, uřa d aṭṭas n temɣarin d yeryazen zeg Iyunaniyyen.
\m 
\v 13 Maca, umi Udayen n Tissalunika ssnen belli Bulus tuɣa ittbarreḥ Awař n AREBBI di Biriya, usin-dd nitni ɛawed din, war ssbedden zeg usɣewweɣ u zeg usxarweḍ jar imezdaɣ \add n tendint\add*. \x ◘ \xo 17:13 \xt 1 Ts. 2:14. \x*
\v 14 \add Xas uca\add* jjin wawmaten ad ihwa Bulus řexdenni ɣar řebḥar, maca Sila d Timutiyu qqimen din.
\v 15 Inni issqebḍen Bulus, iwyen t ɣar tendint n Atina. Xenni, umi t jjin, ṭṭfen zzayes ict n tebrat i Sila d Timutiyu maḥend nitni ad ɣares dd-asen deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt Řex. 18:5. \x*
\b
\s1 Bulus di Atina
\m 
\v 16 Am ten tuɣa ittraja Bulus di Atina, tuɣa arruḥ nnes ixeyyeq umi iẓra tandint teccur s \add řexyařat n\add* l’aṣnam.
\v 17 S uyenni tuɣa issawař di temzida ak-d Wudayen u ak-d yinni itteggʷeden AREBBI, u di ssuq uřa ak-d inni i tuɣa ittmunen dinni kuř ass.
\v 18 Ɛad ca n ifaylasufen zi temzida n Ipikurus u ca nneɣni, qqaren as Istuwakiyyen, mnaqacen akides. Ca \add zzaysen\add* nnan: “Min ixs ad yini wanita s řhard-a qaɛ?” Maca inneɣni nnan: “Iḍhar-dd aqa-t d ambarreḥ n irebbiten iɣriben, minzi tuɣa ittbarreḥ asen s Yasuɛ d tnukra nnes \add zeg imettinen\add*.
\v 19 Uca iwyen t, nedhen t ɣar řebni n taddart n ccreɛ umi qqaren Ariyupagus, nnan as: “Ma iɛeddeř ad nessen man taɣuri n jdid i tᵉttbarrḥed?”,
\v 20 minzi cek tiwyed ca n tmesřayin tiɣribin i imezzuɣen nneɣ, u neccin nexs ad nessen min ixs ad yini man aya.”
\v 21 Marra inni zi Atina d marra ibarraniyyen inni din iqqimen, sseɛdun řweqt mɣir ḥima ad xebbaren u ḥima ad sřen ict n řḥajjet n jdid.
\m 
\v 22 Ikkar-dd Bulus, ibedd di \add taddart n ccreɛ qqaren as\add* ‘Ariyupagus’, inna: “\add A\add* iryazen n Atina, ufiɣ belli kenniw tᵉttɛemmarem sennej i ṭṭarf s tiggʷudi n ccwaṭen \add zi kuř aɣezdis\add*.
\v 23 Minzi umi nnḍeɣ \add di tendint nwem\add*, ẓriɣ timzidawin nwem, ufiɣ ɛawed ijj n uɛalṭar zemmen xas: ‘I AREBBI i war ittwassnen’. S uyenni wenni tɛebbdem kenniw, am war t tessinem, d Wa i zi d awem ttbeccareɣ.
\v 24 Minzi AREBBI wenni dd-yejjin ddunect d marra min dayes, wenni iǧan d Sidi n ujenna d temmurt, war izeddeɣ ca di tzawiyyin i ittwaggen s ifassen \add n iwdan\add*, \x ◘ \xo 17:24 \xt Amz. 1:1; 2 Im. 6:30; Izhd. 33:6; 124:8; 146:6; Ica. 66:1; Řex. 7:48; 14:15; Asa. 14:7. \x*
\v 25 uřa war xas ittwasexxar s ifassen n iwdan axmi Netta iḥwaj ca, minzi Netta simant nnes iwca i mkuř bnadem tudart d twarrit n nnefs. \x ◘ \xo 17:25 \xt Amz. 2:7. \x*
\v 26 Zeg idammen n yijjen igga marra řegnus n bnadem ḥima ad zedɣen x wudem n temmurt marra, u s řumur nnes ifarz asen řmijařat n řweqt uca igga iymiren n tzeddiɣt n iwdan, \x ◘ \xo 17:26 \xt Aɛwd. 32:8: Kul. 1:15, 16\x*
\v 27 ḥima ad arzun x AREBBI u ad \add zzayes\add* ttaren, ad taɣ ad t afen s marra min zzayes ittwaggen, maɣar Netta war iggʷij ca aṭṭas x kuř ijjen zzayneɣ.
\v 28 Minzi neccin dayes i neddar u \add dayes i\add* nᵉttenhezza u \add dayes i\add* neǧa, am mammec nnan ca n imiɣisen nwem: ‘Aqa neqqarṣ zzayes Netta!’
\v 29 S uyenni, am dd-iqqarṣ bnadem zi AREBBI, ittxeṣṣa war nḥesseb ca belli ureɣ niɣ nnuqart niɣ aẓru i ittwaggen s lfenn u s tzemmar n bnadem, aqa aten am AREBBI i ǧan. \x ◘ \xo 17:29 \xt Ica. 40:18. \x*
\v 30 AREBBI ijja ad ɛdunt zzmanat n uweddar, \add maca řexxu,\add* di zzman-a ittamar i marra iwdan, aqa ittxeṣṣa i kuř bnadem di kuř amcan ad dd-idweř ɣar AREBBI! \x ◘ \xo 17:30 \xt Lk. 24:47. \x*
\v 31 Minzi Netta igga ijj n wass i di i ɣa iḥkem x marra tammurt s řḥeqq s ijj n Bnadem i ifarz. Netta igga kuř ijjen ittxeṣṣa as maḥend ad zzayes yamen, řami t-i-dd-issnekkar zi taddart n imettinen.”
\m 
\v 32 Umi sřin x tnukra zi taddart n imettinen, bdan sthezzan s man aya, maca inneɣni nnan: “Ict n twařa nneɣni nexs ad zzayek nseř ktar x man aya.”
\v 33 Ammu iffeɣ Bulus zi řwesṭ nsen.
\v 34 Ca zzaysen ḍfaren t, umnen. Tuɣa Diyunisiyus d ijjen zzaysen, aqa-t jar řquḍat n Ariyupagus, uřa d ict n temɣart qqaren as Damaris u inneɣni akidsen. *
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Bulus di Kurintus
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya ijja Bulus tandint n Atina, yusa-dd ɣar Kurintus.
\v 2 Yufa \add din\add* ijj n weryaz d Uday qqaren as Akwila. Wanita yiweḍ-dd \add din\add* zi Punṭus, yusa-dd zi Iṭalya di řweqt nni, ak-d Priskilla, tamɣart nnes, minzi \add qayṣar\add* Kludiyus tuɣa yumur maḥend marra Udayen ad ffɣen zi Ruma. Uca yusa-dd \add Bulus\add* ɣarsen. \x ◘ \xo 18:2 \xt Rum. 16:3; 1 Kur. 16:19; 2 Tim. 4:19. \x*
\v 3 Umi tuɣa ɣares ṣṣenɛet d icten akidsen, iqqim ɣarsen, ixeddem akidsen, minzi nitni tuɣa aten di ṣṣenɛet nsen d imɛicwen, tteggen iqiḍan. \x ◘ \xo 18:3 \xt Řex. 20:34; 1 Kur. 4:12; 2 Kur. 11:9; 12:13; 1 Ts. 2:9; 2 Ts. 3:8. \x*
\v 4 Tuɣa ittḥeddat kuř ssebt di temzida, yarezzu ad isseqneɛ Udayen d ikafriwen, \add maḥend ad amnen\add*.
\m 
\v 5 Umi dd-ihwa Sila d Timutiyu zi Makiduniya, ssbedden nitni Bulus zeg ubarreḥ n Wawař, minzi Udayen tuɣa ttḍaddan t, ttceqqfen \add dayes\add* umi iched aqa Yasuɛ Netta d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 18:5 \xt Řex. 17:15. \x*
\v 6 Izzerz \add taɛejjact\add* zeg warruḍ nnes, inna asen: “Zi řexxu ttbariɣ ixef inu zzaywem, \add uca\add* ad raḥeɣ ɣar řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 18:6 \xt Mt. 10:14; Řex. 13:51. \x*
\v 7 Iruḥ ssenni uca yusa-dd ɣar taddart n ijj n weryaz qqaren as Titus wenni tuɣa iɛebbden AREBBI. Tuɣa taddart nnes teřṣeq ak-d temzida.
\v 8 U Krispus, ameqqran x temzida, yumen di Siditneɣ ak-d marra aytbab n taddart nnes, uřa d aṭṭas n Ikurintiyyen umi d as sřin, umnen di AREBBI, ttwassɣeḍṣen. \x ◘ \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Kur. 1:14. \x*
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Bulus deg ijj n řewḥiy: “War tteggʷed, siweř, war ttseqqara, \x ◘ \xo 18:9 \xt Řex. 23:11. \x*
\v 10 minzi Necc akidek uca uřa d ijj war izemmar ad cek iḍarr, minzi ɣari aṭṭas n iwdan di tendint-a!”
\v 11 Uca iqqim ijj n useggʷas d setta n iyuren di Kurintus, isseřmad asen awař n AREBBI.
\b
\s1 Bulus zzat i Ɣaliyun
\m 
\v 12 Maca umi tuɣa Ɣaliyun lɛamil x Axaya, kkaren Wudayen am yijj n weryaz x Bulus uca iwyen t-i-dd ɣar řkursi n ccreɛ,
\v 13 nnan: “Wa isseqnaɛ iwdan maḥend ad ɛebden AREBBI s řɛeks n Ccariɛa.”
\v 14 Umi ittar Bulus ttesriḥ maḥend ad yarzem aqemmum nnes, inna Ɣaliyun i Wudayen: “Mařa tusim-dd da ak-d icetciyen zi ssibbet n ijj n ufturi niɣ n ijj n řɣecc niɣ n ijj n nnɛi n taɛeffant, \add a\add* Udayen, xenni iři ad iřiq ad kenniw qebřeɣ s řḥeqq.
\v 15 Maca mařa din ixarwiḍen di ssibbet n ijj n wawař, niɣ \add di ssibbet n\add* n ca n ismawen, niɣ \add di ssibbet n\add* Ccariɛa nwem, ḥḍam t kenniw s yixef nwem, minzi necc war xseɣ ad iřiɣ d řqaḍi x tmesřayin-a!”
\v 16 Uca yuẓẓeř xasen zi řkursi n ccreɛ.
\v 17 Řexdenni ṭṭfen marra lkuffar Sustinis, amɣar n temzida, wtin t qibač i řkursi n ccreɛ, \add maca\add* Ɣaliyun war d as icqi man aya qaɛ.
\b
\s1 Bulus iɛqeb-dd ɣar Antiyuxiya
\m 
\v 18 \add Awarni řami\add* iqqim Bulus din ɛad aṭṭas n wussan, iweddeɛ tawmat uca ibeḥḥar ɣar Suriya u Priskilla d Akwila ruḥen akides. Netta tuɣa iḥeff azeǧif nnes di Kinxriyus, minzi tuɣa ijjaǧ ict n tjaǧit. \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Řxř. 6:18; Řex. 21:23. \x*
\v 19 \add Umi\add* dd-iwḍen ɣar Afasus, yudef Bulus ɣar temzida, tuɣa ittḥeddat Udayen.
\v 20 Řami zzayes ttaren ad kisen iqqim ktar, war ijji ad t ssqenɛen.
\v 21 Netta inna: “Ittxeṣṣa nican ad ɛeyydeɣ Řɛid i dd ɣa yasen di Urcalim. Maca ad ɣarwem dd-ɛeqbeɣ ɛawed mařa ixs AREBBI!” Uca ijja Akwila d Priskilla di Afasus. \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt 1 Kur. 4:19; Ɛbr. 6:3; Yaɛ. 4:15. \x*
\v 22 Icuq řebḥar uca yiweḍ-dd ɣar Qayṣariya, igeɛɛed \add ɣar Řɛid di Urcalim\add*, iseǧem s řehna x tmesmunt, xenni isafar ɣar Antiyuxiya.
\b
\s1 Asafar wiss třata n Bulus: Afasus, Makiduniya d Lyunan
\m 
\v 23 Ařami din isseɛdu ijj n řmijař n ca n wussan, iffeɣ uca icuq di jjwayeh n Galaṭiya d Frixiya, issemḥeḍ marra imeḥḍaren.
\m 
\v 24 Ijj n weryaz, qqaren as Apullus, ijj n weryaz d Uday i dd-ittwaxeřqen di Iskandariyya, yusa-dd ɣar Afasus. Netta tuɣa d ijj n weryaz issen ad issiweř, ittḥaka deg idlisen iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt 1 Kur. 1:12. \x*
\v 25 Wa tuɣa ittwasseřmed deg webrid n SIDI, tuɣa-t s arruḥ imeḥḍen. Issawař u isseřmad zi jjihet n Yasuɛ s cḍaret, waxxa netta war issin mɣir aseɣḍeṣ n Yuḥanna.
\v 26 Ibda issawař s bṭayṭay di temzida. Řami d as sřin Akwila d Priskilla, iwyen t-i-dd ɣarsen uca ssfehmen as abrid n SIDI marra.
\v 27 Ařami tuɣa ixs ad isafar ɣar Axaya, cejjɛen t wawmaten, urin ɣar imeḥḍaren ad t qebřen \add mliḥ\add*. Umi dd-yiweḍ wa ɣar din, iɛawen s arḍa \add i d as iwcin\add* marra inni tuɣa yumnen. \x ◘ \xo 18:27 \xt 1 Kur. 3:6. \x*
\v 28 Minzi netta tuɣa ittqacaḥ s jjehd ḍidd n Wudayen zzat i ubarru \add n iwdan\add*, issbeyyen asen zi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* belli Yasuɛ Netta d Lmasiḥ.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Bulus di Afasus
\m 
\v 1 Řami tuɣa Apullus di Kurintus, icuq Bulus di jjwayeh yuɛřan, yiweḍ-dd ɣar Afasus, uca ibda ittseqsa imeḥḍaren i din yufa. \x ◘ \xo 19:1 \xt 1 Kur. 1:12\x*
\v 2 \add Isseqsa ten:\add* “Ma tqebřem Arruḥ Iqeddsen řami tumnem?” Nitni arrin-dd xas, nnan: “War nesři qaɛ belli din Arruḥ Iqeddsen.”
\v 3 Inna asen: “Xenni min zi tᵉttwassɣeḍṣem?” Nnan as: “S useɣḍeṣ n Yuḥanna!”
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna Bulus: “Tuɣa Yuḥanna isseɣḍaṣ řgens s useɣḍeṣ n ttubet. Iqqar asen ittxeṣṣa ad amnen s wenni i dd ɣa yasen awarni as, aqa Netta d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt Mt. 3:11; Mk. 1:4; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:26; Řex. 1:5; 11:16. \x*
\v 5 Awarni řami sřin timesřayin aya, ttwassɣeḍṣen deg Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\v 6 Umi xasen issars Bulus afus, ihwa-dd xasen Arruḥ Iqeddsen, uca bdan ssawařen \bd s ijj n yiřes nneɣni\bd* uca \add bdan\add* ttnabben. \x ◘ \xo 19:6 \xt Řex. 8:17; 11:15; 2 Tim. 1:6. \x*
\v 7 Tuɣa-ten qaɛ tenɛac n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 8 Yudef \add Bulus\add* ɣar temzida, issawař akidsen teřt n iyuren s teryast, ittḥeddat ɣarsen, yarezzu ad ten isseqnaɛ di min itthemman Tageldit n AREBBI.
\v 9 Maca řami dewřen ca zzaysen qesḥen, ttemcubbucen, ceqqfen deg Webrid n AREBBI zzat i yinni \add din\add* imunen zi řegnus, xenni iggʷej Bulus xasen, uca issbeɛɛed xasen imeḥḍaren, ibda issawař akidsen kuř ass di temzida n ijj n weryaz qqaren as Tirannus. \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt 2 Tim. 1:15. \x*
\v 10 Ammu i yegga tnayen n iseggʷusa ařami marra inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Asiya sřin Awař n SIDI, am Udayen am Iramiyyen.
\b
\s1 Tarwa n Skiwa
\m 
\v 11 Tuɣa AREBBI ittegg řeɛjayeb imeqqranen s ifassen n Bulus, \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Mk. 16:20; Řex. 14:3. \x*
\v 12 ařami ksin řemḥamat \add n řeqṭen\add* d westawen n ibuyas i iǧan arruḍ x arrimet nnes, ssarsen ten x imehřac, uca \add xenni\add* ruḥen xasen řehřacat uca ccwaṭen ffɣen \add zzaysen\add*.
\m 
\v 13 Tuɣa din ɛawed ca n Wudayen inni tuɣa igguren di temmurt, tuɣa ssuffuɣen ccwaṭen. Nitni ttɛezzmen x yinni di iǧa řaryaḥ aɛeffan s Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ, qqaren: “Neccin nettɛezzem xak s Yisem n Yasuɛ i zi ittbarreḥ Bulus.”
\v 14 Inni t iggin, aqa aten sebɛa n tarwa n Skiwa, wenni d ijj n umeqqran n ikehhanen d Uday.
\v 15 \add Maca\add* cciṭan aɛeffan yarra-dd, inna asen: “Yeccu ssneɣ t uřa d Bulus ssneɣ t, maca min teɛnam kenniw?”
\v 16 Uca bnadem i di iǧa řaryaḥ d aɛeffan ingez xasen, iɣeřb i-ten, inḍar i-ten \add x temmurt\add*, ařami arewřen zi taddart d iɛaryanen d iyezmen.
\m 
\v 17 Řexbar-a iffeɣ-dd ɣar marra Wudayen d Iramiyyen inni izeddɣen di Afasus. Tewḍa-dd ict n tiggʷudi temɣar x marra nitni uca ittwassemɣar Isem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\v 18 Aṭṭas n yinni yumnen usin-dd, steɛtarefen x iɛeddiyyen nsen, neɛmen s min tuɣa tteggen. \x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Mt. 3:6. \x*
\v 19 Uřa d aṭṭas n iseḥḥaren yarwen idlisen nsen, sscemmḍen ten zzat i marra. Nitni ggin asen řeḥsab uca ufin belli ssekkwan xemsin-ařaf \add n řweznat n\add* nnuqart.
\v 20 Ammu tuɣa l’iman n AREBBI iggam, yarenni di jjehd. \x ◘ \xo 19:20 \xt Ica. 55:11 \x*
\b
\s1 Axarweḍ di Afasus
\m 
\v 21 Awarni řami kemmřent tmesřayin-a, igga Bulus maḥend ad icuq di Makiduniya d Axaya marra, ḥima ad isafar ɣar Urcalim, inna: “Xmi din i ɣa reḥḥgeɣ, ittxeṣṣa ayi ad ẓareɣ Ruma ɛawed.” \x ◘ \xo 19:21 \xt Rum. 15:25; Gal. 2:1. \x*
\v 22 Issekk tnayen n yinni tuɣa ixeddmen akides ɣar Makiduniya, ina d Timutiyu d Irastus, \add maca\add* netta \add simant\add* nnes tuɣa iqqim din \add ɛad\add* ca n řweqt di Asiya.
\m 
\v 23 Di řweqt nni ikkar din ijj n uxarweḍ d ameqqran x ssibbet n Webrid n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 19:23 \xt 2 Kur. 1:8. \x*
\v 24 Minzi tuɣa din ijj n usiyaɣ n nnuqart, qqaren as Dimitriyu, wenni tuɣa ittṣennaɛ tizawiyyin timeẓyanin n nnuqart n ‘Artimis’ \add di řeqwařeb\add*, uca ammu i yarbeḥ i ayt n ṣṣenɛet nnes ijj n arbeḥ d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 19:24 \xt Řex. 16:16. \x*
\v 25 Issmun-dd ayt n ṣṣenɛet nnes ak-d inni ixeddmen akidsen, inna asen: “A iryazen, kenniw tessnem belli marra arbeḥ nneɣ yusa-dd ak-d ṣṣenɛet-a.
\v 26 Kenniw tesřim u tessnem belli Bulus wanita isseqnaɛ aṭṭas n iwdan, war iǧi imezdaɣ n Afasus waha, maca uřa d ibarruten n marra Asiya, aqa issbeɛɛed i-ten \add x řexyařat-a\add*, iqqar: ‘\add Řexyařat-a\add* i ittwaggen s ifassen war ǧin ca d irebbiten!’ \x ◘ \xo 19:26 \xt Izhd. 115:4; Irm. 10:3. \x*
\v 27 War teǧi tsebbabt-a waha di lxaṭar uca teggur ad tedweř d ict n tmesřact ibeṭṭřen, maca uřa d zzawect n ‘Artimis’, tarebbit tameqqrant, ad tt ḥesben d walu uca ad sseḥqaren tarebbit-a i tɛebbed \add temmurt n\add* Asiya uřa d marra řegnus.”
\m 
\v 28 Umi sřin man aya, dewřen xeyqqen aṭṭas. Sɣuyyun, nnan: “Tameqqrant d \add tarebbit\add* ‘Artimis’ n Ifasusiyyen!”
\v 29 Tandint qaɛ txarweḍ am tekmeř uca uzzřen am yijj n bnadem ɣar tiyatir n lmesraḥ, uca Xayus d Aristarxus, iryazen zi Makiduniya, inni d imɛacaren n Bulus deg usafar nnes, ṭṭfen ten uca iwyen ten-dd akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 19:29 \xt Řex. 20:4; 27:2; Kul. 4:10. \x*
\v 30 Uřa d Bulus tuɣa ixs ad yadef ɣar tiyatir n lmesraḥ, maca imeḥḍaren \add nnes\add* ssbedden t.
\v 31 Izeǧifen \add imḍebbaren n jjwayeh\add* n Asiya, umi tuɣa aten d imeddukkař nnes, ssekken ɛawed \add ireqqasen\add*, maḥend ad zayes ttaren ḥima war ittsebbeř ixef nnes ad yadef ɣar tiyatir.
\m 
\v 32 Řɣaci i ittwassmunen di tiyatir, tuɣa ssekkaren t aṭṭas. Nitni sɣuyyun ijj i wenneɣni, maɣar azyen ameqqran zzayes war issin mixef tuɣa munen.
\v 33 Řgens n Wudayen i din iǧan, nedhen ijj n weryaz zzaysen ɣar zzat, ijj n Wuday qqaren as Aliksandir. Netta ikkar, iceyyar s ufus nnes u tuɣa ixs ad issiweř x udafeɛ \add n Bulus\add* zzat i řgens.
\v 34 Maca umi fehmen belli aqa-t d Uday, sɣuyen marra s tmijja d icten ɛřaḥař tnayen n tsaɛɛetin: “Tameqqrant d ‘Artimis’ n Ifasusiyyen!”
\m 
\v 35 Azeǧif n tendint isshedden řɣaci, inna: “\add A\add* iryazen n Afasus, man wen war issinen belli tandint n Ifasusiyyen d takehhant tḥeṭṭa nican x zzawect n ‘Artimis’ u x řexyař i dd-iwḍan zeg ujenna!
\v 36 S uyenni, umi war izemmar uřa d ijjen ad iɛekkes timesřayin-a, icuwwar awem ad tarsem, war tteggem ca s uqeǧeq,
\v 37 minzi tiwyem-dd iryazen-a \add danita\add*, inni war iǧin d iceffaren n tzawiyyin uřa war ttceqqafen di trebbit nneɣ.
\v 38 Maca mařa tuɣa ɣar Dimitriyu u ɣar yinni iǧan akides di ṣṣenɛet ca n ucetci x yijjen, aqa din ijj n lɛamil di tendint. Ejj i-ten ad \add ɣares\add* dd-qarrben u ad carrɛen ak-d wayawya \add zzates\add*.
\v 39 Maca mařa texsem ca n tmesřact nneɣni, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwafekk man aya deg ijj n wemcan i ittweṣṣan i tmesmunt ɛlaḥsab ccariɛa,
\v 40 minzi aqa aneɣ di lxaṭar ad xaneɣ ḍeřmen ass-a zi ssibbet n uɣuwweɣ, minzi war din bu řesbab i zi nzemmar ad dd-narr s yijj n wawař di tmesřact n wegraw-a, minzi nessmuna di řbaṭeř u nettɣewweɣ amenni waha.”
\v 41 Awarni řami inna aya, ismeḥ i wegraw ad yuyur.
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Bulus di Masiduniya d Lyunan
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami yarsa uɣuwweɣ, iřaɣa-dd Bulus x imeḥḍaren, iweddeɛ i-ten s usudem \add n wawmaten\add*, uca iffeɣ ḥima ad iraḥ ɣar Makiduniya.
\v 2 Řami icuq di jjwayeh nni, icejjeɛ i-ten s waṭṭas n wawařen, xenni yiweḍ ɣar Hillas, \add ixs ad yini ɣar jjihet Axaya\add*.
\v 3 Ařami isseɛdu din třata n iyuren, ssewjden as Wudayen ijj n řfex, umi tuɣa iggur ad ibeḥḥar ɣar Suriya. S uya igga ad yeɛqeb x webrid n Makiduniya.
\v 4 Supatrus zi tendint n Biriya, Aristarxus d Sikundus zi Tissalunika, Xayus zi Dirbi, Timutiyu zi Listra u Ticikus d Trufimus zi Asiya uyuren akides ař Asiya. \x ◘ \xo 20:4 \xt Řex. 19:29; 21:29; 27:2; 1 Kur. 1:14; Afa. 6:21; Kul. 4:7, 10; 2 Tim. 4:12; Tit. 3:12. \x*
\v 5 Ina izwaren aneɣ, ttrajan aneɣ di Truwas.
\v 6 Maca neccin neffeɣ zi Filippi, tandint \add tamezwarut\add* n Makiduniya, awarni řami kemmřen wussan n \add Weɣrum\add* břa Antun, nekka x řebḥar u di xemsa n wussan niweḍ-dd ɣar Truwas mani neqqim sebɛa n wussan.
\b
\s1 Asnekkar n Utixus zi řmewt di Truwas
\m 
\v 7 Deg wass amezwaru n ssimana umi munen imeḥḍaren maḥend ad arẓen aɣrum \add n tnemmirt\add*, issiweř Bulus akidsen. Isszugar Bulus di řhard nnes ař řwesṭ n ǧiřet, maɣar netta tuɣa inwa ad isafar tiwecca nnes.
\v 8 Aqa areqqen din aṭṭas n řefnarat di tɣurfet n sennej i di tuɣa nmun.
\v 9 Tuɣa din ijj n ubřiɣ qqaren as Utixus, iqqim di řkazi, ittesřa, řexdenni ikka xas yiḍeṣ yuǧeɣ am tuɣa Bulus isszugar di řhard nnes. Umi tuɣa iṭṭeṣ, iwḍa-dd zi ṭṭebqet wiss třata ɣar wadday, ksin t immut.
\v 10 Maca Bulus ihwa, iwḍa xas, idarreɛ as, inna: “War tennexřiɛem ca, aqa dayes tudart.” \x ◘ \xo 20:10 \xt 1 Ij. 17:21; 2 Ij. 4:34. \x*
\v 11 Xenni yuři ɛawed, yarẓa aɣrum, icca \add cwayt zzayes\add*, xenni issiweř akidsen \add ɛad\add* aṭṭas ařami d řefjar. Xas uca iruḥ isafar x temmurt,
\v 12 am dd-iwyen nitni aḥenjir iddar, farḥen as aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 13 Maca neccin nenya deg uɣarrabu, nbeḥḥar ɣar řmarsa n Tissus maḥend ad kidneɣ dd-nawi Bulus ssenni, am mammec tuɣa ittḍebbar, maɣar netta s yixef nnes ikka \add ɣar din\add* x temmurt.
\v 14 Ařami zzayes nareḥḥeb di Tissus, neksi t di tɣarrabut uca niweḍ-ḍḍ ɣar Mitilini.
\v 15 Ssenni neɛdu tiwecca nnes ɣar tegzirt n Xiyus u farwecca nnes niwed ɣar Samus, neqqim di Truxiliyun. Deg wass awarni as niweḍ ɣar Militus,
\v 16 minzi Bulus igga ad iɛdu Afasus x řebḥar ḥima war ittɛeṭṭař dinni, minzi tuɣa ittqeǧeq ḥima, meɛlik iɛeddeř, ad iɛeyyed Řɛid n Xemsin n Wussan di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 20:16 \xt Řex. 21:4, 12. \x*
\b
\s1 Ameřqi aneggaru n Bulus ak-d imɣaren n tmesmunt n Afasus
\m 
\v 17 Zi Militus ijja ad dd-asen imɣaren n tmesmunt di Afasus.
\v 18 Řami dd-usin ɣares, inna asen:
\m “Kenniw tessnem zeg wass amezwaru umi dd-udfeɣ ɣar Asiya, mammec ǧiɣ akidwem marra ussan,
\v 19 am tuɣa ttsexxareɣ i AREBBI s marra awaḍeɛ u s imeṭṭawen, uřa deg iɣekkwan i xafi ikkin zi ssibbet n tmeɛmač n Wudayen.
\v 20 War jjiɣ ca zi min inefɛen i řeɛmur nwem war d awem t barrḥeɣ, war t ssřemdeɣ di řeswaq u di tudrin,
\v 21 am ssqenɛeɣ Udayen d Iramiyyen maḥend ad dd-dewřen ɣar AREBBI, ad amnen di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \f ◼ \fr 20:21 \fk Iramiyyen\ft - di řmaxtuṭṭat s yiřes n L’Yunan ittwari ‘Iyunaniyyen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:21 \xt Mt. 3:2; Mk. 1:15; Lk. 24:47. \x*
\v 22 U řexxu ad raḥeɣ ɣar Urcalim am ttwacarfeɣ zi Arruḥ, war ssineɣ min d ayi ittrajan din,
\v 23 mɣir aqa Arruḥ Iqeddsen iched ayi di kuř tandint, iqqar: ‘Aqa iceddiyyen d řemḥayem ttrajan cek!’
\v 24 Maca necc war ḥessbeɣ tudart inu ca tiɣřa i yixef inu, maḥend ad kemmřeɣ ticři inu d řxedmet n tsexxart i ksiɣ zi Siditneɣ Yasuɛ ḥima ad cehdeɣ x Řexbar Aṣebḥan n arḍa n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 20:24 \xt Řex. 21:13; Gal. 1:1; Tit. 1:3. \x*
\v 25 U řexxu ssneɣ, aqa uřa d ijj zzaywem ad iẓar aɣembub inu ɛad, marra kenniw inni jar awem ggureɣ, ttbarrḥeɣ s Tgeldit n AREBBI.
\m 
\v 26 S uyenni ad xawem cehdeɣ ass-a, belli necc ttbarriɣ ixef inu zeg idammen nwem marra.
\v 27 Minzi war ɛgizeɣ ad awem ssecneɣ marra min ittexs AREBBI.
\v 28 S uyenni ḥḍam x yixef nwem u x tḥimart tmun min xef igga Arruḥ Iqeddsen kenniw d imeḥḍayen, ḥima ad tarwesem tamesmunt n Lmasiḥ tenni d ikesseb s Idammen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 20:28 \xt Afa. 1:7; Kul. 1:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:19; 5:2; Asa. 5:9. \x*
\m 
\v 29 Minzi ssneɣ belli awarni twaḥit inu ad ɣarwem dd-adfen wuccanen imuzzaren \add inni\add* war ittejjin taḥimart. \x ◘ \xo 20:29 \xt 2 Bṭ. 2:1. \x*
\v 30 Ɛad ad zzaywem dd-kkaren yeryazen inni i ɣa issiwřen řhard iɛewwjen ḥima ad ssuffɣen imeḥḍaren zeg webrid, ad ten jarren awarni asen. \x ◘ \xo 20:30 \xt Izhd. 41:10; Mt. 16:21; Řex. 1:17; 1 Yḥ. 2:19. \x*
\v 31 S uyenni faqem, tɛeqřem belli třata n iseggʷusa, ǧiřet d wass, war beddeɣ ad ssmeḥdeɣ kuř ijjen zzaywem s imeṭṭawen.
\m 
\v 32 U řexxu ad kenniw sellmeɣ i AREBBI u i wawař n arḍa nnes, i Wenni ɣar iǧa tizemmar ḥima ad kenniw ibna u ad awem iwc řwart ak-d marra imqeddasen.
\v 33 War ḍmiɛeɣ di nnuqart niɣ deg wureɣ niɣ deg warruḍ uřa zeg ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 20:33 \xt 1 Kur. 9:12; 2 Kur. 11:9; 12:13. \x*
\v 34 Kenniw tessnem simant nwem belli ifassen inu aqa xedmen i min ḥwajeɣ u i min ḥwajen inni iǧan akidi. \x ◘ \xo 20:34 \xt Řex. 18:3; 1 Kur. 4:12; 1 Ts. 2:9; 2 Ts. 3:8. \x*
\v 35 Di kuřci ssecneɣ awem belli ittxeṣṣa, am nxeddem ammu, ad newc afus i yinni iḍeɛfen uca ad nfekkar deg wawařen n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ, belli inna: ‘Sseɛd n wenni iwcin x wenni iksin.’”
\b
\m 
\v 36 Awarni řami inna aya, iwḍa x ifadden nnes, iẓẓuǧ u marra iryazen akides. \x ◘ \xo 20:36 \xt Řex. 21:5. \x*
\v 37 Aqa din jar asen aṭṭas n imeṭṭawen uca darrɛen as, ssudmen t.
\v 38 Ceḍnen aṭṭas, amezwar n marra x wawař i inna, belli war ẓarren ca aɣembub nnes ɛad, uca ssqebbḍen t ɣar uɣarrabu. *
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Asafar n Bulus ɣar Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami xasen nemmsebḍa, nebda nẓekkwa řebḥar, nruḥ nican uca niweḍ ɣar tegzirt n Kus. Tiwecca nnes niweḍ ɣar Rudus u ssenni ɣar Patara.
\v 2 Nufa din ijj n uɣarrabu i tuɣa ad iẓwa ɣar Finiqiya, nenya dayes uca nruḥ.
\v 3 Řami dd-niweḍ ɣar tegzirt n Qubrus, nejja i-tt x uzeřmaḍ uca nruḥ x řebḥar ɣar Suriya uca ssenni niweḍ ɣar Ṣur, minzi aɣarrabu tuɣa igga ad ifarreɣ sseřɛet nnes din.
\v 4 Umi nufa din imeḥḍaren, neqqim ɣarsen sebɛa n wussan. Kuř ass nnan nitni s Arruḥ i Bulus maḥend war ittgeɛɛid ca ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 21:4 \xt Řex. 20:23; 21:12. \x*
\v 5 Awarni i wussan-a neffeɣ, nuyur. Marra nitni ssqebḍen aneɣ, nitni d temɣarin nsen d iḥenjiren nsen, ař barra n tendint. X tma n řebḥar wḍan x ifadden nsen uca ẓẓuǧen.
\v 6 Umi nweddeɛ ayawya s usudem, nenya deg uɣarrabu, maca nitni ɛeqben, kuř ijjen ɣar taddart nnes.
\m 
\v 7 Umi nkemmeř x usafar zi Ṣur niweḍ ɣar Ptulumayu, nseǧmen x wawmaten uca neqqim akidsen ijj n wass. \f ◼ \fr 21:7 \fk Ptulumayu\ft - niɣ ‘Akku’.\f*
\v 8 Tiwecca nnes neffeɣ ssenni, niweḍ ɣar Qayṣariya. Nudef ɣar taddart n umbeccar Filippus, wenni tuɣa d ijjen zi sebɛa \add n imsexxaren\add*, uca neqqim \add ɣares\add*. \f ◼ \fr 21:8 \fk ijjen zi sebɛa \bdit n imsexxaren\bdit*\ft - xzar Řex. 6:5.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 21:8 \xt Řex. 6:5; 8:29. \x*
\v 9 Tuɣa ɣar wa arebɛa n tḥenjirin, \add ɛad\add* d tiɛezriyyin, tinni ittnabben. \x ◘ \xo 21:9 \xt Yuw. 3:1; Řex. 2:17. \x*
\m 
\v 10 Umi nenniwjew din aṭṭas n wussan, ihwa-dd ijj n unabi zi Yahudiyya, qqaren as Aɣabus. \x ◘ \xo 21:10 \xt Řex. 11:28. \x*
\v 11 Yusa-dd ɣarneɣ uca iksi abyas n Bulus, icarf ixef nnes ifassen d iḍaren, inna: “Ammu i iqqar Arruḥ Iqeddsen: ‘Aryaz i ɣar iǧa abyas-a, ammu i t ɣa carfen Wudayen di Urcalim uca ad t sellmen deg ifassen n řegnus.’” \x ◘ \xo 21:11 \xt Řex. 20:23; 21:33. \x*
\v 12 Umi nesřa awařen-a, nettar zzayes, am neccin am yinni zi jjwayeh nni, ḥima war ittgeɛɛid ɣar Urcalim.
\v 13 Maca Bulus yarra-dd, inna: “Min kenniw yuɣin, tᵉttrum uca tessareḍbem uř inu? Minzi aqa ayi wejdeɣ, war iǧi ḥima ad ayi carfen waha, maca ɛawed ḥima ad mmteɣ di Urcalim x ssibbet n Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.”
\v 14 Umi war d aneɣ ijji ad t nesseqneɛ, nesqar, neqqar: “Ad yiři min ixs Siditneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 21:14 \xt Mt. 6:10; Lk. 11:2; 22:42. \x*
\m 
\v 15 Awarni ussan nni nessewjed uca ngeɛɛed ɣar Urcalim.
\v 16 Ruḥen akidneɣ ca n iryazen, imeḥḍaren zi Qayṣariya, iwyen-dd ijj n tewmat, qqaren as Mnasun zi Qubrus, aqa-t d ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren imezwura, ḥima ad ɣares nenniwjew.
\b
\s1 Amuni n Bulus ak-d rrusul d wawmaten di Urcalim
\m 
\v 17 Ařami dd-niweḍ ɣar Urcalim, tareḥḥeb zzayneɣ tawmat s řefraḥet.
\v 18 Tiwecca nnes yudef Bulus akidneɣ ɣar Yaɛqub, umi ḥḍaren din akides marra imɣaren.
\v 19 Awarni řami xasen nseǧem, ibda Bulus ad iɛawed s usettef x marra min igga AREBBI jar řegnus s tsexxart nnes.
\v 20 Umi sřin aya, ssemɣaren AREBBI, nnan as: “\add A\add* umatneɣ, tᵉttwařid mecḥař n ɛecra n řuřuf di Yahudiyya i yumnen, u nitni marra ttasmen x Ccariɛa.
\v 21 Maca yiweḍ asen-dd řexbar xak belli tesseřmaded i marra Udayen inni iǧan jar řegnus maḥend ad semḥen di \add Ccariɛa n\add* Musa am d asen teqqared ittxeṣṣa war xettnen iḥenjiren nsen war gguren deg webrid n Ccariɛa.
\v 22 S uyenni, minzi sřin belli aqa tusid-dd da,
\v 23 egg min d ac ɣa nini! Ɣarneɣ arebɛa n yeryazen inni ɣar iǧa ijj n lwaɛd mahend ad ssizdigen ixef nsen.
\v 24 Awi ina akidek, tessizdeged ixef nnec akidsen, uca xeǧeṣ xasen ḥima ad ḥeffen izeǧifen nsen. Xenni ad ssnen marra belli min xak ittwannan war iǧi bu nican, u belli cek tᵉttkemmřed Ccariɛa u tᵉttᵉṭṭfed dayes.
\v 25 Maca zi jjihet n yinni yumnen jar řegnus, aqa nura belli ad beɛɛden x min iɣarṣen \add i l’aṣnam\add*, x farq-ccɣeř, x jjiyfat, uřa x idammen.” \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt Amz. 9:4; Uf. 20:3; Řex. 15:23; 1 Kur. 8:1. \x*
\m 
\v 26 Xenni yiwyi Bulus iryazen nni akides uca tiwecca nnes issizdeg ixef nnes akidsen. Ruḥen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant, isscen asen mammec ittxeṣṣa ad kemmřen wussan n usizdeg, ař d iqeddem zi mkuř ijjen zzaysen taɣarṣt \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:26 \xt Řex. 24:6. \x*
\b
\s1 Uḍuf n Bulus di Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 27 Ařami dd-yiweḍ wass sebɛa, ẓrin t Wudayen n Asiya di Zzawect Tameqqrant, ssenhezzen řgens marra ḍidd nnes, ḥarten xas s ifassen,
\v 28 sɣuyyun: “A kenniw, \add a\add* ayt n Israil, ɣawřem ɣar twiza! Wa d bnadem nni isseřmaden iwdan marra ḍidd i řgens nneɣ u ḍidd i Ccariɛa u ḍidd i wemcan-a. Ɛawed issidef-dd Iramiyyen ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant uca issexmej amcan iqeddsen wanita!”
\v 29 Minzi tuɣa izwaren akides ẓrin Trufimus zi Afasus di tendint, ittɣiř asen belli netta yudef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant ak-d Bulus. \x ◘ \xo 21:29 \xt Řex. 20:4; 2 Tim. 4:20. \x*
\v 30 Tandint marra thaj uca iwdan dduqqzen-dd, ḥarten x Bulus, jarren t barra i Zzawect Tameqqrant, řexdenni bellɛent tiwwura.
\m 
\v 31 Am yarezzu řɣaci ad t ineɣ, yiweḍ řexbar ɣar ukumandar n řkumpaniyyet, aqa Urcalim amen tekmeř txarweḍ.
\v 32 Řexdenni yiwyi-dd ijj n řqebṭan x mya uřa d ijj ubarru n iɛeskariyyen, uca uzzřen ɣarsen. Ařami ẓrin nitni akumandar d řɛeskar, ssbedden ad wten Bulus.
\v 33 Ařami ɣares dd-iqarreb ukumandar, iṭṭef i-t, yumur ad t carfen s tnayen n ssnaseř, xenni isseqsa min iɛna netta d min igga. \x ◘ \xo 21:33 \xt Řex. 21:11. \x*
\v 34 Jar řɣaci aqa din ijjen ittřaɣa ammu u wenneɣni ammu. Řami war izemmar ad issen tidett zi ssibbet n lharaj, yumur ad t awyen ɣar lqecla.
\v 35 Ařami dd-yiweḍ Bulus ɣar ddruj, imsar belli iɛeskariyyen arbun t x ssbab n lɛunf n řgens,
\v 36 minzi aṭṭas n iwdan tuɣa ḍeffaren t, sɣuyyun, nnan: “Kksem t zeg webrid!” \x ◘ \xo 21:36 \xt Lk. 23:18; Yḥ. 19:15; Řex. 22:22. \x*
\m 
\v 37 Ařami dd-iqarreb ɣar lqecla, ḥima ad yadef ɣar daxeř, inna Bulus i ukumandar: “Ma iḥiqq ayi ad ac iniɣ ca?” Inna as: “Ma tessned Tayunanit?
\v 38 Ma war teǧid cek d Amiṣri wenni iggin aɣuwweɣ qbeř ussan-a, indeh akides arebɛa ařaf n yeryazen d iqettařen ɣar řexřa?”
\v 39 Inna as Bulus: “Necc d aryaz d Uday zi Tarsus, ict n tendint ittwassnen di Kilikiya mani dd-xeřqeɣ. Necc ttareɣ zzayek ttesriḥ ḥima ad ssiwřeɣ ɣar řgens.” \x ◘ \xo 21:39 \xt Řex. 9:11,30. \x*
\v 40 Umi d as ismeḥ, ibedd Bulus x ddruj, iceyyar s ufus ɣarsen, uca umi arsin qaɛ, issiweř akidsen s iřes n Tɛibranit, inna asen ...
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Adafeɛ n Bulus x yixef nnes zzat i řgens
\m 
\v 1 ... “\add A\add* tawmat d ibabaten, sřem i min d awem ɣa iniɣ x udafeɛ inu.”
\v 2 Umi sřin, aqa issawař akidsen s \add yiřes n\add* Tɛibranit, qqimen sqaren ɛad ktar. Inna asen:
\v 3 “Necc d ijj n bnadem d Uday, xeřqeɣ-dd di Tarsus di Kilikiya, maca arebbiɣ di tendint-a ɣar iḍaren n Gamaliyal u ttwassřemdeɣ ɛlaḥsab tidett nican n Ccariɛa n řejdud nneɣ. Ceṭṭareɣ x min iǧan n AREBBI am mammec uřa d kenniw marra. \x ◘ \xo 22:3 \xt Řex. 5:34; 9:11; 21:39; 2 Kur. 11:22\x*
\v 4 Necc tuɣa ḍeffareɣ Abrid-a s řmewt am carrfeɣ iryazen d temɣarin, ttsellameɣ ten ɣar řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Řex. 8:3; 9:1; 26:9; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 5 Arrays n ikehhanen d marra imɣaren \add n řgens\add* zemmaren ad cehden belli ksiɣ tibratin i tawmat, maḥend ad ruḥeɣ ɣar Dimacq ḥima ad awyeɣ inni din iǧan ɛawed s tcarfin ɣar Urcalim, ḥima ad ṭṭfen lɛiqab.
\m 
\v 6 Umi d ayi tuɣa deg webrid uca iwḍeɣ ɣar Dimacq ɣar wezyen n wass, tařɣa xafi s řɣefřet ict n tfawt temɣar zeg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 22:6 \xt 1 Kur. 15:8; 2 Kur. 12:2. \x*
\v 7 Wḍiɣ x temmurt, sřiɣ ict n tmijja, teqqar ayi: ‘Cawul, Cawul, mayemmi d ayi tdarrced?’
\v 8 Arriɣ-dd xas: ‘Min teɛnid Cek, a Sidi?’ Inna ayi: ‘Necc d Yasuɛ, Nnaṣiri, wenni tᵉttdarraced!’
\v 9 Iryazen nni tuɣa iǧan akidi, ẓrin tafawt, maca war sřin ca i tmijja n Wenni akidi issawařen. \x ◘ \xo 22:9 \xt Dan. 10:7. \x*
\v 10 Nniɣ: ‘Min ɣa ggeɣ, a Sidi?’ Inna ayi Siditneɣ: ‘Kkar, traḥed ɣar Dimacq, din ad ac ittwanna x marra min d ac yuran ad tegged!’
\v 11 Umi dewřeɣ war ttwiřiɣ zi tissiqt n tfawt nni, gewwden ayi inni i tuɣa akidi iǧan zeg ufus, uca \add ammu\add* i dd-iwḍeɣ ɣar Dimacq.
\m 
\v 12 Tuɣa din ijj weryaz, qqaren as Ananiyas. Netta d amsegged ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa, am mammec tuɣa xas cehhden marra Udayen. \x ◘ \xo 22:12 \xt Řex. 9:17. \x*
\v 13 Netta yusa-dd ɣari, inna ayi: ‘\add A\add* uma Cawul, arzem tiṭṭawin nnec!’ Řexdenni di tsaɛɛet nni ttwarzment tiṭṭawin inu, uca ẓriɣ t.
\v 14 Netta inna ayi: ‘Aqa AREBBI n řejdud nneɣ ixḍar i cek, ḥima ad tessned min ixs Netta, u ḥima ad tẓared Amseggad, ad tesřed tmijja nnes zeg uqemmum nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:14 \xt Řex. 7:52; Rum. 3:26; 1 Bṭ. 3:18; 1 Yḥ. 2:1\x*
\v 15 Cek ad as tiřid d acehhad ɣar marra iwdan s marra min teẓrid u s min tesřid.
\v 16 Iwa řexxu, mayemmi war tezɛimed ɛad? Kkar, ejj ad cek ssɣeḍṣen, ad tᵉttwasizedged zi ddnub nnec am tᵉttřaɣid x Yisem nnes!’
\m 
\v 17 Awarni řami dd-ɛeqbeɣ, iwḍeɣ da ɣar Urcalim, uca am tuɣa ttẓaǧiɣ di Zzawect Tameqqrant,
\v 18 ẓriɣ t deg ijj n řewḥiy, inna ayi: ‘Azzeř, teffɣed deɣya zi Urcalim minzi war qebbřen ca cchadet nnec xafi!’ \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Mt. 10:14. \x*
\v 19 Nniɣ necc: ‘\add A\add* Sidi, aqa nitni ssnen belli tuɣa ttḥebbseɣ inni yumnen zzayek, hettkeɣ ten s urekkuḍ di temzidawin, \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Řex. 22:4. \x*
\v 20 u řami ttwasizzřen idammen n ucehhad nnec Stifanus, tuɣa beddeɣ akidsen, arḍiɣ x yinni t nɣin u ḥḍiɣ arruḍ n yinni t yarejmen.’ \x ◘ \xo 22:20 \xt Řex. 7:58; 8:1. \x*
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: ‘Ruḥ, minzi ad cek ssekkeɣ ɣar řaggʷaj ḥima ad tbarrḥed \add L’Injil\add* i řegnus!’” \x ◘ \xo 22:21 \xt Řex. 9:15; 13:2; Gal. 1:15; 2:8; Afa. 3:8; 1 Tim. 2:7; 2 Tim. 1:11. \x*
\m 
\v 22 Tuɣa ttesřan as ař awař-a, xenni kkaren ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen, qqaren: “Kksem t zi temmurt, minzi am wanita war isdiheǧ ad iddar.” \x ◘ \xo 22:22 \xt Řex. 21:36. \x*
\v 23 Am tuɣa sɣuyyun, neṭṭaren arruḍ nsen uca zuzzaran ucař ɣar ujenna.
\v 24 Yumur ukumandar maḥend ad t ssidfen ɣar lqecla, ad t sseqsan am t tthettaken s urekkuḍ ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* ifhem mayemmi xas sɣuyen \add ammu\add*.
\v 25 Umi t jebden s tḥezzamin \add i uhettek s urekkuḍ\add*, inna Bulus i řqebṭan x mya i din ibedden: “Ma iḥeǧeř awem ɛlaḥsab ccariɛa \add nwem\add* ad thettkem ijj n bnadem d Arumani s urekkuḍ am war xas teḥkimem \add ɛad\add*?”
\m 
\v 26 Umi isřa řqebṭan x mya man aya, iruḥ ɣar ukumandar, inna as: “Min ɣa tegged? Aqa aryaz-a d Arumani!”
\v 27 Iqarreb-dd ɣares ukumandar, inna as: “Ini ayi, ma cek d Arumani?” Yarra-dd xas Bulus: “Wah!”
\v 28 Yarra-dd xas ukumandar, inna: “Necc ṭṭfeɣ řḥeqq-a n umezdaɣ Arumani s ijj n řqedd d ameqqran n tmenyat!” Bulus inna: “Maca necc xeřqeɣ-dd zzayes!”
\v 29 Řexdenni, inni tuɣa nwan ad t hettken s urekkud, jjin t. Akumandar idweř iggʷed, minzi ifhem aqa-t d Arumani u minzi ijja i-t ad t carfen.
\v 30 Tiwecca nnes am tuɣa ixs ad issen tidett min xef t ḍeřmen Wudayen, igga ad fesyen iceddiyyen \add nnes\add* uca yumur ad ssmunen izeǧifen n ikehhanen d marra Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add* n imeqqranen nsen uca issehwa-dd Bulus \add ɣar din\add*, issbedd i-t di řwesṭ nsen.
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Bulus zzat i Jmaɛet Tameqqrant n Wudayen
\m 
\v 1 Bulus iqceɛ \add deg inni iqqimen\add* di Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*, inna: “A iryazen tawmat! Aqa necc uyureɣ s tnefsect teṣfa ɣar marra \add iɣezdisen\add* zzat i AREBBI ař ass-a!” \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt Řex. 24:16. \x*
\v 2 Ananiyas, akehhan, yumur inni i tuɣa din akides ibedden, ad t wten ɣar uqemmum. \x ◘ \xo 23:2 \xt 1 Ij. 22:24; Irm. 20:2; Yḥ. 18:22. \x*
\v 3 Xenni inna as Bulus: “Ad cek iwwet AREBBI, cek d řḥiḍ ijiyyaren! Aqa cek teqqimed da maḥend ad xafi tḥekmed ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa, \add maca\add* txařafed Ccariɛa s yixef nnec am tumured ad ayi wten!” \x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Aɛwd. 17:9. \x*
\v 4 Inni i tuɣa kis ibedden, nnan: “Ma tdeǧmed akehhan n AREBBI?”
\v 5 Inna Bulus: “\add A\add* tawmat, war ssineɣ aqa-t d akehhan, minzi tura: ‘Azeǧif n řgens nnec war t neɛɛeř!’” \x ◘ \xo 23:5 \xt Uf. 22:27. \x*
\m 
\v 6 Umi issen Bulus, aqa \add azyen\add* n řgens d Iṣaduqiyyen u \add azyen nneɣni\add* zeg Ifarisiyyen, iřaɣa di Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*: “A iryazen tawmat, necc d Afarisi, mmis n Ifarisiyyen, necc ttᵉttwaḥakameɣ di ssibbet n usitem d tnukra n imettinen.” \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt Řex. 24:21; 26:6; Fil. 3:5. \x*
\v 7 Ařami inna aya, imsar ijj n uxarweḍ jar Ifarisiyyen d Iṣaduqiyyen uca ittwabḍa řgens,
\v 8 minzi Iṣaduqiyyen qqaren belli war teǧi ca d tanukra niɣ d lmalakat uřa d buḥbeř, maca Ifarisiyyen cehhden x marra man aya. \x ◘ \xo 23:8 \xt Mt. 22:23; Mk. 12:18; Lk. 20:27. \x*
\v 9 Ikkar ijj n uxarweḍ d ameqqran. Ca n imseřmaden n idlisen zeg wezyen n Ifarisiyyen kkaren, ttemnaqacen akidsen s jjehd, nnan: “War nufi uřa d ijj n řɣar di bnadem-a. Mařa issiweř akides ijj n buḥbeř niɣ ijj n lmalak, man řɛib i yeǧa \add xenni\add* di man aya?” \x ◘ \xo 23:9 \xt Řex. 25:25; 26:31. \x*
\v 10 Umi ikkar ijj n uxarweḍ d ameqqran, iggʷed ukumandar ad mezzqen Bulus. Xenni yumur iɛeskariyyen Irumaniyyen maḥend ad dd-asen, ad t xeḍfen zi řwesṭ nsen, uca ad t awyen ɣar lqecla.
\m 
\v 11 Di ǧiřet iḍhar-dd Siditneɣ i Bulus, inna as: “Egg uř, minzi am mammec xafi tcehded di Urcalim ammu i ɣa tcehded uřa di Ruma!” \x ◘ \xo 23:11 \xt Řex. 18:9. \x*
\b
\s1 Taxceft n Wudayen ḥima ad nɣen Bulus
\m 
\v 12 Ařami d iṣbeḥ řḥař, munen ca zeg Wudayen, qqnen ixef nsen s ict n nneɛřet maḥend war ttᵉtten war sessen ař d nɣen Bulus. \x ◘ \xo 23:12 \xt Řex. 23:21, 29,30. \x*
\v 13 Ktar zi arebɛin n yeryazen kksen wawař-a s ict n tjaǧit.
\v 14 Ina ruḥen ɣar imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add*, nnan: “Aqa neqqen ixef nneɣ s ict n nneɛřet maḥend war nᵉttett walu ař ɣa nenneɣ Bulus.
\v 15 Xenni řexxu, \add mařa\add* kenniw d imeqqranen n Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add* ad tᵉttarem zeg ukumandar maḥend ad t-i-dd-indeh ɣarwem axmi texsem ad txebbcem di tmesřact-a mliḥ, aqa neccin newjed ḥima ad t nenneɣ qbeř ma ad ɣarwem dd-yaweḍ.”
\m 
\v 16 Isřa mmis n učmas n Bulus x tḥiřet-a. \add Xenni\add* yudef ɣar lqecla uca ixebbar Bulus x man aya.
\v 17 Iřaɣa Bulus i yijjen zeg řqebṭanat x mya, inna as: “Ruḥ s ubřiɣ-a ɣar ukumandar minzi ɣares ca ad as t yini.”
\v 18 Iksi řqebṭan x mya abřiɣ, uca iwyi t ɣar ukumandar, inna: “Bulus, ameḥbus, iřaɣa ayi-dd, ittar ayi ad ac awyeɣ abřiɣ-a i ɣar iǧa ca ad ac t ini.”
\m 
\v 19 Iṭṭef ukumandar abřiɣ s ufus, iddur zzayes weḥḥdes uca isseqsa t: “Min ɣarek ad ayi t tinid?”
\v 20 Inna as ubřiɣ: “Aqa Udayen arezzun ad zzayek ttaren maḥend ad dd-tessehwid Bulus tiwecca ɣar Jmaɛet nsen \add Tameqqrant\add*, axmi xsen ad t sseqsan ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 23:20 \xt Řex. 23:12. \x*
\v 21 War ttejji ad cek ssqenɛen, minzi ktar zi arebɛin n yeryazen zzaysen ggin as ijj n řfex deg webrid, qqnen ixef nsen s ict n nneɛřet maḥend war ttᵉtten war sessen ař t nɣen. Aqa nitni wejden řexxu, ttrajan ad tewced ttesriḥ nnec.”
\v 22 Akumandar ijja abřiɣ ad iraḥ, inna as: “War ttejji ḥed ad issen, aqa tessaregbed ayi x man aya.”
\m 
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa-dd ɣares x tnayen n iqebṭanen x mya, inna: “Swejdem mitayen n iɛeskariyyen Irumaniyyen maḥend ad raḥen ɣar Qayṣariya ɣar třata n ǧiřet, akidsen sebɛin n yinni inyin x yiysan u mitayen n imjebbaden n řqews s ufus ufusi.
\v 24 Ejj i-ten ad sswejden ict n zzayřet maḥend ad xas ssɣimen Bulus, ad t nedhen ɣar lɛamil Filiks di řaman.”
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* yura ict n tebrat, iwca asen tt. Ammu i dayes \add yura\add*:
\b
\m 
\v 26 “Kludiyus Lisiyas, i lɛamil yuɛřan Filiks: Sřam \add xak!\add*
\m 
\v 27 Udayen aqa ṭṭfen aryaz-a u tuɣa xsen ad t nɣen. Wciɣ \add as\add* afus ak-d iɛeskariyyen Irumaniyyen uca fekkeɣ t umi sřiɣ aqa-t d Arumani. \x ◘ \xo 23:27 \xt Řex. 21:33. \x*
\v 28 Minzi tuɣa xseɣ ad ssneɣ min xef t ḍeřmen, iwyeɣ t ɣar Jmaɛet nsen \add Tameqqrant\add*.
\v 29 Ufiɣ aqa ḍeřmen t di ssibbet n ca n ixarwiḍen n Ccariɛa nsen, maca war din \add ufiɣ\add* aḍřam i isdaheǧen iceddiyyen niɣ řmewt.
\v 30 Umi d ayi ittwanna, belli Udayen ggin as ijj n řfex deg webrid s tnuffra, ssekkeɣ t-i-dd řexdenni ɣarek, umureɣ i yinni t iḍeřmen ad ɣarek ruḥen maḥend ad kides ssiwřen zzatek \add mi xef t ḍeřmen\add*. S ttisir!”
\b
\m 
\v 31 Iɛeskariyyen Irumaniyyen ksin Bulus, am mammec d asen yumur, uca iwyen t s ǧiřet ɣar tendint n Antipatris.
\v 32 Tiwecca nnes jjin inni inyin x yeysan ad ɛeqben iɛeskariyyen imeddukkař nsen x iḍaren ɣar lqecla.
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* iwyen t ɣar Qayṣariya, wcin tabrat i lɛamil uca ssbedden Bulus zzates.
\v 34 Awarni řami iɣra tabrat \add nni\add*, isseqsa x man jjihet i zi dd-yusa netta, uca řami yufa belli netta yusa-dd zi Kilikiya,
\v 35 inna as: “Ad ac sřeɣ mařa uřa d yinni i cek iḍeřmen iwḍen-dd da!” Xenni yumur ad t ḥḍan di taddart n ccreɛ n Hirudus, \add umi qqaren ‘Prituriyum’\add*.
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Bulus zzat i lɛamil Filiks
\m 
\v 1 Awarni xemsa n wussan ihwa Ananiyas, arrays n ikehhanen, ak-d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* u ak-d ijj n weryaz s řhard iṣebḥen, qqaren as Tartulus, uca xebbaren lɛamil x Bulus. \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt Řex. 23:2. \x*
\v 2 Umi xas dd-řaɣan, iqarreb-dd Tartulus ɣar zzat maḥend ad t iḍřem, inna:
\b
\m “Aqa zzayek ɣarneɣ řehna tameqqrant u ssiyasa nnec aqa tiwi-dd aṭṭas n weɛdeř di ṭṭweɛ n řgens-a i dd-yiwyen ssahřa,
\v 3 u di kuř amcan marra neccin neqbeř tcuni nnec, \add a sidi\add* Filiks yuɛřan.
\v 4 Maca ḥima war cek hekkweřeɣ aṭṭas, ttareɣ zzayek ad tesřid mɣir cwayt ɣar tutra nneɣ i \add zzayek\add* nettar s uwaḍeɛ.
\v 5 Minzi nufa belli bnadem-a aqa-t d ijj n řeḥřac, ittsebbeb aɣuwweɣ jar marra Udayen di mkuř tammurt, minzi netta d azeǧif n tebridt n Inaṣiriyyen.
\v 6 Řami netta tuɣa yarezzu maḥend ad issexmej Zzawect Tameqqrant nneɣ, xenni neṭṭef i-t uca tuɣa nexs ad xas neḥkem s Ccariɛa nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 24:6 \xt Řex. 21:28. \x*
\v 7 Maca akumandar Lisiyas yusa-dd di řwesṭ s uhettek aṭṭas, iksi t jar ifassen nneɣ, issekk i-t ɣarek,
\v 8 uca yumur maḥend inni ixsen ad t ḍeřmen, ad ɣarek dd-asen. Mařa t tesseqsid, ad tfehmed zzayes s yixef nnec marra timesřayin-a min xef t neḍřem.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 Ccetcan xas Wudayen nni ɛawed, nnan: “Man aya ammu i iǧa!”
\v 10 Xas uca iceyyar lɛamil i Bulus maḥend ad issiweř. Bulus yarra-dd, inna:
\b
\m “Necc ssneɣ belli cek d řqaḍi x řgens-a i yijj n řmijař n waṭṭas n iseggʷusa, s uyenni ad wteɣ x yixef inu s teryast ktar.
\v 11 Am mammec ɣa yiři tessned cek, aqa ɛdun mɣir tenɛac n wussan waha zeg wami geɛɛdeɣ ḥima ad ɛebdeɣ di Urcalim.
\v 12 Nitni war d ayi ufin di Zzawect Tameqqrant ssawařeɣ ak-d ca n ijjen niɣ ssmuneɣ ijj n ubarru n řgens, war iǧi di temzidawin nsen, war iǧi di tendint. \x ◘ \xo 24:12 \xt Řex. 25:8; 28:17. \x*
\v 13 Nitni war zemmaren ad ssbeyynen min zi d ayi ḍeřmen řexxu.
\v 14 Maca man aya ad ac neɛmeɣ, belli ɛebbdeɣ AREBBI n řejdud inu x řeḥsab tɣuri nni x ssawařen, minzi umneɣ marra min yurin di Ccariɛa u deg Inabiyyen,
\v 15 am ɣari simant n usitem di AREBBI am mammec uřa d nitni ɣarsen, aqa ad din tiři tnukra zi taddart n imettinen, \add tanukra\add* n imseggaden uřa d \add tanukra\add* n yinni war iseggden.
\v 16 Ammu uřa d necc tteggeɣ tizemmar ḥima ad ɣari tiři řebda tnefsect teṣfa zzat i AREBBI u zzat i iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 24:16 \xt Řex. 23:1. \x*
\m 
\v 17 Awarni i waṭṭas n iseggʷusa usiɣ-dd ɣar řgens inu maḥend ad awyeɣ ṣṣdaqi d tɣarṣin. \x ◘ \xo 24:17 \xt Řex. 11:29; Rum. 15:25. \x*
\v 18 Aqa iwdan-a ufin ayi di Zzawect Tameqqrant awarni řami ttwassizdegeɣ, am war din \add ɣari\add* řɣaci niɣ d axarweḍ. \x ◘ \xo 24:18 \xt Řex. 21:27. \x*
\v 19 Maca Udayen nni dd-yusin zi Asiya, inni issekkaren iwdan, aqa ittxeṣṣa ad ḥḍaren da akidi zzatek maḥend ad ayi ḍeřmen zi min ma ɣarsen \add xafi\add*.
\v 20 Niɣ ad inin ina i da \add ibedden\add* man řɛib i dayi ufin umi beddeɣ zzat i Jmaɛet nsen \add Tameqqrant\add*,
\v 21 mɣir awař-a i tuɣa řaɣiɣ umi beddeɣ jar asen: ‘Ass-a ttwaḥekmeɣ zzatwem di ssibbet n tnukra n imettinen!’” \x ◘ \xo 24:21 \xt Řex. 23:6; 28:20. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 Maca umi issen Filiks Abrid-a mliḥ, issbedd i-ten, inna: “Xmi dd ɣa yas ukumandar, ad kemmřeɣ aseǧi ɣar min din jar awem.”
\v 23 \add Xas uca\add* yumur i řqebṭan x mya ḥima ad iḥḍa Bulus s cwayt n lḥurriya ktar u war imenneɛ uřa d ijj zeg inni t issnen ad xas sexxaren. \x ◘ \xo 24:23 \xt Řex. 27:3; 28:16. \x*
\m 
\v 24 Awarni ca n wussan ijja Filiks d Drusilla, tamɣart nnes d Tudact, ad dd-awyen Bulus uca sřan zzayes x l’iman n Lmasiḥ.
\v 25 Ařami yiweḍ řhard x tsegda d ḍḍebṭ n nnefs u x lḥisab i dd ɣa yasen, iggʷed Filiks, inna as: “Ruḥ řexxu! Xmi ɣari i ɣa yiři řweqt, ad ac dd-řaɣiɣ.”
\v 26 Netta tuɣa issitim ɛawed maḥend Bulus ad as iwc tmenyat \add ḥima ad as iḍřeq\add*. S uyenni tuɣa xas dd-iřaɣa aṭṭas n twařawin ḥima ad kis issiweř.
\m 
\v 27 Maca umi kemmřen tnayen n iseggʷusa, yusa-dd lɛamil wenni t i ɣa ixeřfen, qqaren as Purkiyus Fastus. Umi tuɣa Filiks ixs ad yarḍa Udayen, ijja Bulus di ssnaseř \add di řeḥbes\add*.
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Bulus zzat i Fastus
\m 
\v 1 Ařami dd-yiweḍ Fastus ɣar Qayṣariya, iruḥ ɣar Urcalim awarni řami ɛdun třata n wussan.
\v 2 Imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imcennɛen n Wudayen ssaregben t \add dinni\add* x min xef ḍeřmen Bulus uca qeddmen as ict n tutra.
\v 3 Ttaren zzayes maḥend ad \add asen\add* igg s řxaḍar ḥima ad indeh Bulus ɣar Urcalim, ařami zemmaren nitni ad sswejden ijj n řfex deg webrid maḥend ad t nɣen.
\v 4 Maca Fastus yarra-dd: “Bulus ittwaḥḍa di Qayṣariya u necc simant inu ad din raḥeɣ deɣya.
\v 5 Ejj inni zzaywem izemmaren ad afen tawwart ad raḥen akidneɣ, uca ejj i-ten ad t ḍeřmen mařa din ca n řɛib deg weryaz-a.”
\m 
\v 6 Awarni řami iqqim din tmenya niɣ ɛecra n wussan ihwa ɣar Qayṣariya u tiwecca nnes iqqim x řkursi n ccreɛ uca yumur ad dd-awyen Bulus.
\v 7 Umi dd-yiweḍ, nnḍen xas Wudayen inni tuɣa dd-ihwan zi Urcalim, uca ggin \add xas\add* aṭṭas n icetciten iḍeqřen, war zemmaren ad ten ssbeyynen.
\v 8 Umi iwta Bulus x yixef nnes, aqa war ixḍi netta di walu, war teǧi di Ccariɛa n Wudayen niɣ di Zzawect Tameqqrant uřa di qayṣar, \x ◘ \xo 25:8 \xt Řex. 24:12; 28:17. \x*
\v 9 inna Fastus i Bulus, am tuɣa ixs ad igg řxaḍar i Wudayen: “Ma texsed ad tgeɛɛded ɣar Urcalim, ḥima ad din tᵉttwaḥakmed zzati?”
\v 10 Yarra-dd Bulus, inna: “Necc aqa beddeɣ zzat i řkursi n ccreɛ n qayṣar mani ittxeṣṣa ad xafi ittwaḥkem. War xḍiɣ deg Wudayen s walu am mammec cek tessned mliḥ.
\v 11 Mařa xḍiɣ niɣ mařa ggiɣ min isdaheǧen řmewt, war ttrikkʷiřeɣ zi řmewt. Maca mařa war din bu tidett nican i zi d ayi ḍeřmen, xenni war izemmar uřa d ijjen ad ayi isellem ɣarsen i arḍa nsen. Necc uriɣ ddeɛwet inu ɣar qayṣar.” \x ◘ \xo 25:11 \xt Řex. 18:14. \x*
\m 
\v 12 Awarni řami tuɣa imcawar ak-d wegraw, yarra-dd Fastus: “Aqa tessgeɛɛded ddeɛwet nnec ɣar qayṣar, \add xenni\add* ɣar qayṣar i ɣa traḥed!”
\b
\s1 Tawasit n ujeǧid Aɣripas
\m 
\v 13 Awarni řami ɛdun ca n wussan yusa-dd ujeǧid Aɣripas d Barniki ɣar Qayṣariya ḥima ad seǧmen x Fastus.
\v 14 Umi nitni sseɛdun din aṭṭas n wussan iɛawed Fastus i ujeǧid ddeɛwet n Bulus, inna: “Aqa da ijj n weryaz wenni da ijja Filiks d ameḥbus. \x ◘ \xo 25:14 \xt Řex. 24:27. \x*
\v 15 Řami d ayi tuɣa di Urcalim, ssaregben ayi xas imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren n Wudayen, arezzun zzayi ad ittwaḥakem zzatsen.
\v 16 Necc arriɣ-dd xasen belli Irumaniyyen war nnumin ad sellmen ijj n bnadem ḥima ad ittwaneɣ maḥend ad ggen řxaḍar \add i iwdan\add*. Ittxeṣṣa ad ḥḍaren zzates inni t iḍeřmen uca ad ɣares yiři ttasiɛ \add i bnadem nni\add* maḥend ad idafeɛ x yixef nnes zi jjihet n ttuhmet.
\v 17 Umi da dd-iwḍeɣ, war ɛgizeɣ, uca tiwecca nnes qqimeɣ x řkursi n ccreɛ, umureɣ ad dd-awyen aryaz nni ɣari.
\v 18 Inni t iḍeřmen nnḍen as-dd, maca am mammec tuɣa ttrajiɣ war zemmaren ad dd-awyen uřa d ict n ttuhmet i tuɣa zemmaren ad ssbeyynen.
\v 19 Maca tuɣa ɣarsen xas ca n ixarwiḍen di ssibbet n ddin nsen u zi jjihet n ijj n bnadem qqaren as Yasuɛ wenni aqa immut, \add maca\add* wenni xef tuɣa Bulus iqqar belli aqa iddar.
\v 20 Am tuɣa cekkeɣ di tmesřayin-a i di tuɣa arzuɣ, nniɣ i Bulus: ‘Ma zeɛma texsed ad traḥed ɣar Urcalim ḥima ad tᵉttwaḥakmed din x tmesřayin-a?’
\v 21 Maca umi tuɣa yarezzu ad ittwaḥḍa ař xas ɣa iḥkem qayṣar, umureɣ ad t ḥḍan ař t ɣa ssekkeɣ ɣar qayṣar.”
\v 22 Inna Aɣripas i Fastus: “Uřa d necc xseɣ ad sřeɣ i bnadem-a!” Yarra-dd xas: “Tiwecca ad as tesřed!”
\m 
\v 23 Tiwecca nnes yusa-dd Aɣripas d Barniki s marra ccan uca udfen ɣar taddart n ccreɛ ak-d ikumandaren n řɛeskar d izeǧifen n tendint. Xenni yumur Fastus, uca yudef-dd Bulus.
\v 24 Inna Fastus: “\add A\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas u kenniw marra iryazen i da iḥḍaren akidneɣ: Aqa x weryaz-a nni teẓrim danita, aqa cetcan xas ɣari marra řɣaci n Wudayen di Urcalim uřa danita, sɣuyyun maḥend war ittɣimi ad iddar ɛad.
\v 25 Maca ufiɣ netta war iggi walu min isdaheǧen řmewt, maca umi issgeɛɛed ddeɛwet nnes ɣar qayṣar, umureɣ ad ittwassekk din. \x ◘ \xo 25:25 \xt Řex. 23:9; 26:31. \x*
\v 26 Maca war ɣari bu tmesřact nican ssneɣ tt zi jjihet nnes ḥima ad tt ariɣ i qayṣar. S uyenni sseḥḍareɣ t-i-dd i kenniw, d amezwaru i cek, \add a\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas, ḥima, awarni řami i ɣa nkemmeř tarezzut, ad ɣari yiři min ɣa ariɣ \add i qayṣar\add*,
\v 27 minzi war icuwwar ad ssekkeɣ ijj n umeḥbus břa ma ad ariɣ ixeṭṭan nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Adafeɛ n Bulus x yixef nnes zzat i ujeǧid Aɣripas
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* inna Aɣripas i Bulus: “Cek ɣarek ttesriḥ ḥima ad tessiwřed x yixef nnec!” Xenni isswiẓẓeḍ Bulus afus nnes uca iwta x yixef nnes, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Di marra min xef d ayi ḍeřmen Wudayen, \add a\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas, ḥessbeɣ ixef inu d \add bnadem\add* d amimun, aqa ass-a zemmareɣ ad wteɣ x yixef inu qibač nnec.
\v 3 Deg umezwaru s minzi aqa cek tessned mliḥ marra ixarwiḍen d izerfan n Wudayen. S uyenni ttareɣ zzayek ad ayi tesřed s ttasiɛ n řxaḍar.
\v 4 Minzi Udayen, iwa, mařa xsen ad cehden \add waha x man aya\add*, ssnen abrid n tudart inu mliḥ zi temẓi inu, am mammec t tuɣa zeg umezwaru jar řgens inu u di Urcalim.
\v 5 Nitni ssnen ayi mliḥ aṭṭas zeg wami, ssnen aqa tuɣa ddareɣ ɛlaḥsab taɣuri nican n Ifarisiyyen.
\v 6 U řexxu beddeɣ \add danita\add*, ttwaḥakameɣ di ṭṭweɛ n usitem n lwaɛd i zi iwaɛd AREBBI i řejdud nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 26:6 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:24; Dan. 9:24; Mixa 7:20. \x*
\v 7 Maɣar wa d asitem nni ttrajant tenɛac n tqebbař nneɣ ad ɣares dd-awḍent, am ssgeɛɛdent tiẓaǧitin yuǧɣen ǧiřet d wass. Di ṭṭweɛ n usitem-a, \add a\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas, ḍeřmen ayi Wudayen.
\v 8 Mammec tḥekkmem kenniw? Ma war ittxeṣṣa ad namen belli AREBBI ad issnekkar-dd imettinen?
\m 
\v 9 Zic tuɣa zeɛmeɣ nican, aqa ittxeṣṣa ad ggeɣ aṭṭas n tmesřayin ḍidd i Yisem n Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri. \x ◘ \xo 26:9 \xt Řex. 8:3; 9:1; 22:4; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 10 Uca aya i ggiɣ ɛawed di Urcalim. Am ṭṭfeɣ tizemmar zi jjihet n imeqqranen n ikehhanen, ḥebbseɣ aṭṭas n imqeddasen. Uca řami ttwanɣen zzaysen, tuɣa areṭṭiɣ s man aya ak-d inni xas iḥekmen.
\v 11 Ɛedbeɣ ten di marra timzidawin, ggiɣ xasen uɣiř maḥend ad ceqqfen Isem n Yasuɛ. Tuɣa tthajeɣ xasen aṭṭas u tuɣa ggureɣ ɣar tneddam inneɣni maḥend ad ten marrteɣ.
\m 
\v 12 Řami tuɣa ggureɣ ɣar Dimacq zi ssibbet nni s ṣṣulṭa d ttesriḥ zi jjihet n imeqqranen n ikehhanen,
\v 13 xenni, \add a\add* ajeǧid, umi tuɣa ayi deg webrid, ẓriɣ ict n tfawt zeg ujenna ɣar wezyen n wass, tᵉttissiqq ktar zi tfuct, tenneḍ ayi-dd u i yinni akidi imsafaren.
\v 14 Neccin newḍa marra di temmurt, sřiɣ i ict n tmijja tessawař-dd akidi, teqqar s Tɛibranit: ‘Cawul, Cawul, mayemmi xafi tdarrced? Aqa tarenyed tzeyyared x yixef nnec umi cek teccated \add awarni ac\add* di sřek n buykucḍan.’
\v 15 Nniɣ: ‘Min teɛnid Cek, a Sidi?’ Inna Siditneɣ: ‘Necc d Yasuɛ Annaṣiri, wenni tmarrted.’
\v 16 Xenni inna ayi: ‘Kkar, tbedded x iḍaren nnec, minzi i uya i d ac dd-ḍhareɣ ḥima ad cek arecḥḥeɣ d amsexxar d acehhad, aqa umi d ayi teẓrid u aqa ad ayi tẓared ɛawed.
\v 17 Ad fekkeɣ cek zeg weydud n Wudayen u zi řegnus nneɣni i ɣar cek ɣa ssekkeɣ,
\v 18 ḥima ad tarezmed tiṭṭawin nsen, ḥima ad tuben zi taǧest ɣar tfawt u zi ṣṣulṭa n cciṭan ɣar AREBBI, u ad ṭṭfen aɣfar n ddnub d ict n tesɣart n řwart jar imqeddasen s l’iman i dayi iǧan.’ \x ◘ \xo 26:18 \xt Ica. 60:1. \x*
\m 
\v 19 S uyenni, \add a\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas, war ɛekkseɣ ca řewḥiy nni ẓriɣ zeg ujenna,
\v 20 maca ɣar umezwar bdiɣ ad barrḥeɣ \add s Řexbar Aṣebḥan\add* i yinni iǧan di Dimacq d Urcalim u i marra inni \add izeddɣen\add* di dcurat n Yahudiyya, uca \add xenni\add* barrḥeɣ ɛawed i řegnus ḥima ad tuben ad dewřen ɣar AREBBI, ad ggen řexdayem i ittřiqen i ttubet. \x ◘ \xo 26:20 \xt Řex. 9:19, 28; 22:17, 21. \x*
\v 21 S uyenni ṭṭfen ayi Wudayen di Zzawect Tameqqrant uca xsen ad ayi nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 26:21 \xt Řex. 21:30. \x*
\v 22 Maca AREBBI iwca ayi afus ař ass-a, u xzar, aqa beddeɣ \add da\add* zzat i umeẓyan d umeqqran, war qqareɣ walu i dd-itteffɣen zi Ccariɛa n Musa d Inabiyyen, mɣir timesřayin waha nni zi qqaren nitni aqa ad iřint,
\v 23 belli tuɣa ittxeṣṣa i Lmasiḥ ad iweddeb u belli Netta ad yiři d Amenzu n Tnukra zi taddart n imettinen, ad ibarreḥ s Tfawt i řgens\add -a\add* u i řegnus \add marra\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 26:23 \xt Ica. 60:1-3, 19, 20\x*
\b
\m 
\v 24 Awarni řami idafeɛ Bulus s yixef nnes ammu, inna Fastus s jjehd: “Aqa cek d abuhaři, a Bulus. Aṭṭas n tɣuri tessbuhři i cek.”
\v 25 Maca Bulus inna as: “Necc war ttwaxeřfeɣ ca, \add a\add* sidi Fastus yuɛřan, aqa qqareɣ awařen n tidett, daysen řaman.
\v 26 Uřa d ajeǧid Aɣripas issen mliḥ x tmesřayin-a. S uyenni ssawařeɣ s teryast minzi ittřiɣ ayi belli uřa d ict n řḥajjet zi tmesřayin-a aqa tennuffar xas, minzi marra man aya war imsar di tnuffra.
\v 27 Ma tumned zeg inabiyyen, \add a\add* ajeǧid Aɣripas? Necc ssneɣ belli tumned \add zzaysen\add*.”
\v 28 Maca Aɣripas inna as: “\add Mɣir\add* s drus tessqenɛed ayi ḥima ad dewřeɣ d amasiḥi.”
\v 29 Inna \add as\add* Bulus: “Ttareɣ AREBBI belli deɣya u i waṭṭas, war iǧi cek waha, maca uřa d marra inni d ayi ittesřan ass-a, ad dewřen am necc, maca břa iceddiyyen-a.” \x ◘ \xo 26:29 \xt 1 Kur. 7:7. \x*
\v 30 Ikkar ujeǧid d lɛamil d Barniki d \add marra\add* inni tuɣa akidsen iqqimen,
\v 31 uca ffɣen ssenni am ssawařen ak-d wayawya, nnan jar asen: “Aryaz-a war iggi ca min isdaheǧen řmewt uřa d iceddiyyen.” \x ◘ \xo 26:31 \xt Řex. 23:9; 25:25. \x*
\v 32 Inna Aɣripas i Fastus: “Maɛlik war tuɣi issgeɛɛed ddeɛwet nnes ɣar qayṣar, iři aqa ittwaḍřeq bnadem-a.”
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Asafar n Bulus ɣar Ruma
\m 
\v 1 Xas uca ikkes Fastus awař, aqa ittxeṣṣa ad ittwassekk ɣar Iṭalya. Netta isellem Bulus d ca n imeḥbas nneɣni i yijj n řqebṭan x mya qqaren as Yuliyus, tuɣa-t zi řkumpaniyyet n qayṣar.
\v 2 Řami nenwa ad nbeḥḥar, nenya deg ijj n uɣarrabu zi Adramantus, tuɣa ad ikk x jjwayeh i iǧan x tma n Asiya, uca nruḥ. Inya akidneɣ deg uɣarrabu Aristarxus, ijj n weryaz zi Tissalunika di Makiduniya.
\v 3 Tiwecca nnes niweḍ ɣar Ṣaydun. Řqebṭan x mya tuɣa iǧa mliḥ ak-d Bulus, isamḥ as ad iraḥ ɣar imeddukkař nnes ḥima ad xas sexxaren. \x ◘ \xo 27:3 \xt Řex. 24:23; 28:16. \x*
\v 4 Ssenni neffeɣ, nbeḥḥar s ijj n ddura, neɛdu x Qubrus, minzi asemmiḍ tuɣa iccat dayneɣ deg uɣembub.
\v 5 Neẓwa řebḥar n Kilikiya d Pamfiliya, uca niweḍ ɣar Mira, ict n tendint di Likiya.
\v 6 Řqebṭan x mya yufa din ijj n uɣarrabu zi Iskandariyya, ittraḥ ɣar Iṭalya, issenya aneɣ dayes.
\v 7 Maɣar \add aɣarrabu\add* war iruḥ ɣar zzat aṭṭas n wussan, niweḍ s uɣiř zzat i tegzirt n Knidus, u minzi war d aneɣ yejji usemmiḍ ad nraḥ \add ɣar zzat\add*, nbeḥḥar deg udduri n Krita zzat i Salmuni.
\v 8 \add Řami\add* tuɣa war nzemmar ɛřayen ad nendeh ɣar zzat, niweḍ, řami newta ict n ddura temɣar, ɣar ijj n wemcan umi qqaren ‘Řmuyyat Iṣebḥanen’, wenni iǧan ṭṭarf i tendint qqaren as Lasiyya.
\m 
\v 9 Neqqim aṭṭas n řweqt dinni ař dd-iɛdu ass n uẓummi n Wudayen. Umi idweř usafar di řebḥar yewɛar, iɛřem \add asen\add* Bulus,
\v 10 inna: “\add A\add* iryazen, ttwařiɣ asafar ad yawi druct d txessart \add aṭṭas\add*, war teǧi i sseřɛet d uɣarrabu nneɣ waha, maca uřa i tudart nneɣ.”
\v 11 Maca řqebṭan x mya tuɣa isřa ktar ɣar umendah d řqebṭan n uɣarrabu x min tuɣa ittesřa ɣar wawařen n Bulus.
\v 12 Umi tuɣa amcan n řmuyyi war iḥři ḥima ad sseɛdun řmecta din, ibedd array n wezyen ameqqran nsen ad ffɣen ssenni, balak ad awḍen ɣar Finiks, ijj n řmuyyi di Krita, iwařan ljanub, ḥima ad din sseɛdun řmecta. *
\b
\s1 Taḥaryaḍt
\m 
\v 13 Umi isaha usemmiḍ n ljanub, tuɣa nitni ssittimen ad awḍen am mammec tt xsen, uca nebda ttcuqan x ṭṭarf n tma n Krita.
\v 14 Maca cwayt awarni man aya, tekkar ict n tḥaryaḍt, qqaren as ttifun ‘Uruklidun’. \f ◼ \fr 27:14 \fk Ttifun Uruklidyun\ft - aqa-t d ijj n usemmiḍ i dd-yusin zi ccamal.\f*
\v 15 Ittwaksi zzayes uɣarrabu s jjehd, war izemmar i usemmiḍ. \add Xenni\add* nestewṭeɛ \add uca nettwandeh\add*.
\v 16 Am nekka deg udduri n ict n tegzirt d tameẓyant umi qqaren ‘Qawda’, s uɣiř i nemneɛ ḍman n tɣarrabut n usellek \add i iǧan ɣar ḍeffar n uɣarrabu\add*.
\v 17 Nessgeɛɛed i-tt, u nessejhed aɣarrabu am t nebyes swadday s iḥezzamen. Maɣar tuɣa neggʷed aqa aɣarrabu ad immenḍar x ict n řgeɛɛdet n ijdi di řebḥar, nessehwa-dd řbacc uca nettwandeh s usemmiḍ u ammu i nřaḥ.
\v 18 Uca umi taḥaryaḍt thaj xaneɣ aṭṭas, xenni tiwecca nnes nenḍar sseřɛet nneɣ di řebḥar.
\v 19 Deg wass wiss třata nenḍar řeqcuɛ n uɣarrabu s ifassen nneɣ.
\v 20 Řami taḥaryaḍt teqqim tᵉttsuḍ aṭṭas n wussan, war tbin tfuct řa d taziri uřa d itran, xenni ittwaqḍeɛ marra řayas ad neqqim neddar.
\m 
\v 21 Řami war izemmar uřa d ijj ad iṣbar ɛad, ibedd Bulus di řwesṭ nsen, inna: “A iryazen, tuɣa ittxeṣṣa awem ad ɣari tesřem, xenni war neffiɣ ca zi Krita u war d aneɣ třeqqef druct-a d řeḥṣaret-a.
\v 22 Řexxu ad kenniw cejjɛeɣ, minzi uřa d ijj zzaywem war ittweddari ca tudart nnes, mɣir aɣarrabu waha \add ad iɣebbař\add*.
\v 23 Minzi ibedd-dd ɣari ǧiřet-a lmalak n AREBBI wenni necc nnes u wenni umi ɛebbdeɣ.
\v 24 Netta inna ayi: “War tteggʷed ca, a Bulus, minzi ittxeṣṣa ac ad tbedded qibač i qayṣar. Xzar marra inni akidek ittbeḥḥaren, aqa iwca ac ten AREBBI.”
\v 25 S uya ggem taryast, a iryazen, minzi ttiqqeɣ di AREBBI, belli ad teffeɣ am mammec d ayi inna.
\v 26 Maca ad nemmenḍar x ict n tegzirt.”
\m 
\v 27 Awarni řami nettwaɛaren zi ssa ɣar diha u nessiḥeř ixef nneɣ di Řebḥar n Hadriyus, ittɣiř asen i ibeḥriyyen di řwesṭ n ǧiřet, aqa nqarreb-dd ɣar řbarr.
\v 28 Nitni nḍaren ayřizim di raǧaɣ n řebḥar, ɛebbaren ɛicrin n tiddiwin. Umi ɛdun cwayt, ɛebbaren nitni xemmesṭac n tiddiwin. \f ◼ \fr 27:28 \fk tiddi - tiddiwin\ft - řqedd n ijj n bnadem i isswiẓẓaden ifassen nnes sennej i uzeǧif nnes, aqa-t ɛřaḥař 1,8 mitru.\f*
\v 29 Am neggʷed ad neřqef imucan n sseǧaḥ, nenḍar arebɛa n iyřizam zi ḍeffar n uɣarrabu, uca nettar ad dd-yaweḍ uziř.
\m 
\v 30 Řami tuɣa ibeḥriyyen xsen ad arewřen zeg uɣarrabu, ssḍaren taɣarrabut n usellek ɣar řebḥar axmi xsen ad dayes nyin maḥend ad cedden aɣarrabu ɣar temmurt.
\v 31 Umi iẓra Bulus man aya, inna i řqebṭan x mya u i iɛeskariyyen: “Mařa ina war qqimen deg uɣarrabu, war tzemmarem ad ttwassnejmem.”
\v 32 Xenni qessen iɛeskariyyen iseɣwan n tɣarrabut \add n usellek\add* uca jjin tt ad truḥ.
\m 
\v 33 Ařami dd-iqarreb ad iṣbeḥ řḥař, iziyyar i-ten Bulus marra ḥima ad ccen, inna: “Arbeɛṭac n wussan aqa war teccim walu zi ssibbet n lxaṭar.
\v 34 S uyenni cejjɛeɣ kenniw ad teccem, ḥima ad teqqimem teddarem, minzi war iweṭṭi uřa d ijj n uẓeṭṭu \add n ucuwwaf\add* n uzeǧif n uřa d ijjen zzaywem.” \x ◘ \xo 27:34 \xt Mt. 10:30. \x*
\v 35 Awarni řami inna aya, iksi aɣrum, issemɣar AREBBI qibač i marra, yarẓa i-t, ibda ad icc. \x ◘ \xo 27:35 \xt 1 Ṣm. 9:13; Yḥ. 6:11; 1 Tim. 4:3. \x*
\v 36 Marra ttwacejjɛen u ksin macca.
\v 37 Tuɣa aneɣ deg uɣarrabu di mitayen u-setta u-sebɛin n yeryazen.
\v 38 Řami jjiwnen s macca, bdan ssefsasen aɣarrabu, am ksin řḥebb \add n yirden\add*, nḍaren t di řebḥar.
\m 
\v 39 Ařami iṣbeḥ řḥař, tuɣa ibeḥriyyen war ssinen man tammurt \add i teǧa\add*, maca ẓrin ijj n umesruq n řebḥar ɣar tma n řbarr uca mcawaren, ma zemmaren ad din ɛarnen aɣarrabu.
\v 40 Umi qeḍwen iyřizam n uɣarrabu, jjin ten di řebḥar, fesyen iceddan n řemqadef, ssgeɛɛden řbacc n zzat i usemmiḍ ittsuḍen, wejjhen ɣar tma n řbarr.
\v 41 Maca aɣarrabu iwta ijj n uɛarric n yejdi mani iǧa řebḥar ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen uca nnuɣen s uɣarrabu. Yarsa zzat n uɣarrabu \add x uɛarric n yejdi\add*, war izemmar ad inhezz, maca ḍeffar n uɣarrabu iqeřɛ i-t jjehd n řemwaj. \x ◘ \xo 27:41 \xt 2 Kur. 11:25. \x*
\m 
\v 42 Tuɣa newwan iɛeskariyyen ad nɣen imeḥbas ḥima war immenḍar ḥed ixef nnes \add di řebḥar\add* maḥend ad iɛumm, uca ad yarweř.
\v 43 Maca řqebṭan x mya wenni tuɣa ixs ad issenjem Bulus, issbedd i-ten, yumur belli inni izemmaren ad mmenḍaren ixef nsen \add deg waman\add*, maḥend ad ɛummen, ad ɛummen d amezwaru, maḥend ad awḍen ɣar řbarr.
\v 44 Wi iqqimen, ijja i-ten ad ẓwan x tfeřwin u x izeynan n ikeccuḍen n uɣarrabu, uca ammu i iwḍen marra ɣar řbarr, ttwassnejmen.
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Bulus di tegzirt n Malta
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya nefhem, belli tagzirt-a qqaren as Malta.
\v 2 Ibarraniyyen inni din izedɣen ggin akidneɣ mliḥ aṭṭas, am ssiɣen ict n tmessi d tameqqrant uca řaɣan aneɣ marra ɣarsen, ḥima ad neẓɣeř minzi anẓar tuɣa iccat aṭṭas u tuɣa tesmeḍ.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* tuɣa issmun Bulus aɛurric n ikecwaḍ, issars i-ten x tmessi, xenni s řeḥmu nni iffeɣ-dd ijj n ufiɣar uca iqqes as deg ufus.
\v 4 Umi ẓrin ibarraniyyen aqa yuyeř \add ufiɣar\add* ɣar ufus nnes, nnan: “Ad taɣ bnadem-a d aqettař, war t tejji ‘\add lalla\add* řḥeqq’ ad iddar, waxxa injem-dd zi řebḥar.”
\v 5 Maca Bulus izzerz s ufus nnes, immenḍar afiɣar di tmessi, břa ma d as temsar uřa d ict n druct. \x ◘ \xo 28:5 \xt Mk. 16:18; Lk. 10:19. \x*
\v 6 Maca nitni tuɣa ttrajan ad yuff řexdenni uca ad iwḍa ad immet. Maca umi ẓrin, awarni řami rajan aṭṭas, belli war d as temsar uřa d ict n řḥajjet taɛeffant, ibeddeř řhard nsen, nnan, aqa-t d ijj n arebbi. \x ◘ \xo 28:6 \xt Řex. 14:11. \x*
\m 
\v 7 Tuɣa d jjihet nni iyyaren i yeǧan d agřa n ijj n weryaz umi qqaren Publiyus. Netta tuɣa d azeǧif n tegzirt, issnewju aneɣ s řxar třata n wussan di taddart nnes.
\v 8 Babas n Publiyus tuɣa dayes timessi d řeḥriq. Dayes ijj n řeḥřac n teqqrint. Yudef Bulus ɣares, iẓẓuǧ, issars xas afus uca issgenfa i-t.
\v 9 Umi imsar man aya, usin-dd ɣares inneɣni n tegzirt inni tuɣa ɣar iǧa imehřac uca ttwassgenfan.
\v 10 Karmen xaneɣ ina s waṭṭas n ccan. Umi nruḥ nbeḥḥar ssenni, wcin aneɣ min tuɣa neḥwaj.
\b
\s1 Awaḍ n Bulus ɣar Ruma
\m 
\v 11 Awarni teřt n iyuren nruḥ, nbeḥḥar deg ijj n uɣarrabu zi Iskandariyya i isseɛdun řmecta di tegzirt, tuɣa xas arcam n ‘Tecniwin’.
\v 12 Umi dd-niweḍ ɣar Siragusa, neqqim din třata n wussan.
\v 13 Ssenni ndur uca niweḍ-dd ɣar Rixiyum. Awarni ijj n wass ikkar-dd usemmiḍ n tcarmin uca niweḍ-dd deg ijj n řmijař n tnayen n wussan ɣar Putiyuli, ict n tendint di Iṭalya.
\v 14 Dinni i nufa tawmat nni zzayneɣ ittaren ad \add kidsen\add* neqqim, uca neqqim akidsen sebɛa n wussan. Xenni nruḥ ɣar Ruma.
\v 15 Umi sřin tawmat \add di Ruma\add* x umeddur nneɣ, usin-dd ḥima ad kidneɣ mmeřqan deg wazzay umi qqaren ‘Apiyus Furus’ u ɣar ‘Třata n Tḥuna’. Umi ten iẓra Bulus, icekkar AREBBI uca ittwacejjeɛ.
\m 
\v 16 Umi dd-niweḍ ɣar Ruma, iwca řqebṭan x mya ttesriḥ i Bulus maḥend ad izdeɣ mani ixs netta, ak-d ijj n uɛessas wenni t i ɣa iḥḍan. \x ◘ \xo 28:16 \xt Řex. 24:23; 27:3. \x*
\b
\s1 Ameřqi n Bulus ak-d Wudayen di Ruma
\m 
\v 17 Awarni třata n wussan iřaɣa Bulus i imcennɛen n Wudayen. Ařami munen, inna asen:
\b
\m “\add A\add* iryazen tawmat, waxxa necc war ggiɣ uřa d ict n řḥajjet ḍidd i řgens niɣ ḍidd i Ccariɛa n řejdud inu, aqa ttwasellmeɣ d ameḥbus zi Urcalim deg ifassen n Irumaniyyen. \x ◘ \xo 28:17 \xt Řex. 24:12; 25:8. \x*
\v 18 Awarni řami d ayi beqqcen, tuɣa xsen ad ayi arxun minzi war dayi ufin uřa d ict n řḥajjet tessdaheǧ řmewt.
\v 19 Maca umi ɛekksen Wudayen x man aya, s uɣiř xafi ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ ddeɛwet inu ɣar qayṣar, maca břa ma ad ɣari yiři ijj n ucetci x řgens inu.
\v 20 X ssibbet-a ttareɣ ḥima ad kenniw ẓareɣ uca ad kiwem ssiwřeɣ. Minzi di ssibbet n usitem n Israil, aqa ayi carfeɣ s ssnesřet-a.” \x ◘ \xo 28:20 \xt Irm. 14:8; 17:13; Řex. 23:6; 24:21. \x*
\v 21 Maca nitni nnan as: “War xak neṭṭif ca tibratin zi Yahudiyya uca uřa d ijj n tawmat war dd-yusi da wi innan niɣ issiwřen xak s ca n řɛib.
\v 22 Maca neccin nexs ad zzayek nseř min tᵉttwařid, minzi zi jjihet n tebridt-a, aqa nessen belli ttɛekksen tt mani ma.”
\m 
\v 23 Nitni mɛahaden akides x ijj n wass, uca munen. Aṭṭas i-dd-yusin ɣar wemcan mani izeddeɣ. Netta tuɣa ittfessar asen Tageldit n AREBBI, am icehhed u yarezzu ad ten isseqneɛ zi jjihet n Yasuɛ, zi Ccariɛa n Musa u zeg inabiyyen, zi řefjar ařami d tameddit. \x ◘ \xo 28:23 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:24; Dan. 9:24; Mixa 7:20. \x*
\v 24 Ca ttwassqenɛen s wawařen nnes, \add maca\add* inneɣni war ttwassqenɛen ca. \x ◘ \xo 28:24 \xt Řex. 17:4. \x*
\v 25 Nitni ffɣen xas am war dd-usin ak-d wayawya. \add Xenni\add* inna asen Bulus \add ɛad\add* awař-a: “S řḥeqq issiweř Arruḥ Iqeddsen x \add uqemmum n\add* Icaɛya i řejdud nwem, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 26 \qt ‘Ruḥ ɣar řgens-a, ini asen:\qt*
\m \qt ‘S useǧi ad tesřem,\qt*
\m \qt war tfehhemem,\qt*
\m \qt s tmuɣři ad texzarem,\qt*
\m \qt war tᵉttwiřim,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 28:26 \xt Ica. 6:9-10; Ḥiz. 12:2; Mt. 13:14; Mk. 4:12; Lk. 8:10; Yḥ. 12:40; Rum. 11:8. \x*
\m 
\v 27 \qt minzi uř n řgens-a aqa idweř iqseḥ,\qt*
\m \qt Imezzuɣen nsen ssḍeqřen ten i useǧi,\qt*
\m \qt u tiṭṭawin nsen qqnen tent,\qt*
\m \qt maḥend war ttwiřin s tiṭṭawin nsen,\qt*
\m \qt war ttesřin s imezzuɣen nsen,\qt*
\m \qt war fehhemen s wuř nsen,\qt*
\m \qt ařami war ɣari dekkwiřen\qt*
\m \qt uca ad asen ɣfareɣ.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 28:27 \xt Ica. 6:9-10. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 28 Man aya ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem: \add Areqqas n\add* usenjem-a n AREBBI aqa ittwassekk-dd i řegnus uca uřa d nitni ad ɣares sřen.”
\v 29 Awarni řami inna man aya, ffɣen Wudayen, am tuɣa ttemcubbucen jar asen aṭṭas.
\b
\m 
\v 30 Bulus icra ict n taddart, ixeǧeṣ i-tt s yixef nnes, izeddeɣ dayes tnayen n iseggʷusa. Tuɣa ittareḥḥab s marra inni tuɣa ɣares dd-ittasen,
\v 31 ittbarreḥ s Tgeldit n AREBBI, isseřmad x Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ s bṭayṭay u břa ma tᵉttwassbedd uřa d ict n tɛenkrift. 
